var book = {
	"name": "Mathaïos",
	"numChapters": 28,
	"chapters": {
		"1": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Ka kitab ka jingkha ïa U Jisu Khrist, uba u khun u Dabid, uba u khun u Abraham.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> U Abraham u la pynkha ïa u Isaak; bad u Isaak u la pynkha ïa u Jakob; bad u Jakob u la pynkha ïa u Juda bad ïa ki para jong u;",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> bad u Juda u la pynkha ïa u Phares bad ïa u Sera na ka Tamar; bad u Phares u la pynkha ïa u Esrom; bad u Esrom u la pynkha ïa u Aram;",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> bad u Aram u la pynkha ïa u Aminadab; bad u Aminadab u la pynkha ïa u Naason; bad u Naason u la pynkha ïa u Salmon;",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> bad u Salmon u la pynkha ïa u Boas na ka Rahab; bad u Boas u la pynkha ïa u Obed na ka Ruth; bad u Obed u la pynkha ïa u Jesse;",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> bad u Jesse u la pynkha ïa u Dabid Syiem. Bad u Dabid u la pynkha ïa u Solomon na kaba la ju long ka tnga u Uriah;",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> bad u Solomon u la pynkha ïa u Roboam; bad u Roboam u la pynkha ïa u Abia; bad u Abia u la pynkha ïa u Asa;",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> bad u Asa u la pynkha ïa u Josaphat; bad u Josaphat u la pynkha ïa u Joram; bad u Joram u la pynkha ïa u Osias;",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> bad u Osias u la pynkha ïa u Joatham; bad u Joatham u la pynkha ïa u Ahas; bad u Ahas u la pynkha ïa u Esekaïas;",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> bad u Esekaïas u la pynkha ïa u Manasseh; bad u Manasseh u la pynkha ïa u Amon; bad u Amon u la pynkha ïa u Josaïah;",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> bad u Josaïah u la pynkha ïa u Jekhoniah bad ïa ki para jong u, hamar ka por ba la ring mraw ïa ki sha Babilon.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Hadien kata ka jingring mraw sha Babilon te, u Jekhoniah u la pynkha ïa u Salathiel; bad u Salathiel u la pynkha ïa u Sorobabel;",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> bad u Sorobabel u la pynkha ïa u Abiud; bad u Abiud u la pynkha ïa u Eliakim; bad u Eliakim u la pynkha ïa u Asor;",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> bad u Asor u la pynkha ïa u Sadok; bad u Sadok u la pynkha ïa u Akhim; bad u Akhim u la pynkha ïa u Eliud;",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> bad u Eliud u la pynkha ïa u Eleasar; bad u Eleasar u la pynkha ïa u Mathan; bad u Mathan u la pynkha ïa u Jakob;",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> bad u Jakob u la pynkha ïa u Joseph, uba u tnga ka Mari, na kaba la kha ïa U Jisu, ïa uba la khot “U Khrist”.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Kumta, ki pateng bynriew baroh naduh u Abraham haduh u Dabid ki la long khatsaw pateng; naduh u Dabid ruh haduh ka jingring mraw sha Babilon khatsaw pateng; bad naduh ka jingring mraw sha Babilon haduh U Khrist khatsaw pateng.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Ka jingkha ïa U Jisu Khrist te ka la long kumne: Haba ka kmie jong u, ka Mari, ka la ïatehktien bad u Joseph, mynba kim pat ïashem, la paw ba ka la punkhun keiñ na U Mynsiem Bakhuid.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Hynrei, u Joseph, u tnga jong ka, ba u da long u bahok, ba um mon ruh ban pynbna ïa ka ha ki briew, u la mut ban pyllait noh jar jar ïa ka.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Hynrei, haba u dang puson ïa kine kiei kiei ruh, ha khmih, u angel U Trai u la paw ha u ha ka jingphohsniew, u da ong, “Ko Joseph, u khun u Dabid, wat sheptieng ban shim ha me ïa ka Mari ka tnga jong me: naba ita iba la pun ha ka, i long na U Mynsiem Bakhuid:",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> kan kha ruh ïa u khun; men khot ruh ïa ka kyrteng jong u, ‘U Jisu’: naba un pynim ïa la ki briew na ki pop jong ki.”",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> La leh ïa kane baroh te, ba kumta yn pyndep ïa kata ba la ong U Trai da u nongïathuhlypa, u da ong,",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> “Ha khmih, kata ka theisotti kan punkhun, kan kha ruh ïa u khun, bad kin ïakhot ïa ka kyrteng jong u, ‘U Emmanuel,’ ” kaba long, haba la batai, “U Blei lem bad ngi”.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Te haba u Joseph u la khie na kaba thiah, u la leh kumba la hukum u angel U Trai ïa u, bad u la shim ha u ïa ka tnga jong u:",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> hynrei, um pat shym la ithuh ïa ka, tad ynda ka la kha ïa u khun nyngkong jong ka: u la khot ruh ïa ka kyrteng jong u, “U Jisu”."
		},
		"2": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Haba la kha ïa U Jisu ha Bethlehem Judia, mynba u Herod u long syiem, ha khmih, la wan ki riewstad na mihngi sha Jerusalem,",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> ki da ong, “Hangno uba la dang kha shen U Syiem ki Jiw? naba ngi la ïohi ïa u khlur jong u ha ka ri mihngi, bad ngi la ïawan ban mane ïa u.”",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Hynrei, haba u Herod syiem u la ïohsngew ïa kata, u la khihwin, bad ka Jerusalem baroh lem bad u.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Te haba u la ïalum lang ïa ki rangbah lyngdoh baroh bad ïa ki nongthoh u paidbah, u la kylli ïa ki, “Hangno ba yn kha ïa U Khrist?”",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Te ki la ïathuh ha u, “Ha Bethlehem Judia: naba kumne la thoh da u nongïathuhlypa,",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> “ ‘Pha ruh ka Bethlehem, ka ri Judia, pham long i barit tam hapdeng ki syiem Judia: naba na pha un mih U Nongsynshar, u ban sharai ïa ki briew jong nga ki Israel.’ ”",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Ynda kumta, u Herod haba u la khot jar jar ïa kita ki riewstad, u la kylli biang biang ruh na ki, ïa ka aïom ba u la mihpaw uta u khlur.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Bad haba u la phah noh ïa ki sha Bethlehem, u la ong, “To khie leit noh ïawad biang biang ruh ïa uta u khunlung; bad ynda phi la shem, wan ïathuh pat ha nga, ba nga ruh ngan ïoh wan mane ïa u.”",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Te haba ki la ïohsngew ïa u syiem, ki la leit noh: ha khmih ruh, uta u khlur, ïa uba ki la ïohi ha mihngi, u la leit sha shuwa jong ki, tad ynda u la poi bad u la neh haneng ka jaka ha kaba u don uta u khunlung.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Te haba ki la ïohi ïa uta u khlur, ki la ïakmen da ka jingkmen bakhraw eh.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Haba ki la ïawan ruh ha ka ïing, ki la ïohi ïa uta u khunlung lem bad ka Mari ka kmie jong u; haba ki la ïadem ki la ïamane ruh ïa u; bad haba ki la ïalaw ïa ki jingsong jong ki, ki la ïatyrwa ai ki jingai ha u, ïa ka ksiar, bad ïa ka jingiwbih, bad ïa ka mirr de.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Te haba la maham lypa ïa ki na U Blei ha ka jingphohsniew ba kin ym leit phai pat sha u Herod, ki la ïaleit noh sha la ka ri na kawei pat ka lynti.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Haba ki la ïaleit noh, ha khmih, u angel U Trai u la paw ha u Joseph ha ka jingphohsniew, u da ong, “To ïeng to shim noh ruh ïa u khunlung bad ïa ka kmie jong u, to phet noh sha ri Ijipt, bad men shong hangta tad ynda ngan ong ha me: naba u Herod un sa wad ïa uta u khunlung ïa ka ban pynïap noh ïa u.”",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Te haba u la ïeng, u la shim noh ïa uta u khunlung bad ïa ka kmie jong u mynmiet, bad u la leit noh sha Ijipt:",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> bad u la shong hangta haduh ka jingïap u Herod: ba kumta yn pyndep ïa kata ba la ong U Trai da u nongïathuhlypa, u da ong, “Na Ijipt nga la khot ïa u khun jong nga.”",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Ynda kumta, u Herod, haba u la ïohi ba la shukor ïa u da kita ki riewstad, u la bitar eh lep, bad u la phah pynïap noh ïa ki khun shynrang baroh kiba ha Bethlehem, bad ha ki phang jong ka baroh, naduh kiba ar snem bad kiba kham poh, kumba dei kata ka aïom ïa kaba u la kylli biang biang ruh na kita ki riewstad.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Te kumta, la pyndep ïa kata ba la ong da u Jeremaïah u nongïathuhlypa, u da ong,",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> “Ha Rama la ïohsngew ka jingsawa, ka jingïam bad ka jingïambriew kaba khraw, ka Rakhel ka da ïam namar la ki khun: kam mon ruh ba yn pyntngen ïa ka, naba kim don shuh.”",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Hynrei, haba la ïap u Herod, ha khmih, u angel U Trai u la paw ha u Joseph ha ka jingphohsniew ha Ijipt,",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> u da ong, “To ïeng, to shim noh ïa uta u khunlung bad ïa ka kmie jong u, to khie leit ruh sha ka ri Israel: namar ki la ïap kita kiba la ïawad ïa ka mynsiem uta u khunlung.”",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Kumta, haba u la ïeng, u la shim ïa uta u khunlung bad ïa ka kmie jong u, bad u la wan noh sha ka ri Israel.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Hynrei, haba u la ïohsngew ba u Arkhelos u synshar ha Judia ha ka jaka u Herod u kpa jong u, u la sngewsheptieng ban leit shata: te haba la maham lypa ïa u na U Blei ha ka jingphohsniew, u la kynriah noh sha ki phang ka Galilaïa.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Haba u la poi ruh, u la shong duh ha ka shnong ba la khot “ka Nasaret”: ba kumta yn pyndep ïa kata ba la ong da ki nongïathuhlypa, “Ba yn khot ‘u nong Nasaret’ ïa u.”"
		},
		"3": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Ha kita ki sngi, u la wan u Ïoannis u Nongpynbaptis, u da ïalap ha ka ri khlaw Judia,",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> u da ong, “To kylla-ka-bamut; naba ka hima ki bneng ka la jan.”",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Naba une u long uta, ba la ong shaphang jong u da u Isaïah u nongïathuhlypa, u da ong, “Ka ktien uba pyrta ha ka ri khlaw, ‘Phin pynkhreh ïa ka lynti bah U Trai, phin pynbeit ïa ki lynti jong u.’ ”",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Te uta u Ïoannis u la don ka jaiñkup jong u na u shñiuh ut, bad ka panpoh snieh ha ka syngkai jong u; ka jingbam jong u ruh ka la long da ki puit bad ka ngap khlaw.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Ynda kumta, ki la leit noh ha u ka Jerusalem, bad ka Judia baroh, bad baroh ka ri kylleng ka Jordan;",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> bad la pynbaptis ïa ki da u ha wah Jordan; ki da ïaphla noh ïa ki pop jong ki.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Hynrei, haba u la ïohi ba bun na ki Pharisi bad ki Saddusi ki ïawan sha ka jingbaptis jong u, u la ong ha ki, “A phi ki khun ki ksiew ki bseiñ, uei ba la maham ïa phi ban phet ïap noh na kata ka jingbitar ka ban sa lap?",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Naba kumta to sei ïa u soh uba dei biang ïa ka jingkylla-ka-bamut:",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Bad wat mut ban ong ha lade, ‘Ngi don u Abraham uba long u kpa jong ngi’: naba nga ong ha phi, ba U Blei u lah na kine ki maw ban pynmih khun ïa u Abraham.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Hynrei, mynta ruh la thew ïa ka wait ha u thied ki dieng; namar kata, ïa u dieng baroh u bymsei soh babha yn khet noh, bad yn bred sha ka ding.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> “Nga shisha nga pynbaptis ïa phi da ka um ïa ka ban kylla-ka-bamut: hynrei, uta uba wan nadien jong nga u long uba kham khraw bor ïa nga, uba kam dei ïa nga ban rah wat tang ïa ki juti jong u: uta keiñ, un pynbaptis ïa phi da U Mynsiem Bakhuid bad da ka ding:",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> uba ka jingpeh jong u ka ha ka kti jong u, un pynkhuid bha ruh ïa ka kyntem jong u; bad un lum ïa u Kew jong u ha la ka thiar; hynrei, un thang ïa u stait da ka ding bymjulip.”",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Ynda kumta, U Jisu u la wan na Galilaïa sha wah Jordan ha u Ïoannis, ba yn ïoh pynbaptis da u.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Hynrei, u Ïoannis u la khang ïa U, u da ong, “Nga donkam ba yn pynbaptis ïa nga da me, te me wan pynban ha nga?”",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> U Jisu te u la ïathuh bad U la ong ha u, “To shah mynta: naba kumne keiñ ka long kaba dei ïa ngi ban pyndep ïa ka hok baroh.” Ynda kumta, u la shah ïa u.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> U Jisu te, ynda la pynbaptis ïa u, u la kiew noh kumne kumne na ka um: ha khmih ruh, la plie ïa ki bneng ïa u, bad u la ïohi ïa U Mynsiem U Blei ba u da hiar kum ka paro, ba u da wan shong ruh ha u.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Ha khmih ruh ka ktien na ki bneng, ka da ong, “Une u long U Khun jong nga uba ieit, ha uba nga sngewbha eh.”"
		},
		"4": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Ynda kumta, la ïalam noh ïa U Jisu da U Mynsiem sha ka ri khlaw, ba yn pynshoi ïa u da u Soitan.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Ynda U la shah jingit sawphew sngi bad sawphew miet, hadien kata, U la thngan.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Te haba uta u nongpynshoi u la wan ha U, u la ong, “Lada me long U Khun U Blei, to hukum ïa kine ki maw ba kin long ki kpu.”",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Hynrei, U la ïathuh bad U la ong, “La thoh: “ ‘Bym tang da u kpu hi ba un im u briew, hynrei, da ki ktien baroh ba mih noh na ka shyntur U Blei.’ ”",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Ynda kumta, u Soitan u la ïalam ïa U sha ka nongbah ka bakhuid; bad u la buh ïa U halor jrong ka dong ka templ,",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> bad u la ong ha U, “Lada me long U Khun U Blei, to pynnoh ïa lade; naba la thoh: “ ‘Un ai hukum ïa ki angel jong u shaphang jong me’: “bad “ ‘kin rah ïa me ha ki kti jong ki, ba ïoh kumno kumno me jynthut ïa la ka kjat ha u maw.’ ”",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> U Jisu u la ong ha u, “La thoh pat: ‘Men ym tynjuh ïa U Trai  uba U Blei jong me.’ ”",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> U Soitan u la ïalam pat ïa U sha u lum bajrong eh, bad u la pyni ha U ïa ki hima ka pyrthei baroh, bad ïa ka burom jong ki ruh;",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> bad u la ong ha U, “Kita kiei kiei baroh ngan sa ai ha me, lada men dem ban mane ïa nga.”",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Ynda kumta, U Jisu u la ong ha u, “Khie leit noh, me u Soitan: naba la thoh: “ ‘Men mane ïa U Trai uba U Blei jong me, tang ïa u hi ruh men shakri.’ ”",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Haba kumta, u Soitan u la iehnoh ïa U; ha khmih ruh, ki angel ki la ïawan bad ki la shakri ïa U.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Haba U Jisu u la ïohsngew ba la set byndi ïa u Ïoannis, u la leit noh sha Galilaïa.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Te haba u la iehnoh ïa ka Nasaret, u la wan shong sah ha Kapernam, kaba harud ka duriaw, ha ki phang ka Sabulon bad ka Naphtali:",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> ba yn pyndep ïa kata ba la ong da u Isaïah u nongïathuhlypa, u da ong,",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> “Ka ri Sabulon, bad ka ri Naphtali, shaphang ka duriaw, ha shiliang ka Jordan, ka Galilaïa ki Jentil,",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> ki briew kiba shong ha kaba dum ki la ïohi ïa ka jingshai bakhraw, bad ha kita kiba shong ha ka ri bad ha ka syrngiew ka jingïap, la mih ka jingshai.”",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Naduh kata, U Jisu u la sdang ban ïalap, bad ban ong, “To kylla-ka-bamut; naba ka hima ki bneng ka la jan.”",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Haba U Jisu u ïaid harud ka duriaw Galilaïa, u la ïohi ar ngut shipara, u Simon ïa uba khot “u Petros”, bad u Andriw u para jong u, ba ki dang ïabred ïa ka jar ha kata ka duriaw; naba ki ju long ki nongtong dohkha.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> U la ong te ha ki, “To ale nadien jong nga, te ngan pynlong ïa phi ki nongtong briew.”",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Kumta, haba ki la iehnoh dak ïa ki jar, ki la ïabud ïa u.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Te haba u la leit noh nangta, u la ïohi ar ngut kiwei pat kiba shipara, u Jakob u khun u Sebedi, bad u Ïoannis u para jong u, ha ka lieng bad u Sebedi u kpa jong ki, ba ki dang ïashna ïa ki jar jong ki, bad u la khot ïa ki.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Ki ruh de, haba ki la iehnoh dak ïa ka lieng bad ïa u kpa jong ki, ki la ïabud ïa u.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Bad U Jisu u la leit kylleng ka Galilaïa baroh, u da hikai ha ki synagog jong ki, bad u da ïalap ïa ka gospel ka hima, u da pynkhiah de ïa ki jingpang baroh bad ïa ki jingkhrew baroh ruh ha ki briew.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Te ka nam jong u ka la phriang ïa ka Syria baroh: bad ki la ïawallam ha u baroh kiba la pang, ïa kiba la ngat da ki bun jait ki jingpang bad ki jingkordit, bad ïa kiba shong ksuid, bad ïa ki bapang bhur, bad ïa ki bapang ïapshiliang de: te u la pynkhiah ïa ki.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Ki la ïabud ruh ïa u ki paidbah byllien kiba na Galilaïa bad na Dekapolis bad na Jerusalem bad na Judia bad na sha shiliang ka Jordan ruh de."
		},
		"5": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Te haba u ïohi ïa ki paidbah, u la kiew sha u lum: haba u la shong ruh, ki la ïawan ha u ki synran jong u:",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> bad haba u la ang ïa la ka shyntur u la hikai ruh ïa ki, u da ong:",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> “Suk ki baduk ha ka mynsiem: naba jong ki, long ka hima ki bneng.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> “Suk ki basngewsih: naba yn pyntngen ïa ki.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> “Suk ki bajemnud: naba kin ïaïoh ïa ka khyndew.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> “Suk ki bathngan bad ki basliang ïa ka hok: naba yn pyndap ïa ki.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> “Suk ki ba-isynei: naba yn isynei ïa ki.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> “Suk ki bakhuid ha ka dohnud: naba kin ïohi ïa U Blei.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> “Suk ki bapynïasuk: naba yn khot ïa ki, ‘ki khun U Blei.’",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> “Suk kiba ïoh pynshitom na ka bynta ka hok: naba jong ki, long ka hima ki bneng.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> “Suk ma phi haba kin ïakrenbeiñ, bad pynshitom ïa phi, bad ba kin ong ki ktien bymman baroh ruh ïa phi na ka bynta jong nga, haba ki shu lamler.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> To ïakmen, to ïashadkmen ruh: namar ka bakhraw ka bainong jong phi ha ki bneng: naba kumta ki la ïa-pynshitom ïa ki nongïathuhlypa kiba la mynshuwa jong phi.”",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> “Phi, phi long ka mluh ka pyrthei: te lada kata ka mluh ka la kylla blad, da ei yn pynbha pat ïa ka? Naduh kata, ym donkam shuh ïa ka, hynrei, tang ban bred noh shabar bad ban ïuh ïa ka hapoh ki kjat ki briew.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> “Phi, phi long ka jingshai ka pyrthei. Ym lah ban buhrieh ïa ka shnong ïa kaba la buh halor u lum.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Lymne kim ju thang ïa ka sharak, bad buh ïa ka hapoh ka shang, hynrei, ha ka dieng pynïeng sharak; te ka pynshai ïa baroh kiba ha ka ïing.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> To pynshai kumta ïa ka jingshai jong phi ha khmat ki briew, ba kin ïohi ïa ki jingleh babha jong phi bad ïoh ïaroh ruh ïa U Kpa jong phi uba ha ki bneng.”",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> “Wat mut ba nga la wan ïa ka ban pyndam noh ïa Ka Hukum lane ïa Ki Nongïathuhlypa: ngam shym la wan ïa ka ban pyndam noh, hynrei, ïa ka ban pynskhem.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Naba shisha nga ong ha phi: Ha ban da leit noh ka bneng bad ka khyndew, kat iwei i dak rit lane iwei iba khun khyndiat eh  na Ka Hukum in ym leit noh, tad ynda yn pyndep baroh.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Namar kata, uno uno ruh u ban pynkheiñ ïa iwei, wat iba kham rit tam na kine ki hukum, bad u ban hikai kumta ïa ki briew, yn khot ïa u ‘uba kham rit tam ha ka hima ki bneng:’ hynrei, uno uno ruh u ban leh bad u ban hikai ïa ki, ïa uta te yn khot ‘u bakhraw ha ka hima ki bneng.’",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Naba nga ong ha phi, ba lada ka hok jong phi kam da long kaba kham palat shikatdei ïa ka jong ki nongthoh bad ki Pharisi, phin ym ïoh rung satia ha ka hima ki bneng.”",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> “Phi la ïohsngew ba la ong ha kiba mynbarim, ‘Men ym pynïap: uno uno ruh uba pynïap, te kan dei ïa u ban hap ha ka jingbishar:’",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> hynrei, nga ong ha phi, ba uno uno ruh uba da sngewbitar ïa u paralok jong u khlem nia, kan dei ïa u ban hap ha ka jingbishar: uno uno ruh de u ban khot ïa u paralok jong u, ‘Raka’, kan dei ïa u ban hap ha ka jingbishar bah; uno uno ruh de u ban khot ïa u, ‘Me uba mutlop runar’, kan dei ïa u ban hap ha ka dujok ding.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Namar kata, lada me ainguh ïa la ka jingainguh ha ka duwan, bad hangta me da kynmaw ba u paralok jong me u don ei ei ruh ban mudui ïa me,",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> to iehnoh hangta ïa ka jingai jong me ha khmat ka duwan, to khie leit noh ruh, ba men ïasuk shuwa bad uta u paralok jong me, ynda kumta te, men sa wan ainguh ïa ka jingai jong me.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> To ïasuk noh kloi kloi ruh bad uba ïaleh bad me, katba me dang leit ha ka lynti bad u; ba ïoh kumno kumno uta uba ïaleh u ai noh ïa me ha u nongbishar, bad uta u nongbishar ruh u ai noh ïa me ha u shakri, ba yn bred ïa me ha ka byndi ruh.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Shisha nga ong ha me, men ym mih noh nangta, tad ynda me la siew ïa ka peisa ka bakhatduh.”",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> “Phi la ïohsngew ba la ong ha kiba mynbarim, ‘Men ym klim’:",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> hynrei, nga ong ha phi, ba uno uno ruh uba da khmih ïa ka briew ïa ka ban kwah ïa ka, u la lah klim lypa ïa ka kumta ha la ka dohnud.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Lada ka khmat jong me ruh kaba sha kamon ka pynjynthut ïa me, to khlaw noh ïa ka, bad to bred noh na me: naba ka myntoi ïa me ba kan duh noh kawei na ki dkhot jong me, bad ban ym bred ruh ïa ka met jong me shitylli sha dujok.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Lada ka kti kamon jong me ruh ka pynjynthut ïa me, to ot noh ïa ka, bad to bred noh na me: naba ka myntoi ïa me ba kan duh kawei na ki dkhot jong me, bad ban ym bred ruh ïa ka met jong me shitylli sha dujok.”",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> “La ong ruh, ‘Uno uno ruh u ban pyllait noh ïa ka tnga jong u, un ai ha ka, ïa ka kot iehnoh:’",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> hynrei, nga ong ha phi, ba uno uno ruh u ban pyllait noh ïa ka tnga jong u, lymda tang na ka bynta kaba klim, u pynklim ïa ka: uno uno ruh u ban shongkurim bad kaba la iehnoh, u ruh u klim.”",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> “Phi la ïohsngew pat ba la ong ha kiba mynbarim, ‘Men ym smai lamler, hynrei, men ai ha U Trai ïa ki jingsmai jong me.’",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> Hynrei, nga ong ha phi: Wat smai satia, lymne ha ka bneng, naba ka long ka khet U Blei;",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> lymne ha ka khyndew, naba ka long ka jingïuh kjat jong U; lymne ha ka Jerusalem, naba ka long ka nongbah U Syiem Bakhraw.",
			"36": "<sup>36</sup> Lymne men ym smai ha ka khlieh jong me, naba mem lah ban pynlieh lymne pynïong ïa iwei i shñiuh.",
			"37": "<sup>37</sup> Hynrei, ka ktien jong phi to ai ba kan long kaba, ‘Ho-oid, Ho-oid’; kaba, ‘Em, Em’: naba, kaba tam na kita ka long na ka basniew.”",
			"38": "<sup>38</sup> “Phi la ïohsngew ba la ong, ‘Ka khmat namar ka khmat, ka bniat ruh namar ka bniat’:",
			"39": "<sup>39</sup> hynrei, nga ong ha phi, wat ïeng ïaleh markylliang ïa u basniew: hynrei, mano mano ruh uba thab ïa me ha ka ngab kamon jong me, to pynphai sha u ïa kawei pat ruh.",
			"40": "<sup>40</sup> Uba imon ruh ban tian bishar ïa me, bad ban shim noh ïa ka sopti jong me, to iehnoh ha u ïa ka jaiñkup jong me ruh.",
			"41": "<sup>41</sup> Mano mano ruh u ban pynïaid ïa me shilynter, to khie leit lem bad u ar lynter.",
			"42": "<sup>42</sup> To ai ha uta uba pan na me, bad na uta uba mon ban pan kylliang na me, to wat phai noh.”",
			"43": "<sup>43</sup> “Phi la ïohsngew ba la ong, ‘Men ieit ïa la u paramarjan, men shun ruh ïa uba shun ïa me.’",
			"44": "<sup>44</sup> Hynrei, nga ong ha phi, to ieit ïa ki nongshun jong phi, bad to kyrkhu ïa kiba tim ïa phi, to leh bha ïa kiba shun ïa phi, to duwai ruh na ka bynta kiba leh sniew ïa phi, bad lehbeiñ ruh ïa phi;",
			"45": "<sup>45</sup> ba phin ïoh long ki khun U Kpa jong phi uba ha bneng: naba u pynmih ïa ka sngi jong u ha ki basniew bad ha ki babha, u phah ruh ïa u slap ha ki bahok bad ha ki bymhok.",
			"46": "<sup>46</sup> Naba, lada phi shu ieit ïa kiba ieit ïa phi, phi ïohnong aïu? Hato ki nongkhrong kim leh kumjuh?",
			"47": "<sup>47</sup> Lada phi nguh ruh tang ïa ki kur jong phi, phi leh kaba kham kor aïu? hato ki nongkhrong kim leh kumjuh?",
			"48": "<sup>48</sup> Namar kata, phin ïalong kiba janai, kumba U Kpa jong phi uba ha bneng u long uba janai.”"
		},
		"6": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> “To sumar ban ym leh ïa ka babha jong phi ha khmat ki briew, khnang ba kin khmih ïa phi: lymda kumta, phim don nong ha U Kpa jong phi uba ha bneng.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> “Namar kata, haba me leh ka jingai isynei, wat put ka ronsing ha shuwa jong me, kumba leh ki nongarsap ha ki synagog bad ha ki lynti shnong, ba kin ïoh burom na ki briew. Shisha nga ong ha phi, ki la ïoh ïa la ka nong.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Hynrei, me, haba me da leh ka jingai isynei, wat ai ba ka kti kadiang jong me kan tip aïu ba ka leh ka kti kamon jong me;",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> ba kata ka jingai isynei jong me kan ïoh long ha kaba rieh: bad U Kpa jong me uba ïohi ha kaba rieh un ai nong ha me ha kaba paw.”",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> “Haba me duwai ruh, wat long kum ki nongarsap: naba ki ieit ban ïeng kyrpad ha ki synagog bad ha ki dong ki lad, ba kin ïoh pynpaw ha ki briew. Shisha nga ong ha phi, ki la ïoh ïa la ka nong.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Hynrei, me, haba me duwai, to leit rung sha la ka pulit, bad haba me la khang ïa la ka jingkhang, to kyrpad ïa U Kpa jong me uba ha kaba rieh; te U Kpa jong me uba ïohi ha kaba rieh un ai nong ha me ha kaba paw.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> “Bad haba phi duwai, wat bun ktien bieit kum ki Jentil: naba ki ïamut ba yn sngew ïa ki namar kaba bun ktien jong ki.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Namar kata, wat long kum kita: naba U Kpa jong phi u tip ïa kaei ruh ba phi donkam, mynshuwa ba phin pan na u.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Namar kata, phin duwai kumne: “Ko Kpa jong ngi uba ha bneng, long bakhuid ka kyrteng jong me.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Wan ka hima jong me. Long ka mon jong me ha ka khyndew, kumba ha bneng.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> To ai ha ngi mynta ka jingbam jong ngi kaba ha la ka sngi ka sngi.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> To map ruh ïa ngi ïa ki ryngkang jong ngi, kumba ngi ruh ngi map ïa kiba leh sniew ïa ngi.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> To wat ïalam ïa ngi sha ka jingpynshoi ruh, hynrei, sumar ïa ngi na ka basniew. Naba ka jong me long ka hima, bad ka bor, bad ka burom ruh, ha la ka rta: Amen.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> “Naba lada phi map ïa ki briew ïa ki ryngkang jong ki, U Kpa jong phi uba ha bneng un map ruh ïa phi:",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> hynrei, lada phim map ïa ki briew ïa ki ryngkang jong ki, U Kpa jong phi ruh un ym map ïa ki ryngkang jong phi.”",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> “Haba phi shah jingit ruh, wat long kiba 'matsngewsih kum ki nongarsap; naba ki pynkynriang ïa ki khmat jong ki, ba kin pynpaw ha ki briew ba ki shah jingit. Shisha nga ong ha phi, ki la ïoh ïa la ka nong.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Hynrei, me, haba me shah jingit, to sleh ïa la ka khlieh, bad bta ïa la ka khmat;",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> ba kumta men ym pynpaw ha ki briew ba me shah jingit, hynrei, ha U Kpa jong me uba ha kaba rieh; bad U Kpa jong me uba ïohi ha kaba rieh un ai nong ha me ha kaba paw.”",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> “Wat kynshew ki spah ïa lade ha ka khyndew, ha kaba bam ka khñiang bad ka sarang, bad sha kaba ki nongtuh ki pynpei, ki tuh ruh:",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> hynrei, phin kynshew ki spah ïa lade ha bneng, ha kaba kam bam lymne ka khñiang lymne ka sarang, bad sha kaba ki nongtuh kim pynpei lymne kim tuh:",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> naba ha kaba long ka spah jong phi, hangta ruh kan long ka dohnud jong phi.”",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> “Ka khmat ka long ka sharak ka met: namar kata, lada ka khmat jong me ka long sngur, ka met jong me baroh kan shai bha.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Hynrei, lada ka khmat jong me ka long jngut, ka met jong me baroh kan long dum. Namar kata, lada ka jingshai kaba ha me ka long dum, kata kaba dum kaba katno!”",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> “Ym don uba lah ban shakri ar ngut ki kynrad; naba un isih ïa uwei, bad un ieit ïa uwei; lane un bat ïa uwei, bad un lyndet ïa uwei. Phim lah ban shakri ïa U Blei bad ïa ka spah.”",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> “Namar kata, nga ong ha phi, wat khuslai ïa la ka jingim, kaei ba phin bam, lane kaei ba phin dih; lymne ïa ka met jong phi, kaei ba phin kup. Ka jingim kam long kaba kham kor ïa ka jingbam, ka met ruh ïa ka jaiñkup?",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> To khmih thuh ïa ki sim bneng, ba kim ïabet, lymne kim ïa-ot, lymne kim ïalum ha ki thiar; hynrei, pynban, U Kpa jong phi uba ha bneng u bsa ïa ki. Phi te phim long kiba kham kor shibun ïa ki?",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Uno te na phi, haba u da khuslai ruh, uba lah ban pyntam shi pruh ïa la ka rynïeng?",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Balei ba phi khuslai shaphang kaba kup ruh? To pyrkhat ïa ki 'tiew Lili ka ryngkew, katno ki man bha; kim trei, lymne kim thir;",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> hynrei, nga ong ha phi, ba wat u Solomon ha ka burom jong u baroh um shym la kup kum uwei na kine.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Lada U Blei te u pynkup kumta ïa u 'hur ryngkew, uba mynta u long, lashai te la bred ha ka lawar ding, kaba katno tam ïa phi, A phi kiba rit ka jingngeit!",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Namar kata, wat khuslai, da kaba ong, ‘Kaei ba ngin bam?’ lane, ‘Kaei ba ngin dih?’ lane, ‘Kaei ba ngin kup?’",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> naba ïa kita kiei kiei baroh, ki Jentil ki ïawad; naba U Kpa jong phi uba ha bneng u tip ba phi donkam ïa kine kiei kiei baroh.",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Hynrei, phin ïawad shuwa ïa ka hima U Blei, bad ïa ka hok jong u: te ïa kine kiei kiei baroh, yn sa ai lang tam ha phi.",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> “Namar kata, wat khuslai na ka bynta kaba lashai, naba kata kaba lashai kan khuslai na ka bynta la ka jong. Ïa ka sngi ka biang la ka jong ka basniew.”"
		},
		"7": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> “Wat bishar, ba yn ym bishar ïa phi.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Naba da ka jingbishar ba phi bishar, yn bishar ïa phi: bad da ka jingthew ba phi thew, yn thew pat ïa phi.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Balei ruh ba me khmih ïa u thngiat uba ha ka khmat u paralok jong me, hynrei, mem sngew ïa ka khung kaba ha ka khmat jong me hi?",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Lane kumno ba me ong ha u paralok jong me, ‘To shah ba ngan khlaw noh ïa u thngiat na ka khmat jong me;’ ha khmih ruh, ka khung ka don ha ka khmat jong me hi?",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Me uba arsap! khlaw noh shuwa ïa ka khung na ka khmat jong me hi; kumta te men ïohi bha ban khlaw noh ïa u thngiat na ka khmat u paralok jong me.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> “Wat ai ïa ka bakhuid ha ki ksew, lymne wat bred ïa ki mawlynnai jong phi ha khmat ki sniang, ba ïoh kin ïuh ïa ki hapoh ki kjat jong ki, bad kin phai pat, kin tar ruh ïa phi.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> “To pan, te yn sa ai ha phi; to wad, te phin sa shem; to tied, te yn sa plie ïa phi.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Naba baroh uba pan, u pdiang; bad uba wad, u shem; bad ïa uba tied, yn plie.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Lane uei u briew uba na phi, lada u khun jong u un pan ïa u kpu, u ban ai da u maw ha u;",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> lane lada un pan ïa ka dohkha, un ai da u bseiñ ha u?",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Namar kata, lada phi, kiba long bymman, phi tip ïa ka ban ai ïa ki jingai babha ha ki khun jong phi, kaba katno tam ba U Kpa jong phi uba ha bneng un ai ïa kiei kiei ruh ki babha ha kita kiba pan na u?",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> “Namar kata, ïa kiei kiei baroh kiba phi ïamon ba ki briew kin leh ha phi, kumta, to leh ma phi ruh ha ki: naba kane ka long Ka Hukum bad Ki Nongïathuhlypa.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> “To bsut lyngba ïa ka khyrdop bakhim: naba ka kylluid ka khyrdop, kaba jlan ruh ka lynti, kaba lam sha ka ban jot; bun ruh kiba ïabsut na kata.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Hynrei, A kaba khim kata ka khyrdop; A kaba wit ruh kata ka lynti kaba lam sha ka ban im! A ki long khyndiat ruh kiba shem ïa kata!",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> “To sumar na ki nongïathuhlypa balamler, kiba ïawan ha phi ha ki jaiñkup snieh langbrot, hynrei, hapoh ki long ki suri bapynjot.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Na ki soh jong ki phin ithuh ïa ki. Ki briew ki ju kheit ïa ki soh Waiñ na ki dieng shiah, lane ïa ki soh Dumbur na ki ñiut shiah?",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Kumta, u dieng babha baroh u sei ki soh babha; hynrei, u dieng bymman u sei ki soh bymman.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> U dieng babha um lah ban sei ki soh bymman, lymne u dieng bymman um lah ban sei ki soh babha.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Ïa u dieng baroh u bymsei ki soh babha yn khet noh, yn bred ruh ïa u ha ka ding.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Naba kumta, na ki soh jong ki phin ithuh ïa ki.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> “Ym u briew baroh uba ong ha nga, ‘A Trai, A Trai’, u ban ïoh leit hapoh ka hima ki bneng; hynrei, uta keiñ uba leh ïa ka mon U Kpa jong nga uba ha bneng.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Shibun kin ïa-ong ha nga ha kata ka sngi, ‘A Trai, A Trai, ngi ngim shym la ïalap ha ka kyrteng jong me? Ngi ngim shym la beh noh ïa ki ksuid ha ka kyrteng jong me? Ngi ngim shym la leh shibun ki kambah ruh ha ka kyrteng jong me?’",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Ynda kumta te, nga ruh ngan ong pyrshah ha ki: Ngam ju la ithuh ïa phi; khie leit noh na nga, phi kiba ju trei bymman.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> “Te mano mano baroh uba sngew ïa kine ki ktien jong nga, bad uba leh ïa ki, ngan tharai ïa u kum u briew u bastad, uba la tei ïa ka ïing jong u halor u mawsiang:",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> te u slap u la hap, bad ki wah ki la ïashlei, bad ki lyer ki la ïabeh, bad ki la shoh ïa kata ka ïing; te kam shym la kyllon noh: naba la pynshong nongrim ïa ka halor u mawsiang.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Hynrei, mano mano baroh uba sngew ïa kine ki ktien jong nga, bad u bymleh ïa ki, yn tharai ïa u kum u briew ba-bieit, uba la tei ïa ka ïing jong u halor u shyiap:",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> u slap te u la hap, bad ki wah ki la ïashlei, bad ki lyer ki la ïabeh, bad ki la shoh ïa kata ka ïing; te ka la kyllon: bad ka jingkyllon jong ka, ka la long kaba khraw.”",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Ka la jia ruh, haba U Jisu u la wai noh ïa kine ki ktien, ba kita ki paidbah ki la ïasngewkyndit thred na ka jinghikai jong u:",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> naba u la hikai ïa ki kum uba don bor, bym kum ki nongthoh te."
		},
		"8": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Te haba U la wan hiar na u lum, ki paidbah babun ki la ïabud ïa U.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Ha khmih ruh, u bapang 'ñiangthohlieh u la wan, bad u la mane dem ïa U, u da ong, “Ko Kynrad, lada me mon, me lah ban pynkhuid ïa nga.”",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> U Jisu te u la kner ïa la ka kti, bad U la ktah ïa u, U da ong, “Nga mon; to men long khuid.” Kumne kumne ruh la pynkhuid ïa u na kata ka pang 'ñiangthohlieh jong u.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> U Jisu u la ong ruh ha u, “To sumar wat ïathuh hano hano ruh; hynrei, khie leit noh, to pyni ïa lade ha u lyngdoh, to ainguh ruh ïa ka jingai ïa kaba u Moses u la hukum, ïa ka ban long ka jingphla ïa ki.”",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Haba U Jisu u la poi ha Kapernam, u rangbah shispah u la wan ha U, bad u la kyrpad ïa U,",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> u da ong, “Ko Kynrad, u shakri jong nga u thiah ha ïing ba u pang ïapshiliang, u da kordit eh.”",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Te U Jisu u la ong ha u, “Ngan sa wan pynkhiah ïa u.”",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Uta u rangbah shispah te u la ïathuh bad u la ong, “Ko Kynrad, ngam long uba dei ba men wan rung hapoh ka ïing jong nga: hynrei, shu ong tang da ka ktien, te yn sa pynkhiah ïa u shakri jong nga:",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> naba nga ruh nga long u briew hapoh ka hukum, uba don ki shipai hapoh jong nga; te nga ong ha une, ‘Khie leit’, te u leit; bad ha uwei pat, ‘Ale’, u ruh u wan; bad ha u shakri jong nga, ‘Leh ïa kane’, u ruh u leh.”",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Te haba U Jisu u la ïohsngew, u la kyndit, bad u la ong ha kita kiba bud, “Shisha nga ong ha phi, wat ha Israel, ngam shym la shem kat kane ka jingngeit.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Nga ong ruh ha phi, ba shibun kin ïawan na mihngi bad na sepngi, bad kin ïashong shaniah lem bad u Abraham, bad u Isaak, bad u Jakob ruh, ha ka hima ki bneng:",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> hynrei, ïa ki khun ka hima yn shop noh sha ka ba-dum jngai bah: hangta yn long kaba lynñiar, bad kum dait bniat.”",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Bad U Jisu u la ong ha uta u rangbah shispah, “To khie leit noh; kat kumba me la ngeit, kan long ruh ïa me.” Te ha kata hi ka por la pynkhiah ïa u shakri jong u.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Haba U Jisu u la wan ha ka ïing u Petros, U la ïohi ïa ka syngken kurim jong u ba ka da thiah, bad ba ka da khieshoh.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Bad U la ktah ïa ka kti jong ka, te kata ka khieshoh ka la iehnoh ïa ka; te ka la ïeng, bad ka la shakri ïa U.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Ynda la janmiet ruh, ki la ïawallam ha U shibun kiba shong ksuid; te U la beh noh ïa ki mynsiem da ka ktien, bad U la pynkhiah ïa ki bapang baroh:",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> ba kumta yn pyndep ïa kata ba la ong da u Isaïah u nongïathuhlypa, u da ong, “U hi u la shimti ïa ki jingkhrew jong ngi, bad u la bah noh ïa ki jingpang jong ngi.”",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Te haba U Jisu u la ïohi ïa ki paidbah babun sawdong jong u, u la hukum ban leit noh sha shiliang.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Te haba uwei u nongthoh u la wan, u la ong ha U, “Ko Nonghikai, ngan bud ïa me kat shaba me leit.”",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> U Jisu te u la ong ha u, “Ki myrsiang ki don ki thliew, bad ki sim bneng ki jaka rieh: hynrei, U Khun u briew um don jaka ban buh ïa la ka khlieh.”",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Uwei pat ruh na ki synran jong U, u la ong ha U, “Ko Trai, to shah ba ngan leit shuwa ban tep ïa la u kpa.”",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Hynrei, U Jisu u la ong ha u, “Bud ïa nga; bad ieh ïa ki baïap ban tep ïa ki baïap jong ki.”",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Te haba u la kiew ha ka lieng, ki synran jong u ki la ïabud ïa u.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Ha khmih ruh, ka jingkhih phaloh kaba khraw ka la mih ha ka duriaw, kat ban tyllep ïa kata ka lieng da ki jingat phyllung; hynrei, u la ïohthiah.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Te haba ki synran jong u ki la ïawan ha u, ki la kyrsiew ïa u, ki ïa-ong, “Ko Kynrad, to pynim ïa ngi; ngin sa ïap!”",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> U te u la ong ha ki, “Balei ba phi long kiba sheptieng, A phi kiba rit jingngeit?” Ynda kumta, u la khie, u la sneng ïa ka lyer bad ïa ka duriaw ruh; te ka la long kaba jai jai eh.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Kita ki briew te ki la kyndit, ki ïa-ong, “Uba kumno une, ba ki lyer ruh bad ka duriaw ki ïakohnguh ïa u!”",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Te haba u la wan sha shiliang sha ka ri ki Gadara, la ïawan tan ïa u ar ngut kiba shong ksuid, kiba da mih noh na ki maw jingtep, kiba runar eh, katba ym don uba shlan ban leit na kata ka lynti.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Ha khmih ruh, ki la ïapyrta noh, ki da ong, “Me donkam aïu bad ngi, ko Jisu, U Khun U Blei? me la wan shane mynshuwa ka aïom ban pynkordit ïa ngi?”",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Hynrei, la don kham jngai na ki, shi kynhun bah ki sniang, kiba ïabam phlang.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Kita ki ksuid te ki la ïakyrpad ïa u, ki da ong, “Lada me beh noh ïa ngi, to ai ïa ngi ban leit noh ha kato ka shi kynhun ki sniang.”",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> U la ong te ha ki, “To khie leit.” Te haba ki la ïamih noh, ki la ïaleit ha kata ka shi kynhun ki sniang; ha khmih ruh, kata ka shi kynhun ki sniang baroh ki la ïaphet ïap arsut ïa ka riat sha ka duriaw, bad ki la ïap noh ha ki um.",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Te kita kiba ïa-ap ïa ki, ki la ïaphet noh; bad haba ki la ïapoi ha kata ka shnong, ki la ïathuh ïa kiei kiei baroh, bad ïa kaba la jia ha kita kiba shong ksuid ruh.",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> Ha khmih ruh, kata ka shnong baroh ka la mih ïa ka ban shem ïa U Jisu; te haba ki la ïohi ïa u, ki la ïaduwai ba un leit noh na ki phang jong ki."
		},
		"9": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Te haba u la kiew ha ka lieng, u la leit sha shiliang, bad u la poi ha la ka shnong.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Ha khmih ruh, ki la ïawallam ha u ïa u bapang ïapshiliang, uba thiah ha ka jingthiah: te haba U Jisu u la ïohi ïa ka jingngeit jong ki, u la ong ha uta u bapang ïapshiliang, “To kyrmen, ko khun; la map noh ïa me ïa ki pop jong me.”",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Ha khmih ruh, kiba na ki nongthoh ki la ïa-ong ha lade, “Une u krenbeiñ Blei.”",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Te U Jisu ba u da tip ïa ki jingmut jong ki, u la ong, “Na ka balei ba phi ïamut bymman ha ki dohnud jong phi?",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> naba kano kaba kham jem, ban ong, ‘La map ïa ki pop jong me;’ lane ban ong, ‘To ïeng, to ïaid ruh?’",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Hynrei, ba phin ïoh tip ba U Khun u briew u don bor ha ka khyndew ban map ïa ki pop,” (hangta u la ong ha uta u bapang ïapshiliang), “To ïeng, to rah noh ïa la ka jingthiah, to khie leit ruh sha la ïing.”",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Te haba u la ïeng, u la leit sha la ïing.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Ki paidbah te haba ki la ïohi ïa kata, ki la ïakyndit, bad ki la ïaroh ïa U Blei, uba la ai bor kum kata ha ki briew.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Haba U Jisu te u la ïaid noh nangta, u la ïohi ïa u briew, ïa uba la khot “Mathaïos”, uba shong ha ka ïing khrong; U ong te ha u, “To bud ïa nga.” Te haba u la ïeng, u la bud ïa U.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Ka la jia ruh, haba U la shong bam ha ka ïing uta, ha khmih te, bun ki nongkhrong bad ki bapop ki la ïawan shong shaniah lem bad U Jisu bad ki synran jong U.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Haba ki Pharisi te ki la ïohi, ki la ïa-ong ha ki synran jong U, “Balei ba U Nonghikai jong phi u ïabam lem bad ki nongkhrong bad ki bapop ruh?”",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Te haba U Jisu u la ïohsngew, u la ong ha ki, “Ki bakhiah kim donkam ïa u nongpynkhiah, hynrei, ki bapang keiñ;",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> hynrei, khie leit ma phi to hikai kaei kane, ‘Ïa ka jingisynei nga mon, te ym ïa ka jingkñia:’ naba ngam shym la wan ban khot ïa ki bahok, hynrei, ïa ki bapop ïa ka ban kylla-ka-bamut.”",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Ynda kumta, ki la ïawan ha u ki synran u Ïoannis, ki da ong, “Balei ba ngi bad ki Pharisi ngi ïashah jingit bunsien, ki synran jong me te kim ïashah jingit?”",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> U Jisu te u la ïathuh ha ki, “Ki nong-on kurim ki lah ban sngewsih, haba u dang sah bad ki u nongleit-kurim? Hynrei, kin poi ki sngi, ynda yn shim noh na ki, ïa u nongleit-kurim, hangta te kin sa ïashah jingit.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Ym don ruh uba suh syrdep ïa ka jaiñkup barim da ka jaiñ thymmai; naba kata ka jaiñsyrdep hi ka pynkad na ka jong kata ka jaiñkup, ka pynlong ruh ïa ka jingkad kaba kham khraw:",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> lymne kim ju ïabuh ïa ka Waiñ thymmai ha ki lywa snieh barim; lymda kumta, kita ki lywa snieh ki pdang, te ka jaw noh kata ka Waiñ, bad kita ki lywa snieh ki jot noh: hynrei, ki ïabuh ïa ka Waiñ thymmai ha ki lywa snieh thymmai, ba kin ïabha baroh ar.”",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Haba u dang ong ïa kine kiei kiei ruh ha ki, ha khmih, la wan uwei u rangbah, bad u la mane dem ïa U, u da ong, “Ka khun jong nga katta ka la ïap; hynrei to da wan buh ïa ka kti jong me ha ka, te kan sa im.”",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> U Jisu te haba u la ïeng, U la bud ïa u, lem bad ki synran jong U de.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Ha khmih ruh, ka briew kaba la pang mihsnam khat-ar snem, ka la wan hajan na shadien, bad ka la ktah ïa ka rmiang ka jaiñkup jong U;",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> naba ka la ong ha lade, “Lada ngan shu ïoh ktah tang ïa ka jaiñkup jong U, ngan sa khiah.”",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> U Jisu te haba u la phai, bad u la ïohi ïa ka, u la ong, “To kyrmen, ko ka khun; ka jingngeit jong pha ka la pynkhiah ïa pha.” Kata ka kynthei te ka la khiah naduh kata ka por.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Te haba U Jisu u la poi ha ïing uta u rangbah, bad ba U la ïohi ïa ki duhalia, bad ïa ki paidbah ba ïambriew,",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> u la ong ha ki, “To kynriah noh; naba ka khynnah kam shym la ïap, hynrei, ka ïohthiah.” Ki te, ki la rkhiebeiñ ïa u.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Hynrei, haba la pynmih noh ïa u paidbah, U la leit hapoh, bad U la bat ïa ka na ka kti; te kata ka khynnah ka la ïeng.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Ka jingbna ïa kata te ka la leit kylleng ha kata ka ri baroh.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Te haba U Jisu u la leit noh nangta, ki la ïabud ïa u ar ngut ki bamatlah, ki da kyrpad, ki da ong ruh, “To isynei ïa ngi, ko Khun u Dabid.”",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Haba u la wan hapoh ïing te, kita ki bamatlah ki la ïawan ha u; te U Jisu u la ong ha ki, “Phi ngeit ba nga lah ban leh ïa kane?” Ki la ong ha u, “Ho-oid, ko Trai.”",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Ynda kumta, u la ktah ïa ki khmat jong ki, u da ong, “Katba kum ka jingngeit jong phi kan long ha phi.”",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Ïa ki khmat jong ki te la pynpeit. U Jisu te u la maham ïa ki, u da ong, “To sumar ban ym tip mano mano ruh.”",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Hynrei, haba ki la ïaleit noh, ki la ïa-pynbna ïa u ha kata ka ri baroh.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Haba ki dang ïamih noh ruh nangta, ha khmih, ki la ïawallam ha u ïa u briew u bymnangkren uba shong ksuid.",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Te haba U la beh noh ïa uta u ksuid, uta u bymnangkren u la kren; ki paidbah te ki la ïakyndit, ki da ong, “Mynno mynno ruh ym ju paw kumne ha Israel!”",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> Hynrei, ki Pharisi ki la ïa-ong, “U beh noh ïa ki ksuid da u rangbah ki ksuid.”",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> U Jisu u la ïaid ruh kylleng sha ki nongbah bad ki nongrit baroh, u da hikai ha ki synagog jong ki, bad u da ïalap ïa ka gospel ka jong ka hima, bad u da pynkhiah ïa ka jingpang baroh bad ïa ka jingkhrew baroh de.",
			"36": "<sup>36</sup> Bad haba u la ïohi ïa ki paidbah, u la sngewsynei namar jong ki, naba ki long kiba la sakma bad kiba la saphred ruh, kum ki langbrot ki bymdon u nongsharai.",
			"37": "<sup>37</sup> Ynda kumta, u la ong ha ki synran jong u, “Ka jingot kaba bun shisha, hynrei, ki nongtrei ki khyndiat;",
			"38": "<sup>38</sup> namar kata, to kyrpad ïa U Trai ka jingot, ba un phah noh ïa ki nongtrei sha ka jingot jong u.”"
		},
		"10": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Te haba u la khot ha lade ïa ki khat-ar ngut ki synran jong u, u la ai bor ïa ki halor ki mynsiem bymkhuid kat ban beh noh ïa ki, bad ban pynkhiah ïa ka jingpang baroh bad ïa ka jingkhrew baroh.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Ki kyrteng jong kita ki khat-ar ngut ki apostol te ki la long kine: u banyngkong, u Simon, ïa uba la khot “u Petros”, bad u Andriw u para jong u; u Jakob u khun u Sebedi, bad u Ïoannis u para jong u;",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> u Philip, bad u Bartholomai; u Thomas, bad u Mathaïos u nongkhrong; u Jakob u khun u Alphaïos, bad u Lebbaïos, ïa uba ki sin “Thaddaïos”,",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> u Simon u Bashitrhem, bad u Judas Iskariot, uba la die noh ïa U ruh.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Ïa kine ki khat-ar ngut, U Jisu u la phah noh, bad u la hukum ïa ki, u da ong, “Wat leit ha ka lynti ki Jentil, ha ka shnong ki kynja Samaria ruh phi wat rung.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Hynrei, phin kham ïaleit ha kita ki langbrot kiba la jah noh na ka ïing Israel.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Katba phi ïaid ruh, to ïalap, da ong, ‘Ka hima ki bneng ka la jan.’",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> To pynkhiah ïa ki bapang, to pynkhuid ïa ki bapang 'ñiangthohlieh, to pynim pat ïa ki baïap, to beh noh ïa ki ksuid: phi la pdiang ei, phin ïa-ai ei.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Wat ïabuh lypa ïa ka ksiar, lymne ka rupa, lymne ka rnong, ha ki 'saipan jong phi;",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> lymne ka ïarong ïa ka lynti, lymne ar tylli ki jingphong, lymne ki juti, lymne u diengduh; naba ka dei ïa u nongtrei ban ïoh la ka bam.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Sha kano kano ka nongbah lane ka nongrit ba phin leit rung, to wad uei ha kata uba bit nam; te hangta phin ïaishong tad ynda phi mih noh.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Haba phi leit hapoh ka ïing ruh, phin khublei ïa ka.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Lada kata ka ïing ruh ka long kaba bit shisha, ai ba ka jingsuk jong phi kan wan ha kata; hynrei, lada kam long kaba bit, ai ba ka jingsuk jong phi kan wan phai pat ha phi.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Lada uno uno ruh un ym pdiang ïa phi, lymne sngew ruh ïa ki ktien jong phi, haba phi mih noh na kata ka ïing lane na kata ka shnong, to ïakynther noh ïa ka 'dewmet na ki kjat jong phi.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Shisha nga ong ha phi, ba kan long kham jem ïa ka ri Sodom bad Gomorra ha ka sngi bishar ban ïa kaba kan long ïa kata ka shnong.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> “Ha khmih, nga phah noh ïa phi kum ki langbrot hapdeng ki suri; namar kata, phin ïalong ki basian kum ki bseiñ, bad ki bajemnud kum ki paro.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Hynrei, to ïasumar na ki briew, naba kin ïa-ai noh ïa phi ha ki jingbishar, bad kin ïasympat ïa phi ha ki synagog jong ki;",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> yn ïalam ruh ïa phi ha khmat ki lyngskor bad ki syiem na ka bynta jong nga, ïa ka ban long ka jingphla ha ki bad ha ki Jentil.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Hynrei, ynda ki ïa-ai noh ïa phi, wat sngewkhuslai, kumno, lane kaei ba phin kren; naba yn ai ha phi ha kata ka por, ïa kaei ba phin kren.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Naba ym dei ma phi kiba kren, hynrei, U Mynsiem U Kpa jong phi uba kren ha phi.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> U para te un ai noh ïa la u para ïa ka ban ïap, u kpa ruh ïa la ki khun: ki khun ruh kin ïeng ïaleh ïa ki kmie ki kpa, bad kin ïa-pynïap ruh ïa ki.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Te phin long ïa kiba la shun da ki briew baroh na ka bynta ka kyrteng jong nga: hynrei, uta uba da ïaineh ha ban da kut, uta keiñ u ban lait im.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Hynrei, haba ki ïabehbeiñ ïa phi ha kawei ka shnong, to ïaphet sha kawei pat: naba shisha nga ong ha phi, ba phin ym pat lah pyndep ïa ki shnong ki Israel, tad ynda un wan U Khun u briew.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> “U synran um long halor u nonghikai, lymne u shakri halor u kynrad jong u.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> La biang ïa u synran ba un long kum u nonghikai jong u, ïa u shakri ruh kum u kynrad jong u. Lada ki la khot ‘Belsebul’ ïa u trai ïing, kaba katno tam ba kin ïakhot sin ïa kita kiba na ka ïing jong u!",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> “Namar kata, to wat sheptieng ïa ki: naba ym don kaei kaei ruh ba la tap, ïa kaba yn ym pynpaw; bad ba la buhrieh, ïa ka ban ym pyntip.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Ïa kaba nga ong ha phi ha ka ba-dum, to ïathuh ha ka bashai: bad ïa kaba phi ïohsngew da ka shkor, to phin ïalap nalor ïing.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> To wat sheptieng te ïa kita kiba pynïap ïa ka met, bad ki bym lah ban pynïap ïa ka mynsiem: hynrei, phin kham sheptieng ïa uta uba lah ban pynjot bad ïa ka mynsiem bad ïa ka met ha dujok.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Kim ju die ar peisa ïa ki ar tylli ki sim ïing? hynrei, na kita, kawei kam hap ha khyndew khlem U Kpa jong phi.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Wat ïa u 'ñiuh khlieh jong phi baroh ruh la ñiew.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Namar kata, to wat sheptieng; phi long kham kor ïa ki shibun ki sim ïing.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> “Uno uno baroh te u ban phla ïa nga ha khmat ki briew, nga ruh ngan phla ïa u ha khmat U Kpa jong nga uba ha bneng.",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Hynrei, uno uno ruh u ban len ïa nga ha khmat ki briew, nga ruh ngan len ïa u ha khmat U Kpa jong nga uba ha bneng.",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> “Wat mut ba nga la wan ban buh ka jingsuk ha ka pyrthei: ngam shym la wan ban buh ka jingsuk, hynrei, ka wait.",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> Naba nga la wan ba u briew un ïaleh bad la u kpa, ka khun ruh bad la ka kmie, ka pyrsa kurim ruh bad la ka syngken kurim.",
			"36": "<sup>36</sup> Bad ki nongshun u briew kin long kiba na ïing jong u hi.",
			"37": "<sup>37</sup> Uta uba ieit ïa u kpa lane ka kmie nalor jong nga, ym dei ïa u ban ïoh ïa nga; bad uta uba ieit ïa u khun lane ïa ka khun nalor jong nga, ym dei ïa u ban ïoh ïa nga.",
			"38": "<sup>38</sup> Bad uta u bym shim ïa la ka diengphna bad bud nadien jong nga, ym dei ïa u ban ïoh ïa nga.",
			"39": "<sup>39</sup> Uta uba shem ïa la ka jingim un duh noh ïa ka; bad uta uba duh noh ïa la ka jingim na ka bynta jong nga un shem ïa ka.",
			"40": "<sup>40</sup> “Uta uba pdiang ïa phi u pdiang ïa nga; uta te uba pdiang ïa nga u pdiang ïa uta uba la phah ïa nga.",
			"41": "<sup>41</sup> Uta uba pdiang ïa u nongïathuhlypa ha ka kyrteng u nongïathuhlypa un ïoh ïa ka nong u nongïathuhlypa; bad uta uba pdiang ïa u riewhok ha ka kyrteng u riewhok un ïoh ïa ka nong u riewhok.",
			"42": "<sup>42</sup> Bad uno uno ruh u ban ai dih tang shi khuri ka um khriat ïa uwei na kine ki barit, ha ka kyrteng u synran, shisha nga ong ha phi, un ym duh shuh la ka nong.”"
		},
		"11": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Ka la jia ruh, haba U Jisu u la wai noh kaba hukum ïa ki khat-ar ngut ki synran jong u, ba u la leit noh nangta ïa ka ban hikai bad ban ïalap ha ki shnong jong ki.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Te haba u Ïoannis u la ïohsngew ha ka byndi shaphang ki jingleh U Khrist, u la phah da ki synran jong u,",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> bad u la kylli ha U, “Me long uta u ban sa wan, ne ngin ïa-ap ïa uwei pat?”",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> U Jisu te u la ïathuh bad u la ong ha ki, “To khie leit ïathuh ha u Ïoannis ïa kiei kiei ruh kiba phi ïohsngew bad ba phi ïohi ruh:",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Ki bamatlah ki peit pat, ki ba-dkoh ruh ki ïaid, la pynkhuid ïa ki bapang 'ñiangthohlieh, ki bakyllut ruh ki ïohsngew, la pynim pat ïa ki nongïap, bad la ïalap ïa ka gospel ha ki baduk ruh:",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> suk ruh ma u, u ban ym thut ha nga.”",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Te haba kita ki dang ïaleit noh, U Jisu u la sdang ban ong ha kita ki paidbah shaphang u Ïoannis: “Phi la leit sha ka ri khlaw ban jngoh aïu? ïa u phlang ba la pynkhih da ka lyer?",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Hynrei, phi la leit ban ïohi aïu? ïa u briew ba la kup ki jaiñ bani? ha khmih, kita kiba kup ki jaiñ bani ki long ha ki ïingsyiem.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Hynrei, phi la mih noh ban ïohi aïu? ïa u nongïathuhlypa? shisha, nga ong ha phi, ïa uba kham khraw ïa u nongïathuhlypa.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Naba une u long uta ba la thoh shaphang jong u: “ ‘Ha khmih, nga phah ïa u nonglam-ktien jong nga ha shuwa ka khmat jong me, u ban khreh ïa ka lynti jong me ha shuwa jong me.’",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> “Shisha nga ong ha phi, na kiba la kha na ki kynthei, ym don uba la mih uba kham khraw ïa u Ïoannis u Nongpynbaptis: hynrei, uta uba kham rit ha ka hima ki bneng, u kham khraw ïa u.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Te naduh ki sngi u Ïoannis u Nongpynbaptis haduh mynta, la ïaknieh ïa ka hima ki bneng, bad kiba ïaknieh ki shim ïa ka da ka bor.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Naba Ki Nongïathuhlypa baroh bad Ka Hukum ki la ïathuhlypa haduh u Ïoannis.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Te lada phi mon ban pdiang, une u long u Elias u ban sa wan.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Uba don ki shkor ban sngew, to un sngew.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> “Hynrei, kum kaei ngan pynsyriem ïa kane ka pateng bynriew? Ka long kum ki khynnah kiba ïashong ha ki jaka ïew, bad kiba ïakhot ïa ki lok jong ki,",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> ki da ong, “ ‘Ngi la put jingput ha phi, te phim shym la shad; ngi la rwai sngewsynei ha phi, te phim shym la sngewsih.’",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> “Naba u Ïoannis u la wan, um da bam um da dih, bad ki ong, ‘Uba shong ksuid’ ïa u.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> U Khun u briew u la wan, u da bam u da dih ruh, te ki ong, ‘Ha khmih, u briew uba bam lalot, bad uba dih kyiad, u lok ki nongkhrong bad ki bapop!’ Hynrei, ka jingstad ka la ksan na ki khun jong ka.”",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Ynda kumta, u la sdang ban maham ïa kita ki shnong, ha kiba la leh kham bun ki kambah jong u, naba kim shym la kylla-ka-bamut.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> “Kordit ïa pha Khorasin! Kordit ïa pha Bethsaida! naba lada la leh ha ka Tyros bad ka Sidon ïa kita ki kambah ïa kiba la leh ha phi, kin da la kylla-ka-bamut la mynslem da ki jaiñ khain bad da ka dpei.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Hynrei, nga ong ha phi, ba kan long kham jem ïa ka Tyros bad ka Sidon ha ka sngi bishar ban ïa kaba ïa phi.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Ïa pha ka Kapernam ruh, ïa kaba la pynkyntiew haduh ka bneng, yn pynhiar keiñ haduh ka dujok: naba lada la leh ha Sodom ïa kita ki kambah ïa kiba la leh ha pha, kan da la sah haduh mynta.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Hynrei, nga ong ha phi, ba kan long kham jem ïa ka ri Sodom ha ka sngi bishar ban ïa kaba ïa pha.”",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Mynkata U Jisu u la ïathuh bad u la ong: “Nga nguh ïa me, ko Kpa, U Trai ka bneng bad ka khyndew, ba me la buhrieh ïa kine kiei kiei ruh na ki bastad bad ki basian, bad ba me la pynpaw ïa ki ha ki khunlung:",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> shisha, ko Kpa, naba kumta ka la ibit ha khmat jong me.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Kiei kiei baroh la ai ha nga na U Kpa jong nga: ym don ruh uba ithuh ïa U Khun, hynrei, tang U Kpa; lymne uba ithuh ïa U Kpa, hynrei, tang U Khun, bad uta ha uba uta U Khun u mon ban pynpaw ïa u.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> To wan ha nga, phi baroh ki bathait bad bakhia ka jingkit, te ngan pynjem ïa phi.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> To shim ïa ka lyngkor jong nga ha phi, to hikai ruh na nga; naba nga uba lui lui bad u barit ruh ha ka dohnud: te phin shem kaba jahthait ha ki mynsiem jong phi.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Naba ka lyngkor jong nga ka long kaba jem, bad ka jingkit jong nga kaba sting.”"
		},
		"12": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Mynkata, U Jisu u la leit ha ka sngi Sabbaton lyngba ïa ki lyngkha Kew; ki synran jong u te ki la thngan, bad ki la ïasdang ban kheit soh Kew, ban bam ruh.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Hynrei, haba ki Pharisi ki la ïohi, ki la ong ha u, “Ha khmih, ki synran jong me ki leh ïa ka bymbit ban leh ha ka sngi Sabbaton.”",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> U te u la ong ha ki, “Phim ju la pule, kaei ba u Dabid u la leh, mynba u la thngan, bad kita kiba bad u ruh?",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> kumno ba u la leit hapoh ka templ, bad ba u la bam ïa kita ki 'pu pyni, ïa ki bymbit ïa u ban bam, lymne ïa kita kiba bad u, hynrei, tang ïa ki lyngdoh hi?",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> lane phim ju la pule ha Ka Hukum, ba ki lyngdoh ha ka templ ha ka sngi Sabbaton ki pynkheiñ ïa ka Sabbaton khlem pop ruh?",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Hynrei, nga ong ha phi, ba uba kham khraw ïa ka templ u don hangne.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Hynrei, lada phi la lah tip kaei kane, ‘Ïa ka jingisynei nga mon, te ym ïa ka jingkñia,’ phin ym da la pynrem ïa kita kiba khlem pop.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Naba U Khun u briew, u long U Trai ka Sabbaton.”",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Te haba u la mih noh nangta, u la leit ha ka synagog jong ki.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Ha khmih ruh, la don u briew uba don ka kti ka baïap. Te ki la kylli ïa u, ki da ong, “Ka bit ne em ban pynkhiah ha ka sngi Sabbaton?” ba kin ïakem daw ïa u.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> U te u la ong ha ki: “Uno u briew uba na phi uba don kawei ka langbrot, lada kata ka hap ruh ha ka thliew ha ka sngi Sabbaton, un ym shim bad rah noh ïa ka?",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> u briew te katno u kham kor ïa ka langbrot! Kumta, ka bit ban leh bha ha ka sngi Sabbaton.”",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Haba kumta u la ong ha uta u briew, “To rah ïa la ka kti.” U la rah te ïa ka; bad la pynbha pat ïa ka kum kata kawei.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Te haba kita ki Pharisi ki la leit noh, ki la ïasylla pyrshah ïa U, kumno ba kin ïoh pynïap noh ïa U.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Hynrei, U Jisu haba u la tip u la leit noh nangta: te ki paidbah babun ki la ïabud ïa u, bad u la pynkhiah ïa ki baroh;",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> te u la maham ïa ki ba kin ym pynpaw ïa u:",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> kumta ba la pyndep ïa kata ba la ong da u Isaïah u nongïathuhlypa, u da ong,",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> “Ha khmih, u shakri jong nga ïa uba nga la jied; uba ieit jong nga ha uba ka mynsiem jong nga ka sngewbha eh: ngan buh ïa U Mynsiem jong nga ha u, bad un pynbna ïa ka jingbishar ha ki Jentil:",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> un ym ïaleh, lymne pyrta; lymne uei uei ruh un ym ïohsngew ïa ka ktien jong u ha ki lynti:",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> un ym pynkheiñ ïa u khah uba la mong, bad un ym pynlip ïa u 'saihon uba sah tdem, tad ynda un pynphriang ïa ka jingbishar haduh ka jingjop:",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> te ha ka kyrteng jong u ki Jentil kin ïakyrmen.”",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Ynda kumta, la wallam ha U ïa uba shong ksuid u bamatlah bad u bymnangkren; bad U la pynkhiah ïa u, kat haduh ba uta u bamatlah bad u bymnangkren u la ïohi bad u la kren ruh.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Te kita ki paidbah baroh ki la ïasngewkyndit eh, bad ki la ïa-ong, “Une um long u khun u Dabid?”",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Hynrei, haba kita ki Pharisi ki la ïohsngew ki la ïa-ong, “Une u briew um beh noh ïa ki ksuid, lymda da u Belsebul u rangbah ki ksuid.”",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Hynrei, U Jisu haba u la tip ïa ki jingmut jong ki, u la ong ha ki, “Ka hima baroh kaba ïaleh makynti, kan jot; ka shnong ruh ne ka ïing baroh kaba ïaleh makynti, kan ym neh.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Lada u Soitan ruh u shop noh ïa u Soitan, u ïaleh hi ïa lade; kumta, kan neh kumno ka hima jong u?",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Lada nga ruh nga beh noh ïa ki ksuid da u Belsebul, dano ba ki khun jong phi ki beh noh ïa ki? Namar kata, kin long ki nongbishar jong phi.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Hynrei, lada nga beh noh ïa ki ksuid da U Mynsiem U Blei, kumta te, ka hima U Blei ka la wan shisyndon ha phi.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Lane kumno uno uno ruh u lah ban leit hapoh ka ïing u bakhlaiñ, bad kurup ïa kiei kiei ruh ki jong u, lymda u khum shuwa ïa uta u bakhlaiñ? Ynda kumta te, un sa kurup ïa ka ïing jong u.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> U bymlong bad nga u ïaleh ïa nga: bad u bymïalum bad nga u pynsaphred.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Namar kata, nga ong ha phi, ba yn map ïa ki briew ïa ka pop baroh bad ïa kaba krenbeiñ blei: tang ïa kaba krenbeiñ ïa U Mynsiem Bakhuid, yn ym map shuh.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Bad uno uno ruh uba krenbeiñ ïa U Khun u briew, ïa uta lah ban map; hynrei, uno uno ruh uba krenbeiñ ïa U Mynsiem Bakhuid, ïa u yn ym map, ha kane ka pyrthei lymne ha kata ka ban sa wan.”",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> “Lane phin tharai babha ïa u dieng, bad ïa u soh jong u ruh; lane phin tharai basniew ïa u dieng, bad ïa u soh jong u ruh: naba ïa u dieng yn ithuh na u soh jong u.",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> A phi ki khun ki ksiew ki bseiñ! Phi ki bymman, kumno phi lah ban kren ka babha? naba na ka jingshlei ka dohnud ba ka kren ka shyntur.",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> U briew u babha u sei noh ïa kiei kiei ki babha na ka jingkynshew ka babha ka dohnud jong u: u briew babymman ruh u sei noh ïa kiei kiei babymman na ka jingkynshew babymman jong u.",
			"36": "<sup>36</sup> Hynrei, nga ong ha phi, ba ïa ka ktien thala baroh ïa kaba ki briew kin kren, kin ïa-ai jingkheiñ shaphang kata ha ka sngi bishar.",
			"37": "<sup>37</sup> Naba na ki ktien jong me yn pynksan ïa me, bad na ki ktien jong me yn pynrem ïa me.”",
			"38": "<sup>38</sup> Ynda kumta, kiba na ki nongthoh bad na ki Pharisi ki la ïathuh ki da ong, “Ko Nonghikai, ngi kwah ban ïohi ka dak na me.”",
			"39": "<sup>39</sup> U te u da ïathuh u la ong ha ki: “Ka pateng bynriew bymman bad baklim ka ïaiwad ka dak: hynrei, yn ym ai ka dak ha ka, hynrei, tang kata ka dak u Jonah u nongïathuhlypa.",
			"40": "<sup>40</sup> Naba kumba u Jonah u la shong lai sngi bad lai miet ha ka kpoh u dohkha khraw, kumta ruh U Khun u briew un shong lai sngi bad lai miet ha ka kpoh ka khyndew.",
			"41": "<sup>41</sup> Ki nong Ninebeh kin ïaïeng lem bad kane ka pateng bynriew ha ka jingbishar, bad kin ïa-pynrem ïa ka: naba ki la ïakylla-ka-bamut da ka jingïalap u Jonah: ha khmih te, hangne uba kham khraw ïa u Jonah.",
			"42": "<sup>42</sup> Ka syiem na shathie kan ïamih lem bad kane ka pateng bynriew ha ka jingbishar, bad kan pynrem ïa ka: naba ka la wan na sha ki bakut ka pyrthei ban ïohsngew ïa ka jingstad u Solomon; te ha khmih, hangne uba kham khraw ïa u Solomon.",
			"43": "<sup>43</sup> “Te haba u mynsiem bymkhuid u la mih noh na u briew, u ïaid ïa ki jaka ryngkhiang, ba u da wad ïa ka jaka shongthait, te um shem.",
			"44": "<sup>44</sup> Ynda kumta, u ong: ‘Ngan leit phai pat sha la ïing na kaba nga la mih noh’; te haba u la wan pat, u shem ïa ka ïing ba la suda, ba la sar, bad ba la buh beit ki jingbuh.",
			"45": "<sup>45</sup> Ynda kumta, u leit noh, u shim lem bad u, hynñiew ki mynsiem kiwei pat kiba kham bymman ïa u hi, te ki ïaleit hapoh bad ki shong sah hangta: ka bakhatduh te ïa uta u briew kan long kham sniew ïa ka banyngkong. Kumta, kan long ruh ïa kane ka pateng bynriew bymman.”",
			"46": "<sup>46</sup> Haba u dang kren ha kita ki paidbah, ha khmih, ka kmie jong u bad ki hynmen hynbew jong u ruh ki ïaïeng shabar, ba ki ïakwah ban ïakren bad u.",
			"47": "<sup>47</sup> Uwei u la ong te ha U, “Ha khmih, ka kmie jong me bad ki hynmen hynbew jong me ruh ki ïaïeng shabar, ba ki ïakwah ban ïakren bad me.”",
			"48": "<sup>48</sup> U te U da ïathuh U la ong ha uta uba la ïathuh ha U, “Kano kaba long ka kmie jong nga? bad kino kiba long ki hynmen hynbew jong nga?”",
			"49": "<sup>49</sup> Bad haba u la kner ïa la ka kti sha ki synran jong u, u la ong, “Ha khmih ka kmie jong nga bad ki hynmen hynbew jong nga!",
			"50": "<sup>50</sup> Naba uno uno ruh u ban leh ïa ka mon U Kpa jong nga uba ha bneng, uta keiñ u long u para jong nga bad ka para bad ka kmie de.”"
		},
		"13": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Ha kata kajuh ka sngi, U Jisu u la mih noh na ïing, bad u la shong harud duriaw.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Ki paidbah babun ruh ki la ïawan lang ha u, katba u la kiew halor ka lieng, bad u la shong; uta u paidbah baroh te u dang ïeng harud duriaw.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Bad U la kren ha ki, bun kiei kiei ruh ha ki pharshi, U da ong: “Ha khmih, u nongbet u la leit noh ban bet.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Haba u dang bet te, khyndiat ki la hap harud lynti, bad ki sim ki la wan, bad ki la bam ïa ki.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Kiwei pat de ki la hap halor ki jaka maw ha ka bymdon bun khyndew; kumne kumne ruh ki la mih, naba kam long jylliew ka khyndew:",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> haba ka la ïeng ka sngi te, ki la shit tyrkhong eh; bad naba kim don thied, ki la ïap ryngkhiang.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Kiwei pat te ki la hap hapdeng ki dieng shiah; te kita ki dieng shiah ki la mih, bad ki la ïakjap ïa ki.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Kiwei pat te ki la hap ha ka khyndew ka babha, bad ki la sei soh, kiba shispah shah, kiba hynriewphew shah, kiba laiphew shah ruh.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Uba don ki shkor ban sngew, to un sngew.”",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Kita ki synran te ki la ïawan ha u, bad ki la ïa-ong ha u, “Balei ba me kren ha ki ha ki pharshi?”",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> U da ïathuh te u la ong ha ki: “Naba la ai ha phi ban tip ïa ki maïan ka hima ki bneng, hynrei, ym shym la ai ha ki.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Naba uno uno ruh uba don, ha u yn ai, un ïoh kyrhai ruh: te uno uno ruh u bymdon, wat ïa kata kaba u don yn shim noh na u.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Namar kata ba nga kren ha ki ha ki pharshi: naba haba ki ïohi, kim ïohi; bad haba ki ïohsngew, kim ïohsngew, lymne kim sngewthuh.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Kumta, la pyndep ruh ha ki, ïa kata ka jingïathuhlypa u Isaïah, kaba ong: “ ‘Ïa kaba ïohsngew phin ïohsngew, te phin ym sngewthuh shuh: bad ïa kaba ïohi phin ïohi te phin ym ishemphang.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Naba ka dohnud kine ki briew ka la rben, bad ki la sngewkhia da la ki shkor, bad ki la khapbrip ïa la ki khmat; bad ïoh kin ïohi da la ki khmat, bad ba kin ïohsngew da la ki shkor, bad ba kin ïoh sngewthuh da la ka dohnud, bad ba kin ïoh kylla, bad ba ngan ïoh pynkhiah ruh ïa ki.’",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> “Hynrei, suk ki khmat jong phi, ba ki ïohi, bad ki shkor jong phi ba ki ïohsngew!",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Naba shisha nga ong ha phi, ba bun ki nongïathuhlypa bad ki riewhok ki la kwah ban ïohi ïa kiei kiei ruh ba phi ïohi, te kim shym la ïohi; bad ban ïohsngew ïa kiei kiei ruh ba phi ïohsngew, te kim shym la ïohsngew.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> “Namar kata, phin sngew ïa ka pharshi u nongbet.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Haba uno uno ruh u ïohsngew ïa ka ktien ka hima bad um sngewthuh ïa ka, u bymman u wan bad u rong noh ïa kata ïa kaba la bet ha ka dohnud jong u. Une u long uta ïa uba la bet harud lynti.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Uta ïa uba la bet halor ki jaka maw te, u long uta uba ïohsngew ïa kata ka ktien, bad uba pdiang kumne kumne ruh ïa ka da kaba kmen;",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> hynrei, u bymdon thied ha lade, u long te tang shibit; naba haba jia kaba jynjar ne kaba lehbeiñ namar kata ka ktien, kumne kumne ruh u thut.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Uta te ïa uba la bet hapdeng ki dieng shiah, long uta uba ïohsngew ïa kata ka ktien; hynrei, ka jingkhuslai kane ka pyrthei, bad ka jingshukor ka spah, ki ïakjap ïa kata ka ktien, te kam sei soh shuh.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Hynrei, uta ïa uba la bet ha ka khyndew ka babha, u long uta uba ïohsngew ïa kata ka ktien bad uba da sngewthuh ïa ka; uba sei soh ruh, bad ba pynmih ruh uba shispah shah, uba hynriewphew shah, uba laiphew shah ruh.”",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Ïa kawei pat ka pharshi u la buh ha khmat jong ki, u da ong: “Yn tharai ïa ka hima ki bneng kum u briew uba la bet ïa u symbai babha ha ka lyngkha jong u;",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> te haba ki dang ïohthiah ki briew, u la wan uba shun ïa u bad u la bet ïa ki ñiut hapdeng u Kew, te u la leit wan noh.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Hynrei, mynba u la speh uta u Kew, bad ba u la sei soh, mynkata ki la paw kita ki ñiut ruh.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Te haba ki la ïawan ki shakri jong uta u trai ïing, ki la ïa-ong ha u: ‘Ko kynrad, mem shym la bet ïa u symbai babha ha ka lyngkha jong me? nangno te ka la ïoh ki ñiut?’",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> U te u la ïathuh ha ki, ‘U briew uba shun u la leh ïa kata.’ Ki shakri te ki la ïakylli ïa u, ‘Me mon te ba ngin ïaleit thiew noh ïa ki?’",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Te u la ong, ‘Em; ba ïoh haba phi thiew noh ïa ki ñiut, phi rat lem bad ki, ïa u Kew ruh.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Ieh ba baroh ar kin ïamih lem haduh ka aïom ot: te ha kata ka aïom ka jingot ngan ong ha kiba ot, to ïalum shuwa ïa ki ñiut, to tehsong ruh ïa ki, ïa ka ban thang ïa ki: hynrei, ïa u Kew phin ïalum ha ka thiar jong nga.’ ”",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Ïa kawei pat ka pharshi u la buh ha khmat jong ki, u da ong: “Ka hima ki bneng ka long kum u symbai tyrso, ïa uba u briew u la shim, bad u la bet ha ka lyngkha jong u;",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> uba long kham rit shisha ïa ki symbai baroh, hynrei, ynda u la san u long kham khraw ïa ki jhur bad u long dieng, katba ki sim bneng ki wan bad ki shongtngen ha ki tnat jong u.”",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> U la kren ïa kawei pat ka pharshi ha ki: “Ka hima ki bneng ka long kum u thiat, ïa uba ka la shim ka kynthei, bad ka la btep ha ki lai pyrha u 'purew, tad ynda u la sieb baroh.”",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> Ïa kita kiei kiei baroh U Jisu u la kren ha kita ki paidbah ha ki pharshi: bad khlem pharshi um shym la kren ei ei ha ki,",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> ba kumta la pyndep ïa kata ba la ong da u nongïathuhlypa, u da ong: “Ngan ang ïa ka shyntur jong nga ha ki pharshi, ngan pynbna ïa kiei kiei ruh ba la buhrieh na myndanglong ka pyrthei.”",
			"36": "<sup>36</sup> Ynda kumta, haba U Jisu u la iehnoh ïa ki paidbah, u la leit sha ïing: te ki synran jong u ki la wan ha u, ki da ong, “To batai ïa ngi ïa kata ka pharshi ki ñiut ka lyngkha.”",
			"37": "<sup>37</sup> U te u la ïathuh bad u la ong ha ki: “Uta uba bet ïa u symbai babha, u long U Khun u briew;",
			"38": "<sup>38</sup> kata ka lyngkha ruh, ka long ka pyrthei; kita ki symbai babha ruh, ki long ki khun ka hima; hynrei, kita ki ñiut, ki long ki khun uta u bymman;",
			"39": "<sup>39</sup> uta u nongshun uba la bet ruh ïa ki, u long u Soitan; kata ka aïom ot ruh, ka long kaba wai noh ka pyrthei; kita kiba ot ruh, ki long ki angel.",
			"40": "<sup>40</sup> Namar kata, kumba ïalum ïa kita ki ñiut bad ba thang ïa ki ha ka ding, kumta keiñ, kan long ha kaba wai noh kane ka pyrthei.",
			"41": "<sup>41</sup> U Khun u briew un phah noh ïa ki angel jong u, bad kin ïalum na ka hima jong u ïa kiei kiei baroh kiba pynthut, bad ïa kita kiba leh bymman,",
			"42": "<sup>42</sup> bad kin bred ïa ki ha ka lawar ka ding; hangta keiñ yn long kaba lynñiar bad kum dait bniat.",
			"43": "<sup>43</sup> Ynda kumta, ki bahok kin ïatyngshaiñ noh kum ka sngi ha ka hima U Kpa jong ki. Uba don ki shkor ban sngew, to un sngew.",
			"44": "<sup>44</sup> “Pat, ka hima ki bneng ka long kum ka jingkynshew ïa kaba la buhrieh ha ka lyngkha, ïa kaba u briew u la shem, bad u la buhrieh; te na kaba kmen u leit noh, bad u die noh ïa kiei kiei baroh katba u don, bad u thied ïa kata ka lyngkha.",
			"45": "<sup>45</sup> “Pat, ka hima ki bneng ka long kum u nongkhaïi uba wad ïa ki mawlynnai bakordor;",
			"46": "<sup>46</sup> bad haba u la shem ïa uwei u mawlynnai u bakordor, u la leit die noh ïa kiei kiei baroh katba u don, bad u la thied ïa uta.",
			"47": "<sup>47</sup> “Pat, ka hima ki bneng ka long kum ka jar ïa kaba la bred ha ka duriaw, bad kaba ïalum na ki jaid baroh;",
			"48": "<sup>48</sup> ïa kaba, ynda ka la dap, ki ïaring sha ryngkew; te haba ki la ïashong, ki la ïalum ïa ki babha ha ki jingdiang, ïa ki basniew te ki la ïabred noh.",
			"49": "<sup>49</sup> Kumta kan long ha kaba wai noh ka pyrthei. Ki angel kin ïamih noh bad kin pynïakhlad noh ïa ki bymman napdeng ki bahok,",
			"50": "<sup>50</sup> bad kin bred ïa ki ha ka lawar ka ding: hangta keiñ yn long kaba lynñiar bad kum dait bniat.”",
			"51": "<sup>51</sup> U Jisu u la ong ha ki, “Phi la sngewthuh ïa kita kiei kiei baroh?” Ki ruh ki la ong ha u, “Ho-oid, kynrad.”",
			"52": "<sup>52</sup> U la ong te ha ki, “Namar kata, u nongthoh baroh uba la ïoh hikai ha ka hima ki bneng, u long kum u briew uba u trai ïing, uba sei noh na ka jingkynshew jong u ïa kiei kiei ruh ki bathymmai bad barim.”",
			"53": "<sup>53</sup> Ka la jia, haba U Jisu u la wai noh ïa kine ki pharshi, ba u la leit noh nangta.",
			"54": "<sup>54</sup> Haba u la wan te ha la ka ri, u la hikai ïa ki ha ka synagog jong ki, kat ban pynkyndit thred ïa ki, bad ki la kylli, “Nangno une u la ïoh ïa kane ka jingstad, bad kine ki kambah?",
			"55": "<sup>55</sup> Une um long u khun uta u misteri? ym khot ‘ka Mari’ ïa ka kmie jong u? ‘u Jakob’, bad ‘u Josis’, bad ‘u Simon’, bad ‘u Juda’ ruh, ïa ki para jong u?",
			"56": "<sup>56</sup> ki para kynthei jong u de, kim don baroh bad ngi? nangno te une u la ïoh ïa kita kiei kiei baroh?”",
			"57": "<sup>57</sup> Ki la thut ruh ha u. U Jisu te u la ong ha ki, “U nongïathuhlypa um long khlem burom, hynrei, tang ha la ka ri bad ha la ïing ruh.”",
			"58": "<sup>58</sup> Um shym la leh shibun ki kambah hangta, namar ka jingbymngeit jong ki."
		},
		"14": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Mynkata u Herod uba u Tetrark u la ïohsngew ïa ka jingbna shaphang U Jisu,",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> bad u la ong ha ki shakri jong u, “Une u long u Ïoannis u Nongpynbaptis; u la mihpat na ki nongïap; namar kata keiñ, kine ki borbah ki ïatrei ha u.”",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Naba u Herod haba u la kem ïa u Ïoannis, u la khum ïa u, bad u la buh ruh ïa u ha ka byndi na ka bynta ka Herodias, ka tnga u Philip, u para jong u.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Naba u Ïoannis u la ong ha u, “Ym bit ïa me ban ïoh ïa ka.”",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Haba u mon te ban pynïap ïa u, u la sheptieng ïa u paidbah, naba ki ju ñiew ïa u kum u nongïathuhlypa.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Te haba la dei ka sngi kha u Herod, ka khun ka Herodias ka la shad ha khmat jong ki, bad ka la pynsngewbha ïa u Herod.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Namar kata, u la kular da kaba smai ban ai ha ka kat kaba kan pan.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Ka ruh, haba ka la suh buit ka kmie jong ka, ka la ong, “To ai ha nga hangne ïa ka khlieh u Ïoannis u Nongpynbaptis ha ka pliang.”",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> U syiem te u la sngewsih, hynrei, na ka bynta kita ki jingsmai, bad kita kiba ïashong bam bad u, u la hukum ban ai.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Haba u la phah te, u la khrai khlieh ïa u Ïoannis ha kata ka byndi.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Te la wallam ïa ka khlieh jong u ha ka pliang, bad la ai ha kata ka khynnah; ka ruh ka la leit lam ha ka kmie jong ka.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Te haba ki la ïawan ki synran jong u, ki la ïarah noh ïa ka met, bad ki la ïatep ïa ka; bad ki la leit ïathuh ha U Jisu.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Haba U Jisu u la ïohsngew ruh, u la leit noh nangta ha ka lieng, sha ka jaka kynjah weibriew; te haba ki paidbah ki la ïohsngew, ki la ïabud ïa u da ki kjat na ki shnong.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Haba U Jisu ruh u la mih noh, u la ïohi ïa u paidbah babun, bad u la sngewsynei ïa ki bad u la pynkhiah ïa ki bapang jong ki.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Te haba ka la kham noh ka sngi, ki la ïawan ha u ki synran jong u, ki da ong, “Kane ka long ka jaka kynjah, ka por ruh ka la kham palat; to pyllait noh ïa ki paidbah, ba kin leit sha ki shnong ban thied jingbam ïa lade.”",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> U Jisu te u la ong ha ki, “Kim donkam ban leit noh; to ai ma phi ha ki ban bam.”",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Ki te ki ong ha u, “Ngi don hangne sa tang san tylli ki kpu, bad ar tylli ki dohkha.”",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Te u la ong, “Wallam ïa ki hangne ha nga.”",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Te u la hukum ban pynshong shaniah ïa ki paidbah ha u phlang, bad u la shim ïa kita ki san tylli ki kpu bad ïa kita ki ar tylli ki dohkha, bad haba u la khmied sha bneng, u la nguh, bad u la kdiah, u la ai ïa ki kpu ha ki synran, bad kita ki synran ha ki paidbah.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Te ki la ïabam baroh, bad ki la kdang; bad ki la ïakhar na kiba lwet basah tam, dap khat-ar tukri.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Kita kiba la ïabam te ki long kumba san hajar ki rangbah, nalor ki kynthei bad ki khynnah.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Kumne kumne ruh U Jisu u la kyntu ïa ki synran jong u ban kiew halor kata ka lieng, bad ban leit noh ha shuwa jong u sha shiliang, katba u dang pyllait noh ïa ki paidbah.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Te haba u la pyllait noh ïa ki paidbah, u la kiew sha u lum weibriew ban duwai; bad haba ka la janmiet ruh, u la don hangta weibriew.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Hynrei mynkata, kata ka lieng ka la don hapdeng ka duriaw, ïa kaba la pynkhih eh da ki jingat phyllung; naba ka lyer ka la beh pyrshah.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Te ha ka jingap miet ka basaw U Jisu u la leit ha ki, u da ïaid halor ka duriaw.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Haba kita ki synran te ki la ïohi ïa u ba u ïaid halor ka duriaw, ki la sngewkyiuh eh, ki da ong, “Ka long ka rngai”; te ki la ïalynñiar na kaba sheptieng.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Hynrei, U Jisu kumne kumne ruh u la kren ha ki, u da ong, “To sngewshlur; dei ma nga; to wat sheptieng.”",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> U Petros te u da ïathuh, u la ong ha U, “Ko Trai, lada dei ma me, hukum ïa nga ban wan sha me halor ka um.”",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> U te u la ong, “To wan.” Te haba u Petros u la hiar na kata ka lieng, u la ïaid halor ka um ban leit sha U Jisu.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Hynrei, haba u la ïohi ïa kata ka lyer ba ka jur, u la sngewsheptieng, bad haba u la sdang ban ngam, u la pyrta, u da ong, “Ko Trai, to pynim ïa nga.”",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Kumne kumne ruh U Jisu haba u la kner ïa la ka kti, U la kem ïa u, bad U la ong ha u, “A me uba rit jingngeit! balei ba me la sngew-artatien?”",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Haba ki la ïakiew te halor kata ka lieng, ka lyer ka la jah noh.",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Te kita kiba ha kata ka lieng ki la mane dem ïa u, ki ïa-ong, “Shisha me uba U Khun U Blei.”",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> Te haba ki la lah poi sha shiliang, ki la wan ha ka ri Gennesaret.",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> Te haba ki briew ha kata ka jaka ki la ithuh ïa u, ki la phah kylleng ïa kata ka ri baroh, bad ki la wallam ha u ïa ki bapang baroh;",
			"36": "<sup>36</sup> bad ki la ïakyrpad ïa u ba kin shu ïoh ktah tang ïa ka rmiang ka jaiñkup jong u; te baroh kat kiba la ktah, ki la khiah phar."
		},
		"15": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Ynda kumta, ki la ïawan ha U Jisu ki nongthoh bad ki Pharisi kiba na Jerusalem, ki da ong,",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> “Balei ba ki synran jong me ki ryngkang ïa ka rukom pateng la pateng ki tymmen basan? naba kim da thet ïa ki kti jong ki haba kin sa bam jingbam.”",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> U da ïathuh te u la ong ha ki, “Balei ba phi ruh phi ryngkang ïa ka hukum U Blei da ka rukom pateng la pateng jong phi?",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Naba U Blei u la hukum, u da ong: ‘Burom ïa la u kpa bad ïa la ka kmie ruh:’ bad ‘Uba krenbeiñ ïa u kpa lane ïa ka kmie, ai un ïap da ka jingpynïap.’",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Hynrei, phi ong, ba uno uno ruh u ban ong ha la u kpa ne ha la ka kmie, ‘Kaei kaei ruh ka jong nga na kaba men da la myntoi, ka long ka jingainguh’,",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> un ym burom shuh te ïa u kpa jong u lane ïa ka kmie jong u. Kumta phi la pynduh noh ïa ka hukum U Blei da ka rukom pateng la pateng jong phi.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Phi kiba arsap! Bit kaba u Isaïah u la ïathuhlypa shaphang jong phi, u da ong,",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> “ ‘Kine ki briew ki wan hajan jong nga da ka shyntur jong ki, bad ki burom ïa nga da ki rmiang shyntur jong ki, hynrei, ka dohnud jong ki ka jngai noh na nga:",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> hynrei, ki mane thala ïa nga, haba ki hikai ïa ki hukum jong ki briew kum ka jinghikai.’ ”",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Te haba U la khot ha lade ïa u paidbah, U la ong ha ki: “To sngew phi, to sngewthuh ruh:",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Ym dei kata kaba rung ha ka shyntur kaba pyntngit ïa u briew, hynrei, kaba mih noh na ka shyntur, kata keiñ kaba pyntngit ïa u briew.”",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Ynda kumta, ki synran jong u ki la ïawan, bad ki la ïa-ong ha u, “Me tip ne em ba haba kita ki Pharisi ki la ïohsngew ïa kane ka ktien, ki la sngewthut?”",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Hynrei, u la ïathuh bad u la ong, “Ïa ki jingthung baroh kiba U Kpa jong nga uba ha bneng um shym la thung, yn rat noh keiñ.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> To iehnoh ïa ki; ki long ki nongïalam bamatlah ïa ki bamatlah. Te lada u bamatlah u ïalam ïa u bamatlah, kin ïahap baroh ar ngut ha ka thliew.”",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> U Petros te u la ïathuh bad u la ong ha u, “To batai ïa kata ka pharshi ha ngi.”",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> U Jisu te u la ong, “Phi ruh katta phim pat sngewthuh?",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Phim pat sngewthuh, ba baroh kat kaba rung shapoh ka shyntur ka leit hapoh ka kpoh, bad ba bred noh ïa ka sharud?",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Hynrei, kita kiei kiei ruh kiba mih noh na ka shyntur ki mih na ka dohnud; kita te ki pyntngit ïa u briew.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Naba na ka dohnud ki mih noh ki jingmut bymman, kaba pynïap, kaba klim, kaba ïakai kynthei, kaba tuh, kaba sakhi lamler, kaba krenbeiñ.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Dei kine kiei kiei kiba pyntngit keiñ ïa u briew; hynrei, ban bam da ki kti khlem thet kam pyntngit ïa u briew.”",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Te haba U Jisu u la mih noh nangta, u la leit sha ki phang ka Tyros bad ka Sidon.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Ha khmih ruh, ka kynthei ka nong Kanaan ka la wan na kita ki phang, bad ka la kyrpad ïa u, ka da ong, “To isynei ïa nga, ko Trai, U Khun u Dabid! ka khun jong nga ka kordit eh ba ka shong ksuid.”",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Hynrei, um shym jubab ha ka shikyntien ruh. Ki synran jong u te haba ki la ïawan hajan, ki la kyrpad ïa u, ki da ong, “To pyllait noh ïa ka, naba ka pyrta jam nadien jong ngi.”",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> U da ïathuh u la ong te, “Ym shym la phah ïa nga, hynrei, tang ha kita ki langbrot kiba la jah noh na ka ïing Israel.”",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Ka, hynrei, haba ka la wan, ka la mane dem ha u, ka da ong, “Ko Trai, to ïarap ïa nga.”",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Hynrei, u la ïathuh bad u la ong, “Ym bit ban shim ïa ka jingbam ki khun bad ban bred ïa ka ha ki ksew.”",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Ka te ka la ïathuh, “Shisha, ko Trai, hynrei, wat ki ksew ki ïabam na kita kiba lwet kiba la hap na ka miej ki kynrad jong ki.”",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Ynda kumta, U Jisu u la ïathuh bad u la ong ha ka, “Ko kynthei, kaba khraw ka jingngeit jong pha; to kan long ïa pha kumba pha mon.” Ka khun jong ka, ka la khiah te naduh kata ka por.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Te haba U Jisu u la leit noh nangta, u la wan hajan ka duriaw Galilaïa; haba u la kiew ruh sha u lum, u la shong hangta.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Ki paidbah babun te ki la wan ha u, ki da don lem bad ki, ki ba-dkoh, ki bamatlah, ki bymnangkren, ki bakynriang, bad shibun kiwei kiwei ruh; bad ki la buh ïa ki hajan ki kjat U Jisu, te u la pynkhiah ïa ki.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Katba kita ki paidbah ki la sngewphylla, haba ki la ïohi ïa ki bymnangkren ba ki da kren, ïa ki bakynriang ba ki la khiah, ïa ki ba-dkoh ba ki da ïaid, ïa ki bamatlah ruh ba ki da ïohi, ki la ïaroh ruh ïa U Blei ki Israel.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Haba U Jisu te u la khot ha lade ïa ki synran jong u, u la ong, “Nga sngewsynei ïa u paidbah; naba ki la ïaishong bad nga mynta la lai sngi, bad kim don ei ei ruh ban bam; te ngam mon ban phah noh jingit ïa ki, ba ïoh ki ïapler ha lynti.”",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Te ki synran jong u ki la ïathuh ha u, “Nangno ngin ïoh ki kpu katta katta ha ka ri khlaw, kat ban pynkdang ïa u paidbah kat une?”",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> U Jisu u la kylli te ïa ki, “Phi don katno tylli ki kpu?” Ki la ong te, “Hynñiew tylli, bad khyndiat ki dohkha rit.”",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> Te u la hukum ïa ki paidbah ban shong shaniah ha khyndew.",
			"36": "<sup>36</sup> Haba u la shim te ïa kita ki hynñiew tylli ki kpu bad ïa kita ki dohkha, bad haba u la nguh, u la kdiah, bad u la ai ha ki synran jong u, kita ki synran de ha uta u paidbah.",
			"37": "<sup>37</sup> Kumta, baroh ki la ïabam bad ki la kdang; ki la ïakhar noh ruh na kiba lwet basah tam, dap hynñiew tukri.",
			"38": "<sup>38</sup> Kita kiba la ïabam te ki long kumba saw hajar ki rangbah, nalor ki kynthei bad ki khynnah.",
			"39": "<sup>39</sup> Haba u la pyllait noh ïa ki paidbah, u la kiew pat halor kata ka lieng, bad u la leit sha ki phang ka Magdala."
		},
		"16": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Haba ki Pharisi bad ki Saddusi ruh ki la ïawan hajan, ki da tynjuh ïa u, ki la ïapan ba un pyni ïa ka dak na bneng ha ki.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> U te u la ïathuh bad u la ong ha ki, “Haba la janmiet, phi ong, ‘Kan rang, naba ka saw ka bneng:’",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> mynstep ruh, ‘Kan khih ka lyer mynta, naba ka bneng ka saw jngut’: phi kiba arsap! phi tip ban bishar shisha ïa ka khmat ka bneng, hynrei, phim lah bishar ïa ki dak ki aïom.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Ka pateng bynriew bymman bad baklim ka wad ïa ka dak; te yn ym ai ka dak ha ka, hynrei, tang ïa kata ka dak u Jonah u nongïathuhlypa.” Haba u la iehnoh te ïa ki, u la leit noh.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Haba ki synran jong u te ki la ïawan sha shiliang, ki la klet ban wallam kpu.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> U Jisu te u la ong ha ki, “To sumar, to kiar na u thiat ki Pharisi bad ki Saddusi.”",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Ki te ki la ïakren hi paralok, ki da ong, “Naba ngim shym la wallam kpu keiñ!”",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Haba U Jisu te u la tip ïa kata, u la ong ha ki, “A phi kiba rit jingngeit! balei phi ïakren hi paralok, naba phim shym la wallam kpu?",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Phim pat sngewthuh, lymne phim kynmaw ïa kita ki san tylli ki kpu jong kita san hajar, bad katno tukri phi la ïakhar ruh?",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> lymne ïa kita ki hynñiew tylli ki kpu jong kita ki saw hajar, bad katno tukri phi la ïakhar ruh?",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Kumno ba phim sngewthuh ba ngam shym ong ha phi shaphang u kpu? hynrei, ban sumar na uta u thiat ki Pharisi bad ki Saddusi.”",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Ynda kumta, ki la sngewthuh ba um shym la ong ban sumar na u thiat u kpu, hynrei, na ka jinghikai ki Pharisi bad ki Saddusi.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Haba U Jisu u la wan sha ki phang ka Kaisaria Philippi, u la kylli ïa ki synran jong u, u da ong, “Ki briew ki ong uei ïa nga, U Khun u briew?”",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Ki la ong te, “Don kiba ong u Ïoannis u Nongpynbaptis, kiwei te, u Elias, bad kiwei pat, u Jeremaïah lane uwei na ki nongïathuhlypa.”",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> U la ong ha ki, “Phi te phi ong ba nga long uei?”",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> U Simon Petros u la ïathuh bad u la ong, “Me long U Khrist, U Khun U Blei ba-im.”",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> U Jisu te u la ïathuh bad u la ong ha u, “Suk ma me, ko Simon u khun u Jonah, naba ka doh bad ka snam kam shym la pyni ïa kata ha me, hynrei, U Kpa jong nga uba ha bneng.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Nga ruh nga ong ha me, ba me long u Petros, bad halor une u mawsiang ngan tei ïa ka balang jong nga; te ki khyrdop ka dujok kin ym lah ïa ka.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Bad ngan ai ha me ïa ki shabi ka hima ki bneng; te kaei kaei ruh ïa kaba men teh ha ka khyndew yn teh ïa ka ha bneng ruh, bad kaei kaei ruh ïa kaba men pyllait ha ka khyndew yn pyllait ïa ka ha bneng ruh.”",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Ynda kumta, u la adong ïa ki synran jong u ban ym ïathuh hano hano ruh ba u long uta U Khrist.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Naduh kata, U Jisu u la sdang ban pyni ha ki synran jong u, ba ka dei ïa u ban leit noh sha Jerusalem, ban shah ruh shibun kiei kiei na ki tymmen basan bad na ki rangbah lyngdoh bad na ki nongthoh de, bad ba yn pynïap ruh ïa u, bad ba yn pynmih pat ïa u ha ka balai ka sngi.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Haba u Petros te u la shim kyrpang ïa U, u la sdang ban sneng ïa U, u da ong, “To isynei ïa lade, ko Trai, kata kan ym long ïa me.”",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Haba U la phai te U la ong ha u Petros, “Khie leit shadien jong nga, me u Soitan! Me long u mawjynthut ïa nga! naba mem ñiew ïa kiei kiei ki jong U Blei, hynrei, ïa kiei kiei ki jong ki briew.”",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Ynda kumta, U Jisu u la ong ha ki synran jong u: “Lada uno uno ruh u mon ban wan nadien jong nga, ai ba un len ïa lade, bad un rah ïa la ka diengphna, bad un wan bud ïa nga.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Naba uno uno ruh uba mon ban pynim ïa la ka mynsiem, un duh noh ïa ka, bad uno uno ruh u ban duh noh ïa la ka mynsiem na ka bynta jong nga, un shem ïa ka.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Naba u briew un myntoi aïu, lada un ïoh ïa ka pyrthei baroh, bad un duh noh ïa la ka mynsiem? Lane u briew un ïapli da ei ïa la ka mynsiem?",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Naba U Khun u briew un sa wan ha ka burom U Kpa jong u lem bad ki angel jong u, ynda kumta, un ai ha uwei pa uwei katba kum ka jingleh jong u.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Shisha nga ong ha phi, don kiba ïeng hangne ki ban ym mad ïa ka jingïap, tad ynda ki la ïohi ïa U Khun u briew ba u wan ha ka hima jong u.”"
		},
		"17": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Ynda la hynriew sngi ruh, U Jisu u la shim lem ïa u Petros, bad ïa u Jakob, bad ïa u Ïoannis u para jong u, bad U la leit lam ïa ki kyrpang sha u lum bajrong,",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> bad la pynkylla dur ïa u ha khmat jong ki; ka khmat jong u te ka la tyngshaiñ kum ka sngi, bad ki jaiñ jong u ki la long lieh kum ka jingshai.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Ha khmih ruh, u Moses bad u Elias ki la paw ha ki, ki da ïakren bad u.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> U Petros te u da ïathuh u la ong ha U Jisu, “Ko Trai, ka bha ïa ngi ban don hangne; lada me mon, ngan thaw hangne lai tylli ki ïingtrep; kawei ïa me, kawei ruh ïa u Moses, bad kawei ruh ïa u Elias.”",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Haba u dang kren, ha khmih, u lyoh batyngshaiñ u la kah ïa ki: ha khmih ruh, ka ktien na uta u lyoh ka la ong, “Une u long U Khun jong nga uba ieit, ha uba nga sngewbha: phin sngew ïa u.”",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Haba ki synran te ki la ïohsngew, ki la dem ngon, bad ki la sheptieng shibun eh.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> U Jisu te haba u la wan hajan, u la ktah ïa ki, bad u la ong, “To ïeng, wat sheptieng ruh.”",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Te haba ki la khmied la ki khmat, kim ïohi ïano ïano ruh, hynrei, tang ïa U Jisu hi.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Haba ki dang ïahiar te na uta u lum, U Jisu u la hukum ïa ki, u da ong, “Wat ïathuh hano hano ruh ïa kata ka jingithuhpaw, tad ynda U Khun u briew u la mihpat na ki baïap.”",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Ki synran jong u te ki la ïakylli ïa u, ki da ong, “Na ka balei te ba ki nongthoh ki ong ba ka dei ba u Elias un wan shuwa?”",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> U Jisu te u la ïathuh bad u la ong ha ki, “U Elias shisha u wan, bad un pynbha ïa kiei kiei baroh:",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> hynrei, nga ong ha phi, ba u Elias u la wan lypa, bad kim shym la ithuh ïa u, hynrei, ki la leh ïa u katba ki la imon. Kumta ruh, U Khun u briew un sa shah shitom na ki.”",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Ynda kumta, ki synran ki la ïasngewthuh ba u la ïathuh ha ki shaphang u Ïoannis u Nongpynbaptis.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Te haba ki la ïawan ha u paidbah, uwei u briew u la wan ha U, u da dem khohsiew ïa U, u da ong,",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> “Ko Trai, to isynei ïa u khun jong nga; naba u pang bhur, u kordit eh ruh, naba u hap jyndei ha ka ding, jyndei ha ka um ruh.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Nga la wallam ïa u ha ki synran jong me, te kim lah ban pynkhiah ïa u.”",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> U Jisu te u la ïathuh bad u la ong, “A phi ka pateng bynriew bymngeit bad bamutlop, sa katno ngan long lem bad phi? sa katno ngan shah ïa phi? to wallam ïa u shane sha nga.”",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Te U Jisu u la sneng ïa uta u ksuid, u ruh u la mih noh na u; te uta u khynnah u la khiah naduh kata ka por.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Ynda kumta, ki synran ki la ïawan ha U Jisu jar jar, bad ki la ong, “Balei ba ngi ngim lah ban beh noh ïa u?”",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> U Jisu te u la ïathuh ha ki, “Namar ka jingbymngeit jong phi: naba shisha nga ong ha phi, lada phi don ka jingngeit kaba kat iwei i symbai tyrso, phin ong ha une u lum, ‘To leit noh nangne hangtai’, te un leit noh keiñ; bad ym don kaei kaei ruh ïa kaba phin ym lah leh.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Hynrei, u kynja une um ju mih noh, hynrei, tang da ka jingduwai bad kaba shah jingit.”",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Haba ki dang ïaïaid te ha Galilaïa, U Jisu u la ong ha ki, “Yn sa die noh ïa U Khun u briew ha ki kti ki briew,",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> bad kin ïa-pynïap ïa u, hynrei, ha ka balai ka sngi yn sa pynmih pat ïa u.” Te ki la ïasngewsih eh.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Te haba ki la poi ha Kapernam, kita kiba ïakhrong ïa ki shiteng shekel ki la ïawan ha u Petros, bad ki la ïakylli, “U Nonghikai jong phi um ju siew ïa ki shiteng shekel?”",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> U la ong, “Ho-oid.” Te ynda u la leit hapoh ïing, U Jisu u la kren shuwa ïa u, U da ong, “Me mut kumno, ko Simon? na kino ba ki syiem ka pyrthei ki ju shim khrong lane khajna? na la ki khun hi, ne na ki nongwei?”",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> U Petros u la ong ha U, “Na ki nongwei.” U Jisu u la ong ha u, “Naba kumta te ki khun ki lait.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Hynrei, ïoh ba ngin ïa-pynthut ïa ki, to khie leit sha ka duriaw, bred ïa u khwai, bad to shim ïa kata ka dohkha kaba la ngat nyngkong; bad haba me la pyn-ang ïa ka shyntur jong ka, men shem shi shekel; to shim ïa kata, to ai ruh ha ki na ka bynta jong nga bad jong me ruh.”"
		},
		"18": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Mynkata ki synran ki la ïawan ha U Jisu, ki da ong, “Uei uba kham khraw te ha ka hima ki bneng?”",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Te haba U Jisu u la khot ïa u khynnah, U la buh ïa u hapdeng jong ki,",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> bad u la ong, “Shisha nga ong ha phi, lada phim kylla, bad phim long ruh kum ki khynnah, phin ym leit bsut ha ka hima ki bneng.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Namar kata, uno uno ruh u ban pynrit ïa lade kum une u khynnah, uta u long uba kham khraw ha ka hima ki bneng;",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> uno uno ruh u ban pdiang te ïa iwei i khynnah kum ine ha ka kyrteng jong nga, u pdiang ïa nga.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> “Uno uno ruh u ban pynthut te ïa iwei na kine ki barit kiba ngeit ha nga, ka la kham bha ïa u ba yn teh ïa u mawtylliat bakhraw ha ka ryndang jong u, bad ba yn pynngam jyllop ïa u ha kaba jylliew ka duriaw.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> “Kordit ïa ka pyrthei namar ki jingjynthut! naba donkam ïa kita ki jingjynthut ban wan shisha, hynrei, kordit ïa uta u briew na uba wan kata ka jingjynthut!",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Te lada ka kti jong me lane ka kjat jong me ka pynthut ïa me, to ot noh ïa ka, to bred noh ruh na me; ka kham bha ïa me ban leit bsut dkoh ne kynriang sha ka jingim, ban ïa kaba ïoh ar tylli ki kti ne ar tylli ki kjat, bad ban bred ïa me ha ka ding bymjukut.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Bad lada ka khmat jong me ka pynthut ïa me, to khlaw noh ïa ka, to bred noh ruh na me; ka kham bha ïa me ban leit bsut sha ka jingim tang kawei ka khmat, ban ïa kaba ïoh ar tylli ki khmat, bad ban bred ïa me ha ka dujok ding.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> “To sumar ba phin ym ibeiñ ïa iwei na kine ki barit; naba nga ong ha phi, ba ki angel jong ki ha bneng, ki ïohi ha la ka sngi ïa ka khmat U Kpa jong nga uba ha bneng.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Naba U Khun u briew u la wan ban pynim ïa kaba la jot.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Phi mut kumno? Lada u briew u la don shispah ki langbrot, te lada kawei na ki ka leit sakma, um iehnoh sah ïa ki khyndaiphew khyndai, bad leit sha lum ban wad ïa kata kaba la sakma?",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Te lada ka jia ïa u ban shem ïa kata, shisha nga ong ha phi, ba u kham kmen namar kata, ban ïa namar kita ki khyndaiphew khyndai ki bym shym la leit sakma.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Kumta, kam long ka mon U Kpa jong phi uba ha bneng, ba in jah noh iwei na kine ki barit.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> “Lada u paralok jong me u leh pop ïa me, to khie leit, bad sneng ïa u haba don tang ma u bad me hi: lada un sngew ïa me, me la pynbha ïa u paralok jong me.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Te lada um sngew, to shim lem bad me ïa uwei ne ar ngut kiwei pat, ba da ka shyntur ar ngut ne lai ngut ki sakhi yn pynskhem ïa ka ktien baroh.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Te lada um treh ban sngew ïa kita, to ïathuh ha ka balang; te lada um treh ban sngew ïa kata ka balang ruh, to ai un long ïa me kum u Jentil bad u nongkhrong.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> “Shisha nga ong ha phi, ïa kiei kiei ruh kat kiba phin teh ha ka khyndew yn teh ïa ki ha bneng, bad ïa kiei kiei ruh kat kiba phin pyllait ha ka khyndew yn pyllait ïa ki ha bneng.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Pat nga ong ha phi, ba lada ar ngut na phi kin ïakut lem ha ka khyndew shaphang kaei kaei ruh ïa kaba kin ïapan, kan long ïa ki na U Kpa jong nga uba ha bneng.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Naba ha kaba don ar ngut ne lai ngut kiba la ïaseng ha ka kyrteng jong nga, hangta nga don hapdeng jong ki.”",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Ynda kumta, u la wan u Petros ha U, bad u la ong, “Ko Trai, katno sien ba u paralok jong nga un leh pop ïa nga, bad ba ngan map ïa u? haduh hynñiew sien?”",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> U Jisu u la ong ha u, “Ngam ong ha me haduh hynñiew sien, hynrei, haduh hynñiewphew sien hynñiew!",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> “Namar kata, ïa ka hima ki bneng yn tharai kum uwei u syiem, uba la mon ban ïakheiñ bad ki shakri jong u.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Haba u la sdang te ban kheiñ, la wallam ha u ïa uwei ha uba u shah shiphew hajar ki talent.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Hynrei, haba um don ban siew, u kynrad jong u, u la hukum ban die noh ïa u, bad ïa ka tnga jong u, bad ïa ki khun, bad ïa kiei kiei baroh kat kiba u don, ban siew noh ïa kata ka ram.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Namar kata, uta u shakri haba u la dem u la mane ïa u, u da ong, ‘Ko kynrad, to ïaishah ïa nga, te ngan siew baroh ïa me’.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> U kynrad uta u shakri haba u la sngewsynei te, u la pyllait ïa u, bad u la map ïa kata ka ram ïa u.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Te haba uta u shakri u la mih noh, u la shem ïa uwei na ki para shakri jong u ha uba u la shah shispah suka, bad u la kem ïa u na ka ryndang, u da ong, ‘Ai ïa nga ïa kaba nga la shah!’",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Namar kata, uta u para shakri jong u haba u la dem ha ki kjat jong u, u la kyrpad ïa u, u da ong, ‘To ïaishah ïa nga, te ngan siew ïa me.’",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> U te um shah; hynrei, u la leit bred ïa u ha ka byndi, tad ynda un siew ïa kata ka ram.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Haba ki para shakri jong u ki la ïohi te ïa kiei kiei ba la leh, ki la ïasngewsih shibun eh, bad ki la ïawan ban ïathuh ïa kita kiei kiei baroh ba la leh, ha u kynrad jong ki.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Ynda kumta, haba u kynrad jong u, u la khot ha lade ïa u, u la ong ha u, ‘Me u shakri bymman! ïa kata ka ram baroh nga la map ïa me, naba me la kyrpad ïa nga:",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> kam dei ba me ruh men isynei ïa u para shakri jong me, kumba nga la isynei ïa me?’",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> Te u kynrad jong u, u la sngewbitar, bad u la ai noh ïa u ha ki nongpynshitom, haduh ba un da siew ïa ka ram jong u baroh.",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> Kumta ruh, U Kpa jong nga uba ha bneng un leh ïa phi, lada phin ym ïamap uwei pa uwei ïa la u para naduh la ki dohnud.”"
		},
		"19": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Ka la jia ruh haba U Jisu u la lah wai noh ïa kita ki jingong, ba u la leit noh na Galilaïa, bad u la wan ha ki phang ka Judia sha shiliang ka Jordan;",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> te ki paidbah babun ki la ïabud ïa u, bad u la pynkhiah ïa ki hangta.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Te ki Pharisi ki la ïawan ha u, ba ki da ïatynjuh ïa u, bad ki la kylli ïa u, “Ka bit ne em ïa u briew ban pyllait noh ïa ka tnga jong u na ka bynta kano kano ka daw baroh?”",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> U te u la ïathuh bad u la ong, “Phim shym la pule, ba uta uba la thaw ïa ki naduh kaba mynnyngkong u la thaw shynrang bad kynthei ïa ki,",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> bad ba u la ong, ‘Na ka bynta kata, u briew un iehnoh ïa la u kpa bad ïa la ka kmie, bad un ïaineh bad ka tnga jong u; te ki baroh ar ngut kin ïalong kawei ka doh?’",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Kumta, kim long ar ngut shuh, hynrei, kawei ka doh. Namar kata, ïa kaba U Blei u la pynïasoh lem, to u briew wat pynïakhlad.”",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Ki ong ha u, “Te balei ba u Moses u la hukum ban ai ïa ka kot iehnoh, bad ban pyllait noh ïa ka?”",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> U ïathuh ha ki, “U Moses, namar ka dohnud runar jong phi, u la shah ïa phi ban pyllait noh ïa ki tnga jong phi, hynrei, naduh kaba mynnyngkong kam shym la long kumta.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Nga ong ruh ha phi, ba uno uno ruh u ban pyllait noh ïa ka tnga jong u, lymda tang na ka bynta kaba klim, bad un shongkurim ïa kawei pat, u klim keiñ; bad jar uba shongkurim bad kata ïa kaba la pyllait noh, u klim keiñ.”",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Ki synran jong u ki la ong ha u, “Lada ka jinglong u briew bad la ka tnga ka long kumta, kam myntoi keiñ ban shongkurim.”",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> U te u la ong ha ki: “Ki briew baroh kim lah pdiang ïa kata ka ktien, hynrei, tang kita ha kiba la ai bor.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Naba don ki ïunukh ïa kiba la kha kumta na ka kpoh ka kmie, don ki ïunukh ruh ïa kiba la pynlong ïunukh da ki briew, don ki ïunukh ruh kiba la pynlong ïunukh ïa lade na ka bynta ka hima ki bneng. Uta uba lah ban pdiang, to un pdiang.”",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Ynda kumta, ki la wallam ïa ki khunlung ha u, ba un buh ïa la ki kti ha ki, bad ba un duwai, hynrei, ki synran ki la sneng ïa ki.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> U Jisu te u la ong, “Shah ïa ki khunlung ban wan ha nga, bad wat khang ïa ki, naba ïa kiba kum kita, long ka hima ki bneng.”",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Haba u la buh te ïa la ki kti ha ki, u la leit noh nangta.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Ha khmih ruh, uwei u la wan bad u la ong ha U, “Ko Nonghikai babha, ngan leh ïa ka babha aïu, ba ngan ïoh ïa ka jingim bymjukut?”",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> U la ong te ha u, “Balei ba me khot babha ïa nga? Ym don u babha, hynrei, tang uwei, uba U Blei. Hynrei, lada me mon ban leit bsut sha kata ka jingim, to sumar ïa ki hukum.”",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> U la ong ha U, “Ïa kino?” U Jisu te u la ong: “Men ym pynïap, Men ym klim, Men ym tuh, Men ym sakhi lamler,",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Burom ïa la u kpa bad ïa la ka kmie, bad men ieit ïa u paramarjan jong me kumba ïa lade.”",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Uta u samla u la ong ha U, “Ïa kita baroh nga la sumar na myndang khynnah: don aïu pat ba nga dang duna?”",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> U Jisu u la ong ha u, “Lada me mon ban long janai, to khie leit noh, die noh ïa kiei kiei ruh kat kiba me don, to ai ruh ha ki baduk, men ïoh ka jingkynshew te ha bneng; to wan bud ruh ïa nga.”",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Hynrei, haba uta u samla u la ïohsngew ïa kata ka ktien, u la leit noh sngewsih, naba u don shibun ki spah.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> U Jisu te u la ong ha ki synran jong u: “Shisha nga ong ha phi, ba ka da eh noh ïa u riewspah ban leit bsut hapoh ka hima ki bneng.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Pat ruh nga ong ha phi, ba ka kham jem ïa ka ut ban bsut lyngba ïa ka thliew thyrnia, ban ïa u riewspah ban bsut hapoh ka hima U Blei.”",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Hynrei, haba ki synran jong u ki la ïohsngew ïa kata, ki la kyndit eh thred, ki da ong, “Haba kumta, uei ba lah ban lait im?”",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> U Jisu te haba u la khmih ïa ki u la ong ha ki, “Da ki briew kata ka bym lah, hynrei, da U Blei kiei kiei baroh ki long kiba lah.”",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Ynda kumta, u Petros u la ïathuh bad u la ong ha U, “Ha khmih, ngi la iehnoh ïa kiei kiei baroh, bad ngi la ïabud ïa me; haba kumta ngin ïoh aïu?”",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> U Jisu te u la ong ha ki: “Shisha nga ong ha phi, ba phi kiba la ïabud ïa nga, ha ka jingpynthymmai ynda U Khun u briew un shong ha ka khet ka burom jong u, phi ruh phin shong ha ki khat-ar ki khet, ban bishar ïa ki khat-ar ki jaid Israel.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Uno uno baroh ruh uba la iehnoh ïa ki ïing, lane ïa ki hynmen hynbew shynrang ne kynthei, lane ïa u kpa lane ïa ka kmie, lane ïa ka tnga lane ïa ki khun, lane ïa ki bri, na ka bynta ka kyrteng jong nga, un ïoh shispah shah ïa kata, bad un ïoh ka jingim bymjukut ruh.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Hynrei, shibun na kiba long shuwa kin long khatduh; bad ki bakhatduh kin long shuwa."
		},
		"20": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> “Naba ka hima ki bneng ka long kum u briew uba u trai ïing, uba la leit la dang step ban wer ki nongtrei sha ka brisoh jong u.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Haba u la ïakut te bad kita ki nongtrei, shi suka shi sngi, u la phah noh ïa ki sha ka brisoh jong u.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Haba u la leit ruh hamar kaba lai baje, u la ïohi ïa kiwei kiba ïeng kai ha ka jaka ïew;",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> u la ong te ha ki, ‘To khie leit ma phi ruh sha kata ka brisoh, kat kaba biang ruh ngan ai ha phi.’ Ki ruh ki la leit.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Haba u la leit pat hamar kaba hynriew baje  bad kaba khyndai baje, u la leh kumjuh.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Haba u la leit ruh hamar kaba khatwei baje, u la shem ïa kiwei pat kiba ïeng kai; te u la ong ha ki, ‘Balei phi ïaïeng kai hangne baroh shi sngi?’",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Ki la ong ha u, ‘Naba ym don ba la wan wer ïa ngi.’ U la ong te ha ki, ‘To khie leit ma phi ruh sha kata ka brisoh, kat kaba biang ruh phin ïoh.’",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Ynda la janmiet te, uta u trai brisoh u la ong ha u rangbah jong u, ‘Khot ïa kita ki nongtrei bad to ai ha ki, ïa ka bainong jong ki, da sdang naduh ki bakhatduh haduh ki bashuwa.’",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Te haba ki la wan kita kiba hamar kaba khatwei baje, ki la ïoh uwei uwei mar shi suka.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Hynrei, haba ki la wan kita ki bamynshuwa, ki la ïamut ba kin ïoh tam; hynrei, ki ruh ki la ïoh uwei uwei mar shi suka.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Haba ki la pdiang te, ki la ïakren khñium ïa uta u trai ïing,",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> ki ong, ‘Kine ki bakhatduh ki la trei tang shi kynta, pynban me la pynïaryngkat ïa ki bad ngi, kiba la shah ïa kaba eh bad ïa kaba shit ka sngi.’",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> U te u la ïathuh bad u la ong ha uwei na ki, ‘Ko lok, ngam shym leh ka bymhok ïa me; mem shym la ïakut shi suka bad nga?",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> To shim ïa la ka jong to khie leit noh ruh; nga mon ban ai ha une ruh u bakhatduh kumba ha me keiñ.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Kam bit ïa nga ban leh ïa kaba nga mon da la ki jong? Ne ka khmat jong me ka long ka basniew naba nga long u babha?’",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Kumta, ki bakhatduh kin long shuwa, bad ki bashuwa kin long khatduh keiñ. Naba ki long shibun ïa kiba la khot, hynrei, khyndiat ba la jied.”",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Te katba U Jisu u dang leit kiew sha Jerusalem, u la shim kyrpang ïa ki khat-ar ngut ki synran, bad ha kata ka lynti u la ong ha ki,",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> “Ha khmih, ngi ïakiew sha Jerusalem, bad yn die noh ïa U Khun u briew ha ki rangbah lyngdoh bad ki nongthoh; bad kin ïa-pynrem ïa u ïa ka ban ïap,",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> bad kin ai noh ïa u ha ki Jentil ïa ka ban lehbeiñ bad ban sympat, bad ban sahnarphna ruh; hynrei, ha ka balai ka sngi un mihpat.”",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Ynda kumta, ka kmie ki khun u Sebedi ka la wan ha u bad ki khun jong ka, ka da mane dem ïa u, bad ka da pan kaei kaei na u.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> U la ong te ha ka, “Pha kwah aïu?” Ka ong ha u, “To hukum ba kine ar ngut ki khun jong nga kin ïoh shong uwei sha kamon jong me, bad uwei sha kadiang jong me, ha ka hima jong me.”",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> U Jisu te u da ïathuh u la ong, “Phim tip ïa kaei ba phi pan. Phi lah ban dih na ka khuri na kaba nga ngan sa dih? bad ban pynbaptis ïa phi da kata ka jingbaptis da kaba la pynbaptis ïa nga?” Ki la ong ha u, “Ngi lah.”",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> U ïathuh te ha ki, “Phin ïoh dih shisha na ka khuri jong nga, bad da kata ka jingbaptis da kaba la pynbaptis ïa nga, yn pynbaptis ïa phi keiñ, hynrei, ïa ka ban shong sha kamon jong nga bad sha kadiang jong nga, kam long ka jong nga ban ai, hynrei, tang ha kita ïa kiba U Kpa jong nga u la pynkhreh ïa ka.”",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Haba kita ki shiphew ngut ki la ïohsngew ïa kata, ki la ïabitar ïa kita ki ar ngut shipara.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> U Jisu te u la khot ïa ki ha u, bad u la ong, “Phi tip ba ki syiem ki Jentil ki leh trai khlieh ïa ki, bad kita ki bakhraw ki leh don bor halor jong ki:",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> kan ym long kumta hapdeng jong phi: hynrei, lada uno uno ruh u mon ban long bakhraw hapdeng jong phi, to ai ba un long u shakri jong phi;",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> bad lada uno uno ruh u mon ban long rangbah hapdeng jong phi, to ai ba un long u mraw jong phi:",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> kumba U Khun u briew um shym la wan ba yn shakri ïa u, hynrei, ba u un shakri, bad ba un ai ïa la ka jingim ban long ka jingsiewspah ïa kiba bun.”",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Te haba ki leit noh na Jerikho, u paidbah babun u la bud ïa u.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Ha khmih ruh, haba ar ngut ki bamatlah kiba shong harud lynti ki la ïohsngew ba U Jisu u ïaid lait, ki la ïakyrpad jam, ki da ong, “Ko Trai, U Khun u Dabid, to isynei ïa ngi.”",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Uta u paidbah te u la sneng ïa ki, ba kin sngap jar, hynrei, ki la ïakyrpad kham tam, ki da ong, “Ko Trai, U Khun u Dabid, to isynei ïa ngi.”",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Te U Jisu haba u la ïeng, u la khot ïa ki, bad u la ong, “Phi mon ba ngan leh aïu ïa phi?”",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Ki la ïa-ong ha u, “Ko Trai, ban pynpeit ïa ki khmat jong ngi.”",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> U Jisu te ba u la sngewsynei, u la ktah ïa ki khmat jong ki: te kumne kumne ruh ki khmat jong ki, ki la peit, bad ki la ïabud ïa u."
		},
		"21": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Te ynda ki la poi hajan Jerusalem, bad ki la wan ha Bethphage, ha u lum Olib, ynda kumta, U Jisu u la phah ar ngut ki synran,",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> u da ong ha ki, “Khie leit sha katai ka shnong kaba ha marpyrshah jong phi, te kumne kumne ruh phin shem ïa ka kadda ba la teh lem bad u khun; to pyllait ïa ki, to wallam ruh sha nga.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Bad lada uno uno ruh un ong ei ei ha phi, phin ong, ‘U Trai u donkam ïa ki;’ te kumne kumne ruh un phah noh ïa ki.”",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Kata baroh te ka la long, ba yn pyndep ïa kata ba la ong da u nongïathuhlypa, u da ong,",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> “Ïathuh ha ka khun ka Seïon, ‘Ha khmih, U Syiem jong pha u wan ha pha, uba jemnud bad uba shong halor ka kadda, halor u khun ka kadda kaba la ju mlien bad ka lyngkor ruh.’ ”",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Ki synran te haba ki la leit, bad haba ki la leh kumba U Jisu u la hukum ïa ki,",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> ki la wallam ïa ka kadda bad ïa u khun, bad ki la siang ïa la ki jaiñ halor jong ki; bad ki la pynshong halor ïa u.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Te kiba kham bun na uta u paidbah ki la siang ïa la ki jaiñ ha ka lynti; kiwei te ki la khyllad ïa ki tnat na ki dieng, bad ki la siang ha ka lynti.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Kita ki paidbah de kiba ïaid sha shuwa, bad kita kiba bud nadien, ki la ïapyrta, ki da ong, “Hosanna ïa U Khun u Dabid! Long ba la kyrkhu ïa uta uba wan ha ka kyrteng U Trai! Hosanna ha kiba jrong tam eh!”",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Te haba u la wan hapoh Jerusalem, la khihwin kata ka shnong baroh, ki ïa-ong, “Uei une?”",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Kita ki paidbah te ki la ong, “Une u long uta u nongïathuhlypa, U Jisu keiñ, uba na Nasaret ha Galilaïa.”",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> U Jisu te u la leit hapoh ka templ, bad u la beh noh baroh ïa kiba die bad ba thied ha ka templ, bad u la pynkyllon ïa ki miej jong ki nongïapeiñ sbai, bad ïa ki jingshong jong kita kiba die ïa ki paro;",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> bad u la ong ha ki, “La thoh: ‘Ïa ka ïing jong nga yn khot “ka ïing jingduwai,” ’ hynrei, phi, phi la pynlong ka krem nongtuh ïa ka.”",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Ki bamatlah bad ki ba-dkoh ruh ki la wan ha u ha ka templ, bad u la pynkhiah ïa ki.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Haba ki rangbah lyngdoh bad ki nongthoh ki la ïohi ïa kita ki kam phylla kiba u la leh, bad ïa ki khynnah ba ki ïapyrta ha ka templ, bad ba ki ïa-ong ruh, “Hosanna ïa U khun u Dabid!” ki la sngewbitar eh,",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> bad ki la ong ha u, “Me ïohsngew aïu kine ki ïa-ong?” U Jisu te u la ong ha ki, “Ho-oid, phim pat ju pule, “ ‘Na ka shyntur ki khunlung bad kiba dang buiñ me la pynjanai ïa ka jingïaroh?’ ”",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Haba u la iehnoh te ïa ki, u la leit noh na kata ka shnong sha Bethania, bad u la thiah miet hangta.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Te haba u wan pat sha shnong mynstep, u la sngewthngan.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Haba u la ïohi te ïa uwei u dieng Dumbur harud lynti, u la leit ha u, te um shym la shem ei ei ruh em ha u, hynrei, tang ki sla hi; u la ong te ïa u, “U soh un ym long shuh ha me lano lano ruh.” Te kumne kumne ruh u la ïap tyrkhong noh uta u dieng Dumbur.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Te haba ki synran ki la ïohi, ki la kyndit, ki da ong, “Kumno ba une u dieng Dumbur u la ïap tyrkhong noh kumne kumne ruh?”",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> U Jisu te u la ïathuh u la ong ha ki, “Shisha nga ong ha phi, lada phi don ka jingngeit, bad phim sngew-artatien, phin ym leh tang kata ïa kaba la leh ïa uta u dieng Dumbur, hynrei, lada phin ong ha une u lum ruh, ‘Long ba la rat noh, bad ba la noh ruh sha ka duriaw’, yn sa leh kumta.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Bad ïa kiei kiei baroh kat kiba phin pan ha ka jingduwai da kaba ngeit, phin pdiang.”",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Haba u la wan te ha ka templ, ki rangbah lyngdoh bad ki tymmen basan jong u paidbah ki la wan ha u haba u dang hikai, ki da ong, “Da ka bor aïu ba me leh ïa kine kiei kiei ruh? Bad uei ba la ai ïa kane ka bor ha me?”",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Bad U Jisu u da ïathuh u la ong ha ki, “Nga ruh ngan kylli ïa phi kawei ka ktien, lada phin ïathuh ïa kata ha nga, nga ruh ngan ïathuh ha phi da ka bor aïu ba nga leh ïa kine kiei kiei ruh:",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Kata ka jingbaptis u Ïoannis ka long na-ei? na bneng, ne na ki briew?” Ki te ki ïasaid hi paralok, ki ïa-ong, “Lada ngin ong, ‘Na bneng’, un ong ha ngi, ‘Haba kumta balei ba phim shym la ngeit ha u?’",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Hynrei, lada ngin ong, ‘Na ki briew’, ngi sheptieng ïa u paidbah; naba baroh ki ïañiew ïa u Ïoannis kum u nongïathuhlypa.”",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Ki da ïathuh te ki la ong ha U Jisu, “Ngim tip.” U te u la ïathuh ha ki, “Nga ruh ngam ong ha phi da ka bor aïu ba nga leh ïa kine kiei kiei ruh.”",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> “Hynrei, phi mut kumno? U briew uba la don ar ngut ki khun; te u la wan ha uba nyngkong, bad u la ong, ‘Ko khun, khie leit ban trei mynta ha ka brisoh jong nga.’",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Uta, u da ïathuh te u la ong, ‘Ngam treh’, hynrei, hadien u da kylla-ka-bamut, bad u la leit.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> U la wan ruh ha uba hadien, bad u la ong kumjuh. Uta te u da ïathuh u la ong, ‘Ngan sa leit, ko kynrad’, hynrei, um leit.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Uno na kine ar ngut uba la leh ïa ka mon u kpa?” Ki ong ha u, “Uba nyngkong.” U Jisu u ong ha ki, “Shisha nga ong ha phi, ba ki nongkhrong bad ki nuti ki leit ha shuwa jong phi sha ka hima U Blei.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Naba u Ïoannis u la wan ha phi ha ka lynti ka hok, te phim shym la ngeit ha u; hynrei, ki nongkhrong bad ki nuti ki la ngeit ha u, hynrei phi, haba phi la ïohi, phim shym la kylla hadien, ïa ka ban ngeit ha u.",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> “Ha sngew ïa kawei pat ka pharshi: La don u briew uba u trai ïing, uba la thung ka brisoh, bad u la ker ïa ka baroh sawdong, bad u la tih ïa ka jaka tylliat Waiñ ha ka, bad u la tei ka ïing phira, bad u la ai wai ïa ka ha ki nongsumar bri, bad u la leit noh sha kawei pat ka ri.",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> Ynda ka aïom kheit soh ka la jan, u la phah ïa ki shakri jong u ha kita ki nongsumar bri, ban shim ïa ki soh jong ka.",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> Kita ki nongsumar bri te haba ki la ïakem ïa ki shakri jong u, ïa uwei ki la sympat, ïa uwei pat ruh ki la pynïap, ïa uwei pat de ki la lynthem da ki maw.",
			"36": "<sup>36</sup> U la phah pat ïa kiwei kiwei ki shakri kiba kham kor ïa kiba mynnyngkong, te ki la leh kumjuh ïa kita ruh.",
			"37": "<sup>37</sup> Hynrei, ha ka bakhatduh eh u la phah ïa la u khun ha ki, u da ong, ‘Kin ïaburom ïa u khun jong nga.’",
			"38": "<sup>38</sup> Hynrei, haba kita ki nongsumar bri ki la ïohi ïa uta u khun, ki la ïa-ong paralok hi, ‘Une u ban sa long u trai ka brisoh; ïa ngin ïa-pynïap noh ïa u, ngin ïashim ruh ïa ka bynta jong u.’",
			"39": "<sup>39</sup> Te haba ki la kem ïa u, ki la ïashop noh shabar jong kata ka brisoh, bad ki la ïa-pynïap noh.",
			"40": "<sup>40</sup> Namar kata, ynda uta u trai kata ka brisoh un wan, un sa leh aïu ïa kita ki nongsumar bri?”",
			"41": "<sup>41</sup> Ki ong ha u, “Un pynïap sniew khoit keiñ ïa kita ki bymman, bad un sa ai wai ïa ka brisoh ha kiwei pat ki nongsumar, ki ban ai ïa ki soh ha u ha ki aïom jong ki.”",
			"42": "<sup>42</sup> U Jisu u ong ha ki, “Phim ju la pule ha ki jingthoh: “ ‘Ïa u maw ïa uba ki nongtei ki la bred, ïa une la pynlong ha khlieh ka dong: kane ka long na U Trai, bad ka long iphylla ha ki khmat jong ngi?’",
			"43": "<sup>43</sup> “Namar kata, nga ong ha phi, ba yn shim noh ïa ka hima U Blei na phi, bad yn ai ïa ka ha kynja ki briew ki ban pynmih ïa ki soh jong ka.",
			"44": "<sup>44</sup> Jar uba hap te halor une u maw, yn pynmong ïa u: hynrei, jar ha uba un hap, un pynlwet jin ïa u.”",
			"45": "<sup>45</sup> Te haba kita ki rangbah lyngdoh bad ki Pharisi ki la ïohsngew ïa ki pharshi jong u, ki la tip ba u la kren shaphang jong ki.",
			"46": "<sup>46</sup> Haba ki ïawad dong te ban kem ïa u, ki la sheptieng ïa ki paidbah, naba ki la ñiew ïa u kum u nongïathuhlypa."
		},
		"22": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> U Jisu u la ïathuh bad u la ong pat ruh ha ki ha ki pharshi, u da ong,",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> “Ka hima ki bneng ka long kum uwei u syiem, uba la thaw ka jingkhawai shongkurim ïa u khun jong u,",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> bad u la phah ïa la ki shakri ban khot ïa kita ïa kiba la ïawer sha kata ka jingkhawai shongkurim; ki te kim treh ban wan.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> U la phah pat ïa kiwei ki shakri, u da ong, ‘Ïathuh ha kita ïa kiba la ïawer, “Ha khmih, nga la khreh ïa ka jingkhawai jong nga; la pynïap ïa ki masi dab bad ïa kiba sngaid jong nga, bad ïa kiei kiei baroh la khreh; to wan sha ka jingkhawai shongkurim.” ’",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Hynrei, ki kim da suidñiew, ki shu ïaleit noh ruh, uwei sha la ka bri, uwei pat ruh sha la ka jingkhaïi.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Kiwei pat kiba sah te haba ki la kem ïa ki shakri jong u, ki la lehbeiñ bad ki la pynïap ïa ki.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Te haba uta u syiem u la ïohsngew, u la sngewbitar lep keiñ; te haba u la phah ïa ki nongïapom jong u, u la pynduh noh ïa kita ki nongpynïap, bad u la thang ïa ka shnong jong ki.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Ynda kumta, u la ong ha ki shakri jong u, ‘La khreh shisha ïa ka jingkhawai shongkurim, hynrei, kita ïa kiba la ïawer kim long kiba dei.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Namar kata, to khie leit sha kaba ki ïashem ki lad, bad ïa kat kiba phin shem, to khot sha kata ka jingkhawai shongkurim.’",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Kumta, kita ki shakri haba ki la leit sha kita ki lynti, ki la ïalum ïa baroh kat kiba ki la shem, ïa ki bymman bad ïa ki babha ruh: te ki la pyndap ïa kata ka jingkhawai shongkurim da kiba ïashong bam.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> “Haba uta u syiem u la wan hapoh te ban jngoh ïa kiba ïashong bam, u la ïohi hangta ïa u briew u bym shym la kup ka jaiñ ka jingkhawai shongkurim:",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> bad u la ong ha u, ‘Ko lok, kumno ba me la wan hapoh hangne khlem ka jaiñ ka jingkhawai shongkurim?’ U te um nang ong shikyntien ruh.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Ynda kumta, uta u syiem u la ong ha kita ki shakri, ‘To khum ïa u bad kti bad kjat, to rah noh, to bred ruh ïa u sha ka ba-dum kaba kham jngai; hangta yn long kaba lynñiar bad kum dait bniat.’",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Naba bun ki long ba la khot, hynrei, khyndiat ba la jied.”",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Ynda kumta, ki Pharisi ki la leit ban ïasylla kumno ba kin ïoh ïariam ïa u ha ka ktien.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Te kumta, ki la phah ha u ïa ki synran jong ki, lem bad ki nongbud u Herod, ki ïa-ong, “Ko Nonghikai, ngi tip ba me long uba shisha, bad ba me hikai ïa ka lynti U Blei ha kaba shisha, bad ba mem ñiew ïano ruh; naba mem khmih ïa ka khmat ki briew:",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> namar kata, to ong ha ngi, me mut kumno? Ka bit ne em ban ai khajna ha u Kaisar?”",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> U Jisu te ba u la tip ïa ka buit bymman jong ki, u la ong, “Balei phi pynshoi ïa nga, phi kiba arsap?",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> To pyni ïa u sbai khajna ha nga.” Ki la wallam te ha u shi suka.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> U ong ruh ha ki, “Kane ka dur bad ka jingthoh shalor, ki jongno?”",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Ki ong ha u, “Ki jong u Kaisar.” Hangta u ong ha ki, “Naba kumta ai noh ha u Kaisar ïa ki jong u Kaisar, bad ha U Blei ïa ki jong U Blei.”",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Te haba ki la ïohsngew ïa kata, ki la kyndit, bad haba ki la iehnoh ïa u, ki la leit noh.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Ha kata ka sngi ki la wan ha u ki Saddusi, kiba ong ba ka jingmihpat kam long: te ki la kylli ïa u,",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> ki da ong, “Ko Nonghikai, u Moses u la ong, ‘Lada uno uno ruh u ïap noh, u bymdon khun, ba u para jong u un shongkurim ïa ka tnga jong u, bad un pynmih symbai ïa la u hynmen.’",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> La don te bad ngi ki hynñiew ngut shipara: te uba shuwa haba u la shongkurim, u la ïap noh, te naba um don khun, u la iehnoh ïa la ka tnga ha u para jong u.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Kumjuh ruh uba shi sien bud, bad uba ar sien bud, ha ban da lut kita ki hynñiew ngut.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Hadien kita baroh, te ka la ïap noh kata ka kynthei ruh.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Namar kata, ha ka jingmihpat, kan long ka tnga jongno na kine ki hynñiew ngut? naba baroh ki la ïoh kurim ïa ka.”",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> U Jisu u da ïathuh te u la ong ha ki, “Phi bakla, ba phim tip ïa ki jingthoh, lymne ïa ka bor U Blei.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Naba ha kata ka jingmihpat kim ïashongkurim keiñ, lymne ïa-pynshongkurim, hynrei, ki long kum ki angel U Blei ha bneng.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Hynrei, shaphang kata ka jingmihpat ki nongïap, phim shym la pule ïa kata ba la ong U Blei ha phi, u da ong,",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> ‘Nga uba U Blei u Abraham, bad U Blei u Isaak, bad U Blei u Jakob ruh’? U Blei um long U Blei ki baïap, hynrei, jong ki ba-im.”",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Haba kita ki paidbah te ki la ïohsngew ïa kata, ki la sngewphylla na ka jinghikai jong u.",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> Te haba ki Pharisi ki la ïohsngew ba u la pynduh nia ïa ki Saddusi, ki la ïalum lang.",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> Uwei u riewsaid te uba na ki, khnang ban tynjuh ïa u, u la kylli,",
			"36": "<sup>36</sup> “Ko Nonghikai, kano ka hukum kaba khraw kaba ha Ka Hukum?”",
			"37": "<sup>37</sup> U Jisu te u la ïathuh ha u, “ ‘Men ieit ïa U Trai uba U Blei jong me da ka dohnud jong me baroh, bad da ka mynsiem jong me baroh, bad da ka jingmut jong me baroh.’",
			"38": "<sup>38</sup> Kane keiñ ka long ka hukum ka banyngkong bad kaba khraw.",
			"39": "<sup>39</sup> Ka ba-ar ruh ka long kum kata, ‘Men ieit ïa u paramarjan jong me kumba ïa lade.’",
			"40": "<sup>40</sup> Ha kita ki ar hukum la sdien ïa Ka Hukum baroh, bad ïa Ki Nongïathuhlypa.”",
			"41": "<sup>41</sup> Haba ki dang sah lang ki Pharisi, U Jisu u la kylli ïa ki,",
			"42": "<sup>42</sup> u da ong, “Phi mut kumno shaphang U Khrist? U long u khun jongno?” Ki la ïathuh ha u, “U jong u Dabid.”",
			"43": "<sup>43</sup> U ïathuh ha ki, “Haba kumta, kumno ba u Dabid da U Mynsiem u khot ‘U Trai’ ïa u, u da ong,",
			"44": "<sup>44</sup> “ ‘U Trai u la ong ha U Trai jong nga, “To shong sha kamon jong nga, tad ynda ngan pynlong ïa kiba shun ïa me ka jingïuh hapoh ki kjat jong me?” ’",
			"45": "<sup>45</sup> “Lada u Dabid te u khot ‘U Trai’ ïa u, kumno ba u long u khun jong u?”",
			"46": "<sup>46</sup> Ym don te uba lah ban ïathuh shikyntien ïa U, lymne ym don uba shlan kylli shuh ïa U naduh kata ka sngi."
		},
		"23": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Ynda kumta, U Jisu u la ïalap ha ki paidbah, bad ha ki synran jong u,",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> u da ong, “Ki nongthoh bad ki Pharisi ki shong ha ka jingshong u Moses:",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> namar kata, ïa kiei kiei baroh katba kin ong ha phi ban sumar, to phin sumar, bad leh ruh; hynrei, katba kum ki jingleh jong ki, phi wat leh; naba ki ong, te kim leh hi.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Naba ki teh ki jingbah ki bakhia bad kiba eh ban bah, bad ki buh ha ki tyrpeng ki briew; hynrei, ki kim mon ban pynkhih ïa ki da ka shynriah'ti jong ki.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Hynrei, ïa ki jingleh jong ki baroh, ki leh khnang ïa ka ban ïohi da ki briew: namar ki pynpyiar ïa la ki philakteri, bad ki pynkhraw ïa ki rmiang ki jaiñ jong ki,",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> ki ieit ruh ïa ki jaka ba-donnam tam ha ki jingkhawai, bad ïa ki jingshong bakor tam ha ki synagog,",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> bad ïa ki jingnguh de ha ki ïew, bad ba yn khot ruh ïa ki da ki briew, ‘Ko Rabbi.’",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Hynrei, ïa phi wat shah ban khot ‘Rabbi’: naba uwei u long U Nonghikai jong phi uba U Khrist; phi te phi long shipara baroh.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Wat khot ruh ‘u kpa jong phi’ ïano ïano ruh uba ha ka khyndew: naba uwei u long U Kpa jong phi, uba ha bneng.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Lymne wat ai ba yn khot ïa phi ‘ki nongïalam’: naba uwei u long U Nongïalam jong phi, uba U Khrist.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Hynrei, uta uba long kham khraw na phi, un long keiñ u shakri jong phi.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Uno uno ruh de u ban pynkhraw ïa lade, yn pynpoh; uno uno ruh u ban pynpoh te ïa lade, yn pynkhraw.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> “Hynrei, kordit ïa phi, ki nongthoh bad ki Pharisi, kiba arsap! naba phi bam duh ïa ki ïing ki riewkynthei, te phi duwai jlan khnang ban tyllep: namar kata, phin ïoh diang ka jingshitom kaba kham khraw.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Kordit ïa phi, ki nongthoh bad ki Pharisi kiba arsap! naba phi khang ïa ka hima ki bneng ha khmat ki briew: naba phi phim leit hapoh, lymne phim shah ïa kita kiba leit, ban leit hapoh.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Kordit ïa phi, ki nongthoh bad ki Pharisi kiba arsap! naba phi ïaid sawdong ïa ka duriaw bad ka ryngkew ban pynkylla niam ïa uwei; te haba u la kylla, phi pynlong ïa u, u khun dujok uba ar shah ïa phi hi.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> “Kordit ïa phi, ki nongïalam bamatlah! kiba ong ba uno uno ruh u ban smai ha ka templ, kam long ei ei ruh em; hynrei, uno uno ruh u ban smai ha ka ksiar ka templ, u la teh ïa lade.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Phi kiba bieit bad bamatlah! naba kano ka long kaba kham khraw, kata ka ksiar, lane kata ka templ kaba pynkyntang ïa kata ka ksiar?",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Ruh, ba uno uno ruh u ban smai ha ka duwan, kam long ei ei ruh em: hynrei, uno uno ruh u ban smai ha kata ka jingainguh kaba halor jong ka, u teh ïa lade.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Phi kiba bieit bad bamatlah! Naba kano kaba kham khraw, kata ka jingainguh, lane kata ka duwan kaba pynkyntang ïa ka jingainguh?",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Namar kata keiñ, jar uba smai ha kata ka duwan, u smai ha ka, bad ha kiei kiei baroh kiba halor jong ka.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Jar uba smai ruh ha ka templ, u smai ha ka, bad ha uta uba shong sah ha ka.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Jar uba smai ruh ha ka bneng, u smai ha ka khet U Blei, bad ha uta uba shong halor jong ka.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> “Kordit ïa phi, ki nongthoh bad ki Pharisi kiba arsap! naba phi ai ïa kaba shiphew na ka pudina, bad na ka dill, bad na ka kummin, bad phi iehnoh te ïa kita kiei kiei kiba kham khia ki jong ka hukum, ïa ka hok, bad ïa ka jingisynei, bad ïa ka jingngeit; ka la dei keiñ ïa phi ban leh ïa kine, bad ban ym iehnoh ïa kita kiwei.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Phi ki nongïalam bamatlah, kiba jiar noh ïa u 'kain rit, bad kiba nguid pynban ïa ka ut!",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> “Kordit ïa phi, ki nongthoh bad ki Pharisi kiba arsap! naba phi pynkhuid ïa kaba shabar ïa ka khuri bad ïa ka pliang, hynrei, shapoh ki dap da ka jinglute bad ka jinglalot.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Me u Pharisi bamatlah! to pynkhuid shuwa ïa kaba shapoh ka khuri bad ka pliang, ba kaba shabar jong ki kan ïoh long khuid ruh.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> “Kordit ïa phi, ki nongthoh bad ki Pharisi kiba arsap! naba phi long kum ki jingtep ba la pynlieh, kiba imat ibha shisha na shabar, hynrei, shapoh kiba dap da ki shyieng jong ki baïap, bad da ka jakhlia baroh.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Kumta phi ruh, na shabar phi pynpaw kum ki bahok ha ki briew, hynrei, shapoh phi la dap da kaba arsap bad da ka basniew.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> “Kordit ïa phi, ki nongthoh bad ki Pharisi kiba arsap! naba phi tei ïa ki jingtep ki nongïathuhlypa, bad phi pynibha ïa ki maw jingtep ki bahok,",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> bad phi ong, ‘Lada ngi la long ha ki sngi ka rta ki kpa jong ngi, ngin ym da la long kiba ïasylla lem bad ki ha ka jingpynïap ïa kita ki nongïathuhlypa.’",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Kumta phi ïaphla ïa lade, ba phi long ki khun jong kita kiba la pynïap ïa ki nongïathuhlypa.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Te to pyndap noh phi ïa kata ka jingthew ki kpa jong phi.",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> A ki bseiñ! Ki khun ki ksiew ki 'seiñpuh! kumno phin ïohlait na ka jingshitom ka dujok?",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> Naba kumta, ha khmih, nga phah ha phi ïa ki nongïathuhlypa, bad ïa ki riewstad, bad ïa ki nongthoh ruh; te ïa kiba na ki phin pynïap noh, bad phin sahnarphna; bad ïa kiwei na ki phin sympat ha ki synagog jong phi, bad phin behbeiñ ruh na ka shnong sha ka shnong:",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> kumta, kan wanhap ha phi keiñ ïa ka snam bahok baroh ïa kaba la pynmih noh ha ka khyndew, naduh ka snam u Abel u bahok haduh ka snam u Sakharaïah u khun u Barakhaïah, ïa uba phi la pynïap marpdeng ka jaka kyntang bad ka duwan.",
			"36": "<sup>36</sup> Shisha nga ong ha phi, ba kine kiei kiei baroh kin wanhap ha kane ka pateng bynriew.",
			"37": "<sup>37</sup> “A! Jerusalem, Jerusalem! pha kaba pynïap noh ïa ki nongïathuhlypa, bad kaba lynthem maw ïa kita ïa kiba la phah ha pha! katno sien ba nga la kwah ban kdup ïa ki khun jong pha, kumba ka syiar ka kdup ïa ki khun jong ka hapoh ki thapniang jong ka, phi te phim mon.",
			"38": "<sup>38</sup> Ha khmih, ïa ka ïing jong phi la iehnoh ha phi ka ïingjah.",
			"39": "<sup>39</sup> Naba nga ong ha phi, phin ym ïohi shuh ïa nga naduh mynta, tad ynda phin ong, ‘Long ba la kyrkhu ïa uta uba wan ha ka kyrteng U Trai.’ ”"
		},
		"24": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Te U Jisu u la mih noh, bad u la leit noh na ka templ; te ki synran jong u ki la wan ïa ka ban pyni ha u ïa ki jingtei jong ka templ.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> U Jisu te u la ong ha ki, “Phim ïohi ïa kine kiei kiei baroh? Shisha nga ong ha phi, Yn ym iehnoh hangne u maw halor u maw, ïa u ban ym pynhap noh.”",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Te haba u dang shong halor u lum ki Olib, ki synran ki la wan ha u jar jar, ki ïa-ong, “To ïathuh ha ngi, lano ba kine kiei kiei ruh kin long? bad kaba kumno ka dak ka jingwan jong me, bad kaba wai noh kane ka pyrthei?”",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Te U Jisu u la ïathuh bad u la ong ha ki, “To sumar ba uno uno ruh un ym shukor ïa phi.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Naba bun kin ïawan ha ka kyrteng jong nga, ki da ong, ‘Ma nga uba U Khrist’, bad kin shukor ïa shibun.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Bad phin sa ïohsngew shaphang ki thma bad ki jingbna ïa ki thma: to sumar phi wat sngewkhuslai: naba ka dei ba kine kiei kiei baroh kin long: hynrei, ka bakut kam pat la jia.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Naba ka kynja bynriew kan ïeng ïaleh ïa ka kynja bynriew, bad ka hima ruh ïa ka hima; bad kin long ki 'nemsniew bad ki jingïapthem ruh, bad ki jingkhynñiuh jumai ha shibun ki jaka.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Hynrei, kine baroh ki long tang ki jingsdang ki jingjynjar.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> “Ynda kumta, kin ai noh ïa phi ha ka shitom, bad kin ïa-pynïap noh ïa phi; bad phin long kiba la shun da ki kynja bynriew baroh na ka bynta ka kyrteng jong nga.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Ynda kumta te, shibun kin ïathut, bad kin ïadie paralok, bad kin ïashun paralok.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Bun ki nongïathuhlypa lamler ruh kin mih, bad kin shukor ïa shibun.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Te namar ba ka pop kan man bun, ka jingieit kiba bun kan man khriat.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Hynrei, jar uba da ïaineh haduh ka bakut, uta keiñ u ban ïohlait im.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Te ïa kane ka gospel jong ka hima yn ïalap ha ka pyrthei baroh, ïa ka ban long ka jingphla ha ki kynja bynriew baroh; ynda kumta keiñ, kan jia kata ka bakut.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> “Namar kata, ynda phin ïohi ïa kata ka jingijli bapynduh, ba la ong shaphang jong ka da u Daniel u nongïathuhlypa, ba ka da ïeng ha ka jaka bakhuid,” (Jar uba pule un da sngap),",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> “ynda kumta, kita kiba ha ka Judia to ai kin ïaphet ïap noh sha ki lum.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Jar uba halor ïing, wat ai un hiar ban shim ei ei ruh na ka ïing jong u.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Jar uba ha ka lyngkha ruh, wat ai un wan kylla dien pat ban shim ïa ki jaiñkup jong u.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Hynrei, kordit ïa kita kiba la punkhun bad ïa kiba ai buiñ ha kita ki sngi!",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Hynrei, phin duwai ba kata ka jingphet ïap noh jong phi kan ym long myntlang, lymne ha ka sngi Sabbaton.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Naba hangta, ka kordit bah kan long, kat kaba ym pat ju long naduh myndanglong ka pyrthei haduh mynta, em, lymne kan ym long shuh ruh.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Te lymda pyndkut noh ïa kita ki sngi, kan ym lait im kawei ka doh: hynrei, na ka bynta kiba la jied, yn pyndkut noh ïa kita ki sngi.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Ynda kumta, lada uei uei ruh un ong ha phi, ‘Ha khmih, hangne uba U Khrist,’ lane ‘hangtai;’ phi wat ngeit.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Naba ki khrist lamler, bad ki nongïathuhlypa lamler, kin mih, bad kin pyni ïa ki dak ki bakhraw bad ki jingphylla, kat ban shukor, lada lah, wat ïa kiba la jied.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Ha khmih, nga la ïathuhlypa ha phi.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Namar kata, lada kin ong ha phi, ‘Ha khmih, u don ha ri khlaw;’ phi wat mih noh: ‘Ha khmih, u don ha ki pulit ba jar jar:’ phi wat ngeit.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Naba kumba ka mih noh ka leilieh na mihngi, bad ka shai haduh sepngi, kumta ruh kan long ha kata ka jingwan U Khun u briew.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Naba ha-ei ha-ei ruh ha kaba don ka metïap, hangta keiñ kin ïalang ki pukni.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> “Kumne kumne ruh, hadien ka jynjar kita ki sngi, ïa ka sngi yn pyndum, bad u bnai un ym ai la ka jingshai, bad ki khlur kin hap na bneng, bad yn pynkhynñiuh ïa ki bor ki bneng.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Ynda kumta te, ka dak U Khun u briew kan paw ha bneng; te hangta ki jaid bynriew baroh ka pyrthei kin ïalynñiar lympat, haba kin ïohi ba u wan U Khun u briew ha ki lyoh bneng da ka bor bad ka burom bakhraw.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Un phah noh ruh ïa ki angel jong u da ka jingsawa bakhraw ka turoi, bad kin ïalum lang ïa kiba la jied jong u na ki saw lyer, naduh ki bakut ki bneng haduh ki bakut jong ki.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> “To nang te ïa ka pharshi na u dieng Dumbur: haba ka tnat jong u ka la khie lung, bad ka sei sla, phi tip ba ka lyiur ka la jan;",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> kumjuh ma phi ruh, haba phin ïohi ïa kine kiei kiei baroh, to tip ba ka long hajan, ha ki jingkhang.",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> Shisha nga ong ha phi, kane ka pateng bynriew kan ym leit noh, tad ynda la pyndep noh ïa kine kiei kiei baroh.",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> Ka bneng bad ka khyndew kin leit noh, hynrei, ki ktien jong nga kin ym leit noh satia.",
			"36": "<sup>36</sup> “Hynrei, shaphang kata ka sngi bad kata ka por ruh ym don ba tip, lymne ki angel ki bneng, hynrei, tang U Kpa jong nga hi.",
			"37": "<sup>37</sup> Te kumba la long ki sngi u Noah, kumta ruh kan long kata ka jingwan U Khun u briew.",
			"38": "<sup>38</sup> Naba kumba ka la long ha kita ki sngi kiba mynshuwa kata ka jingshlei ba ki ïabam ki ïadih, ba ki ïashongkurim ki ïa-pynshongkurim, tad ynda kata ka sngi ba u Noah u la leit hapoh kata ka ïinglieng;",
			"39": "<sup>39</sup> bad kim shym la suidñiew tad ynda ka la wan kata ka jingshlei, bad ka la rong noh ïa ki baroh; kumta ruh kan long kata ka jingwan U Khun u briew.",
			"40": "<sup>40</sup> Ynda kumta, ar ngut kin ïadon ha ka lyngkha; ïa uwei la shim noh, te ïa uwei pat la iehnoh.",
			"41": "<sup>41</sup> Ar ngut kin ïashong tylliat ha ka ïing tylliat: ïa kawei la shim noh, te ïa kawei pat la iehnoh.",
			"42": "<sup>42</sup> Namar kata, to sharai, naba phim tip ha kano ma ka sngi ba u wan U Trai jong phi.",
			"43": "<sup>43</sup> Ïa kane te phi tip, ba lada u trai ïing u la tip ha kano ka por ba un wan u nongtuh, un da la ap, bad un ym da shah ban prat ïa ka ïing jong u.",
			"44": "<sup>44</sup> Naba kumta, phi ruh to long kiba la kloi; naba ha ka por ba phim mut, u wan U Khun u briew.",
			"45": "<sup>45</sup> “Naba kumta, uno uba long u shakri bangeit bad bastad, ïa uba u kynrad jong u, u la buh halor ki ba-ha-ïing jong u ïa ka ban ai ha ki, ïa ka jingbam ha ka por kaba biang?",
			"46": "<sup>46</sup> Suk uta u shakri, ïa uba u kynrad jong u haba u wan un shem ba u leh kumta.",
			"47": "<sup>47</sup> Shisha nga ong ha phi, ba un buh ïa u halor kiei kiei baroh kiba u don.",
			"48": "<sup>48</sup> Hynrei, lada uta u shakri bymman te un ong ha la ka dohnud, ‘U kynrad jong nga u tud ban wan;’",
			"49": "<sup>49</sup> bad u sdang ban shoh ïa ki para shakri jong u, bad ban ïabam ïadih ruh lem bad ki babuaid;",
			"50": "<sup>50</sup> u kynrad uta u shakri un wan ha ka sngi ha kaba um mut, bad ha ka por ha kaba um tip;",
			"51": "<sup>51</sup> te un shop noh da sympat ïa u, bad un buh ïa ka bynta jong u lem bad kiba arsap; hangta yn long kaba lynñiar bad kum dait bniat."
		},
		"25": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> “Ynda kumta, ka hima ki bneng kan long kum ki shiphew ngut ki theisotti, kiba haba ki la shim ïa ki sharak jong ki, ki la mih noh ïa ka ban leit tan ïa u nongleit-kurim.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> San ngut te na ki, ki la long ki bastad bad san ngut ki babieit.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Kita ki babieit, haba ki la shim ïa ki sharak jong ki, kim shym la shim ruh ïa ka umphniang lem bad ki.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Hynrei, kita ki bastad ki la shim ïa ka umphniang ha ki khulpi jong ki lem bad ki sharak jong ki.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Haba uta u nongleit-kurim u pyntud, ki la samthiah baroh, bad ki la ïohthiah.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Hynrei, mynshiteng synñia la long ka jingpyrta, ‘Ha khmih, u wan u nongleit-kurim! to mih ban leit tan ïa u.’",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Ynda kumta, kita ki theisotti baroh ki la ïaïeng, bad ki la shna ïa ki sharak jong ki.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Kita ki babieit te ki la ong ha kita ki bastad, ‘To ai ha ngi na ka umphniang jong phi, naba ki sharak jong ngi kin sa lip.’",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Hynrei, kita ki bastad ki la ïathuh, ki ïa-ong, ‘Ba ïoh kan ym dap ïa ngi bad ïa phi ruh, to khie leit keiñ sha kita kiba die, bad da thied ïa lade.’",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Haba ki dang ïaleit ban thied te, u la wan uta u nongleit-kurim; te kita kiba la kloi ki la leit hapoh lem bad u sha ka jingkhawai shongkurim; te la khang ïa ka jingkhang.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Hadien kata te, ki la wan ruh kita kiwei ki theisotti, ki da ong, ‘Ko kynrad, kynrad, to plie ïa ngi!’",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> U la ïathuh te u la ong, ‘Shisha nga ong ha phi, ngam ithuh ïa phi.’",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Namar kata, to sharai, naba phim tip lymne ïa ka sngi lymne ïa ka por ha kaba u wan U Khun u briew.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> “Naba kumta ka long kumba u briew u ban sa leit jingleit sha kawei ka ri, uba la khot ïa ki shakri jong u bad u la ai ha ki, ïa ki spah jong u.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Te ha uwei u la ai san talent, ha uwei pat ruh ar, ha uwei pat ruh kawei; ha uwei pa uwei katba kum ka buit jong u hi: te kumne kumne ruh u la leit sha la ka jingleit.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Ynda kumta, uta uba la ïoh diang ïa ki san talent, u la leit khaïi bad ki, bad u la pynman ïa kiwei ki san talent.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Kumjuh ruh uta u ba-ar, uta ruh u la ïohnong kiwei pat ar.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Uta te uba la ïoh diang ïa kawei, u la leit tih thliew ha ka khyndew, bad u la buhrieh noh ïa u sbai u kynrad jong u.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Te ynda la kham slem, u kynrad jong kita ki shakri u wan, u ïakheiñ bad ki.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Ynda kumta, uta uba la ïoh diang ïa ki san talent u la wan, bad u la wallam ïa ki san tylli kiwei ki talent, u da ong, ‘Ko kynrad, me la ai ha nga san talent; ha khmih nga la ïohnong san tylli kiwei ki talent.’",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Te u kynrad jong u, u la ong ha u, ‘Bha, me u shakri babha bad bangeit: me la minot ha kiba khyndiat, ngan buh ïa me halor kiba bun: to khie leit shapoh ka jingkmen u kynrad jong me.’",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Uta uba la ïoh diang ïa ki ar talent ruh u la wan, u la ong, ‘Ko kynrad, me la ai ha nga ar talent: ha khmih nga la ïohnong ar tylli kiwei ki talent.’",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> U kynrad jong u, u la ong ha u, ‘Bha me u shakri babha bad bangeit; me la minot ha kiba khyndiat, ngan buh ïa me halor kiba bun: to khie leit shapoh ka jingkmen u kynrad jong me.’",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> U la wan ruh de uta uba la ïoh diang ïa kawei ka talent, u la ong, ‘Ko kynrad, nga la tip ba me long u briew uba eh, uba ot na kaba mem shym la bet, bad uba lum na kaba mem shym la pynsaphred:",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> kumta, ba nga la sheptieng, nga la leit buhrieh ïa ka talent jong me ha ka khyndew; ha khmih, me la ïoh la ka jong.’",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> U kynrad jong u te u da ïathuh u la ong ha u, ‘Me u shakri bymman bad ba alhia, me la tip ba nga ot na kaba ngam shym la bet, bad ba nga lum na kaba ngam shym la pynsaphred;",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> ka la dei ïa me namar kata ban ai ïa u sbai jong nga ha ki ba ai sut, ba haba nga wan te ngan da ïoh shim ïa la ka jong bad ïa ka sut.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Namar kata, to shim noh na u ïa kata ka talent, to ai ruh ha uta uba don ki shiphew talent.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Naba ha uwei pa uwei uba don, yn ai, un ïoh kaba dap tam ruh; hynrei, na uta u bymdon, wat ïa kata kaba u don yn shim noh na u.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> To bred noh te ïa uta u shakri bymmyntoi sha ka ba-dum kaba kham jngai; hangta yn long kaba lynñiar bad kum dait bniat.’",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> “Ynda U Khun u briew un wan te ha ka burom jong u, bad ki angel bakhuid baroh lem bad u, ynda kumta, un shong halor ka khet ka burom jong u,",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> bad yn ïalum lang ïa ki bynriew baroh ha khmat jong u; bad un pynïakhlad ïa ki uwei na uwei pat, kumba u nongaplangbrot u pynïakhlad ïa ki langbrot na ki blang;",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> te un buh ïa ki langbrot sha kamon jong u, hynrei, ïa ki blang sha kadiang.",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> Ynda kumta, U Syiem un ong ha kita sha kamon jong u, ‘To wan phi ïa kiba la kyrkhu jong U Kpa jong nga, to ïoh ïa ka hima ïa kaba la pynkhreh keiñ ïa phi na myndanglong ka pyrthei.",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> Namar nga la thngan, te phi la ai ha nga ban bam; nga la sliang, te phi la ai dih ïa nga; nga la long nongwei, te phi la khot lem ïa nga;",
			"36": "<sup>36</sup> ba lyngkhuit, te phi la pynkup jaiñ ïa nga; nga la pang, te phi la wan sumar ïa nga; nga la long ha ka byndi, te phi la wan ha nga.’",
			"37": "<sup>37</sup> Ynda kumta, kita ki bahok kin ïathuh ha u, kin ong, ‘Ko Trai, mynno ba ngi la ïohi ba me la thngan, bad ngi la ai bam? lane ba me la sliang, bad ngi la ai dih?",
			"38": "<sup>38</sup> mynno ruh ba ngi la ïohi ba me long nongwei, bad ngi la khot lem ïa me? lane ba lyngkhuit, bad ngi la pynkup jaiñ?",
			"39": "<sup>39</sup> mynno te ba ngi la ïohi ba me pang, lane ha ka byndi, bad ngi la wan ha me?’",
			"40": "<sup>40</sup> Uta U Syiem te un ïathuh bad un ong ha ki, ‘Shisha nga ong ha phi, ha kaba phi la leh ïa ka ha uwei u barit tam na kine ki para jong nga, phi la leh keiñ ha nga.’",
			"41": "<sup>41</sup> Ynda kumta, un ong ha kita ruh sha kadiang, ‘To khie leit noh na nga, phi ïa kiba la tim, sha ka ding ka bymjukut, ïa kaba la buh lypa ïa u Soitan bad ïa ki angel jong u!",
			"42": "<sup>42</sup> Namar nga la thngan, te phim shym la ai ha nga ban bam; nga la sliang, te phim shym la ai dih ïa nga;",
			"43": "<sup>43</sup> nga la long nongwei, te phim shym la khot lem ïa nga; ba lyngkhuit, te phim shym la pynkup jaiñ ïa nga; bapang, bad ha ka byndi ruh, te phim shym la wan sumar ïa nga.’",
			"44": "<sup>44</sup> Ynda kumta, ki ruh kin ïathuh ha u, kin ong, ‘Ko Trai, mynno ba ngi la ïohi ba me la thngan, lane ba me la sliang, lane nongwei, lane ba lyngkhuit, lane bapang, lane ha ka byndi, bad ngim shym la shakri ïa me?’",
			"45": "<sup>45</sup> Ynda kumta, un ïathuh ha ki, un ong, ‘Shisha nga ong ha phi, ha kaba phim shym la leh ïa ka ha uwei na kine ki barit tam, phim shym la leh keiñ ha nga.’",
			"46": "<sup>46</sup> Kine kin leit noh te sha ka shitom bymjukut, hynrei, ki bahok sha ka jingim bymjukut.”"
		},
		"26": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Ka la jia ruh, haba U Jisu u la lah wai noh ïa kita ki ktien baroh, u la ong ha ki synran jong u,",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> “Phi tip ba ynda sa ar sngi kan long Ka Niam Ka Jinglait; ynda kumta, yn ai noh ïa U Khun u briew ïa ka ban sahnarphna ïa u.”",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Ynda kumta, ki la ïalang ki rangbah lyngdoh bad ki nongthoh bad ki tymmen basan jong u paidlang ha ka ïingbah u rangbah lyngdoh, ïa uba ki khot “u Kaïaphas”;",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> te ki la ïasylla ba kin ïoh kem tuh ïa U Jisu, ba kin ïoh pynïap noh.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Hynrei, ki la ïa-ong, “Ym ha Ka Niam Ka Jinglait, ba ïoh ka jingkhihwin kan long hapdeng u paidbah.”",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Haba U Jisu u dang don te ha Bethania, ha ïing uta u Simon u bapang 'ñiangthohlieh,",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> ka la wan ka kynthei ha U kaba don ka dabi alabaster ka jingsleh ka bakordor eh, bad ka la theh ha ka khlieh jong U haba U shong bam.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Haba ki synran jong u te ki la ïohi, ki la sngewbitar, ki da ong, “Ïa ka ban lei kane ka jinglehnohei?",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Namar lah eh ban die bun sbai ïa kane ka jingsleh, bad ban ïoh ai ha ki baduk.”",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Haba U Jisu u la tip te, u la ong ha ki, “Balei phi pynkhuslai ïa ka kynthei? namar ka la leh ïa ka jingleh babha ïa nga:",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> naba phi ïoh ïa ki baduk lem bad phi ha la ka sngi, hynrei, ïa nga phim ïoh keiñ ha la ka sngi.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Naba haba ka la theh ïa kane ka jingsleh ha ka met jong nga, ka la leh keiñ ïa ka ban kyllan musla ban tep ïa nga.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Shisha nga ong ha phi, shano shano ruh sha kaba yn ïalap ïa kane ka gospel ha ka pyrthei baroh, yn ïathuh ruh ïa kane kaba ka la leh, ïa ka ban kynmaw ïa ka.”",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Ynda kumta, uwei na ki khat-ar ngut, ïa uba ki khot “u Judas Iskariot”, u la leit ha kita ki rangbah lyngdoh,",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> u la ong, “Phin ai aïu ha nga, ba ngan die noh ïa U ha phi?” Ki la thew te ha u laiphew ki sbai rupa.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Naduh kata te u la wad dong kaba bit ba un ai noh ïa U.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Te ha ka sngi ka banyngkong U Kpu Bakhlem Thiat, ki synran ki la wan ha U Jisu, ki da ong, “Me mon hangno ba ngin ïakhreh ïa me ban bam ïa Ka Niam Ka Jinglait?”",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> U la ïathuh te, “To khie leit shapoh kato ka nongbah sha uta u briew, bad ong ha u, ‘U Nonghikai u ong, “Ka por jong nga ka la jan; ngan rakhe ïa Ka Niam Ka Jinglait ha ïing jong me, lem bad ki synran jong nga.” ’ ”",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Ki synran te ki la leh kumba U Jisu u la batai ïa ki; bad ki la ïakhreh ïa kata Ka Niam Ka Jinglait.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Haba la janmiet te, u la ïashong bam bad kita ki khat-ar ngut.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Te haba ki dang ïabam, u la ong, “Shisha nga ong ha phi, ba uwei na phi un die noh ïa nga.”",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Te ki la sngewsih eh, bad ki la sdang uwei pa uwei na ki ban ïa-ong ha u, “Ma nga, ko Trai?”",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> U da ïathuh u la ong, “Uta uba pynngam ïa la ka kti ha ka pliang lem bad nga, uta keiñ u ban die noh ïa nga.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> U Khun u briew shisha un sa leit kumba la thoh shaphang jong u, hynrei, kordit ïa uta u briew da uba yn die noh ïa U Khun u briew! ka la bha ïa uta u briew lada ym shym la kha satia ïa u.”",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Ynda kumta, u Judas uba la die noh ïa U, u da ïathuh u la ong, “Dei ma nga, ko Kynrad?” U la ïathuh ha u, “Me la ong keiñ.”",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Te haba ki dang ïabam, U Jisu u la shim ïa u kpu, bad ynda u la nguh, u la kdiah; bad u la ai ha ki synran, u la ong, “To shim, to bam, une u long ka met jong nga.”",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Ynda u la shim ïa ka khuri ruh, bad ba u la nguh, u la ai ha ki, u da ong, “To dih na kane phi baroh;",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> naba kane ka long ka snam jong nga, kaba ka jong ka jutang bathymmai, ïa kaba yn sa pynmih noh na ka bynta kiba bun, ïa ka ban map ki pop.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Nga ong ruh ha phi, ba ngan ym dih shuh naduh mynta na kane ka umsoh u dieng Waiñ, tad ynda kata ka sngi ba ngan dih thymmai ïa ka lem bad phi ha ka hima U Kpa jong nga.”",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Te haba ki la ïarwai salm, ki la leit noh sha u lum ki Olib.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Mynkata U Jisu u la ong ha ki, “Phi baroh phin thut na nga ha kane ka miet, naba la thoh: ‘Ngan shoh ïa u nongsharai bad yn pynsaphred ïa ki langbrot jong ka kynhun.’",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Hynrei, hadien ba nga la mihpat, ngan leit sha shuwa jong phi sha Galilaïa.”",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> U Petros u da ïathuh te u la ong ha U, “Lada ki baroh kin thut na me, nga te ngan ym thut lano lano ruh.”",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> U Jisu u la ong ha u, “Shisha nga ong ha me, ba ha kane ka miet, shuwa ba um pat riew u syiar, men len ïa nga lai sien.”",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> U Petros u la ong ha U, “La ka dei ïa nga ban ïap noh lem bad me, ngan ym len satia ïa me.” Kumjuh ruh ki la ong ki synran baroh.",
			"36": "<sup>36</sup> Ynda kumta, U Jisu u la wan bad ki sha ka jaka ba ki khot “Gethsemane”, bad u ong ha ki synran, “To ïashong hangne, katba ngan da leit hangtai ban duwai.”",
			"37": "<sup>37</sup> Te haba u la shim lem bad u ïa u Petros bad ïa ki ar ngut ki khun u Sebedi, u la sdang ban sngewsih bad ban sngewkordit eh.",
			"38": "<sup>38</sup> Haba kumta u la ong ha ki, “Ka mynsiem jong nga ka sngewpisa eh, kat ban sa ïap; ïaishong hangne, to ïa-ap ruh lem bad nga.”",
			"39": "<sup>39</sup> Haba u la leit sha shuwa khyndiat, u la dem da pyllup bad u la duwai, u da ong, “Ko Kpa jong nga, lada don lad, to ai ba kane ka khuri kan ïohlait noh na nga. Pynban, ym kumba nga mon ma nga, hynrei, tang kumba me mon.”",
			"40": "<sup>40</sup> U wan te ha kita ki synran, bad u shem ba ki la ïohthiah, bad u la ong ha u Petros, “Wa! phim lah ban ïa-ap lem bad nga shi por?",
			"41": "<sup>41</sup> To sharai, to duwai ruh, ba phin ym leit shapoh ka jingpynshoi. Ka mynsiem shisha ka smat, hynrei, ka doh ka tlot.”",
			"42": "<sup>42</sup> Te ha ka ba-ar sien pat u la leit noh, bad u la duwai, u da ong, “Ko Kpa jong nga, lada ym don lad ïa kane ka khuri ban lait noh na nga lymda nga dih ïa ka, to long ka mon jong me.”",
			"43": "<sup>43</sup> Haba u la wan te, u shem ba ki la ïohthiah pat, naba ki khmat jong ki, ki la khia.",
			"44": "<sup>44</sup> Te haba u la iehnoh ïa ki, u la leit noh pat, u la duwai ka balai sien, u da ong pat ïa kijuh ki ktien.",
			"45": "<sup>45</sup> Ynda kumta, u la wan ha ki synran, bad u la ong ha ki, “To nang thiah mynta, to jahthait ruh. Ha khmih ka por ka la jan, te yn die noh ïa U Khun u briew ha ki kti ki bapop.",
			"46": "<sup>46</sup> To ïeng, ngin ïaleit noh. Ha khmih, uba die noh ïa nga u la jan.”",
			"47": "<sup>47</sup> Haba U dang kren ruh, ha khmih u Judas, uba uwei na ki khat-ar ngut, u la wan, bad u paidbah babun lem bad u bad ki waitlam bad ki diengduh ruh, na ki rangbah lyngdoh bad na ki tymmen basan jong u paidbah.",
			"48": "<sup>48</sup> Uta te uba la die noh ïa U, u la lah ai ka dak ha ki, u da ong, “Ïa uba ngan doh, uta long ma u, to phin kem ïa u.”",
			"49": "<sup>49</sup> Te kumne kumne ruh haba u la wan ha U Jisu, u la ong, “Khublei, ko Kynrad”, bad u la doh ïa U.",
			"50": "<sup>50</sup> U Jisu te u la ong ha u, “Ko lok, me wan ïa-ei?” Ha kata ki la wan, ki la buh ïa la ki kti ha U Jisu, bad ki la kem ïa u.",
			"51": "<sup>51</sup> Ha khmih ruh, uwei na kita kiba bad U Jisu, haba u la kner ïa la ka kti, u la sei noh ïa ka waitlam jong u, bad u la pom ïa u shakri u rangbah lyngdoh, bad u la mait noh ïa ka shkor jong u.",
			"52": "<sup>52</sup> Haba kumta U Jisu u la ong ha u, “To thep noh ïa ka waitlam jong me ha ka jaka jong ka; naba kita baroh kiba shim ïa ka waitlam kin ïap noh da ka waitlam.",
			"53": "<sup>53</sup> Me mut ba ngam lah mynta ban duwai ïa U Kpa jong nga, ba un phah ïarap ïa nga wat mynta da ki khat-ar paidbah tam ki angel?",
			"54": "<sup>54</sup> Lada kumta te, kumno ba yn pyndep ïa kita ki jingthoh, kiba ong ba ka dei ban long kumne?”",
			"55": "<sup>55</sup> Ha kata ka por, U Jisu u la ong ha kita ki paidbah, “Kumba ïa u nongtuh phi la mih bad ki waitlam bad ki diengduh ban kem ïa nga? Ha la ka sngi bad phi nga ju shong hikai ha ka templ, te phim shym la kem ïa nga.",
			"56": "<sup>56</sup> Hynrei, kane baroh te ka la long ba yn pyndep ïa ki jingthoh ki nongïathuhlypa.” Ynda kumta, ki synran baroh haba ki la iehnoh ïa u, ki la phet noh.",
			"57": "<sup>57</sup> Kita te kiba la kem ïa U Jisu ki la ïalam noh ïa u sha ka ïing u Kaïaphas u rangbah lyngdoh, ha kaba ki la ïalang ki nongthoh bad ki tymmen basan.",
			"58": "<sup>58</sup> U Petros te u la bud ïa U na jngai haduh ka phyllaw u rangbah lyngdoh; te haba u la leit hapoh u la shong lem bad ki shakri ban ïohi ïa ka bakut.",
			"59": "<sup>59</sup> Ki rangbah lyngdoh te bad ki tymmen basan bad ka dorbar baroh ruh, ki la ïawad ïa ka sakhi lamler pyrshah ïa U Jisu, ba kin ïoh pynïap ïa U;",
			"60": "<sup>60</sup> hynrei, kim shem, la ki la wan ruh shibun ki nongsakhi lamler. Hynrei, hadien la wan ar ngut ki nongsakhi lamler,",
			"61": "<sup>61</sup> ki la ong, “Une u briew u la ong, ‘Nga lah ban pynjot ïa ka templ, bad ban tei pat lai sngi ïa ka.’ ”",
			"62": "<sup>62</sup> Uta u rangbah lyngdoh haba u la ïeng te, u la ong ha U, “Mem ïathuh ei ei ruh em? kine ki ïasakhi aïu pyrshah ïa me?”",
			"63": "<sup>63</sup> Hynrei, U Jisu u la shu sngap. Te u rangbah lyngdoh u da ïathuh u la ong ha U, “Nga pynsmai ïa me ha U Blei U Ba-im, ba men ïathuh ha ngi, la me long uba U Khrist, U Khun U Blei!”",
			"64": "<sup>64</sup> U Jisu u la ong ha u, “Me la ong. Hynrei, nga ong ruh ha phi, ba phin ïohi lawei ïa U Khun u briew haba u shong sha kamon ka Bor baroh, bad haba u wan ha ki lyoh ka bneng.”",
			"65": "<sup>65</sup> Mynkata u rangbah lyngdoh u la kad ïa la ki jaiñ, u da ong, “U la krenbeiñ blei! Ngi dang donkam aïu pat ïa ki sakhi? ha khmih, mynta phi la ïohsngew ïa ka jingkrenbeiñ blei jong U!",
			"66": "<sup>66</sup> Phi mut kumno?” Ki da ïathuh te ki la ong, “Ka dei ïa U ban ïap.”",
			"67": "<sup>67</sup> Haba kumta, ki la bynthiew ha ka khmat jong U, bad ki la shoh ïa U, bad kiwei ki la thab ïa U.",
			"68": "<sup>68</sup> Ki da ong, “To ïathuh antad ha ngi, ko Khrist, uei ba la shoh ïa me!”",
			"69": "<sup>69</sup> U Petros te u shong shabar ha ka phyllaw. Te ka la wan ha u kawei ka shakri kaba ong, “Me ruh me la long lem bad U Jisu u nong Galilaïa.”",
			"70": "<sup>70</sup> U la len te ha khmat jong ki baroh, u da ong, “Ngam tip ïa kaei ba pha ong.”",
			"71": "<sup>71</sup> Haba u la mih noh te sha ka baranda, kawei pat ka la ïohi ïa u, bad ka la ong ha kiba hangta, “Une u briew ruh u la long lem bad U Jisu u nong Nasaret.”",
			"72": "<sup>72</sup> U la len pat ruh da kaba smai, “Ngam ithuh ïa uta u briew.”",
			"73": "<sup>73</sup> Sa shibit te kita kiba ïeng hajan haba ki la wan, ki la ong ha u Petros, “Shisha me ruh me la long uwei na ki, naba ka ktien jong me ka pynithuh ïa me.”",
			"74": "<sup>74</sup> Ynda kumta, u la sdang ban tim ban smai ruh, “Ngam ithuh ïa uta u briew.” Te kumne kumne ruh u la riew u syiar.",
			"75": "<sup>75</sup> U Petros te u la kynmaw ïa ka ktien U Jisu ba u la ong ha u, “Shuwa ba um pat riew u syiar, men len ïa nga lai sien.” Te haba u la mih noh shabar, u la lynñiar kthang eh."
		},
		"27": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Haba ka la shai te, ki rangbah lyngdoh baroh bad ki tymmen basan jong u paidlang ki la ïasylla shaphang U Jisu, ïa ka ban pynïap ïa u.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Te haba ki la khum ïa u, ki la ïalam noh, bad ki la ai noh ruh ïa u ha u Pontios Pilat uba u lyngskor.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Mynba kumta u Judas, uba la die noh ïa U, haba u la ïohi ba ki la pynrem ïa U, u la kylla-ka-bamut, bad u la wallam pat ïa kita ki laiphew ki sbai ha ki rangbah lyngdoh bad ha ki tymmen basan,",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> u da ong, “Nga la leh pop haba nga la die noh ïa ka snam balui lui.” Ki te ki la ong, “Kata ka dei aïu ïa ngi? khmih hi ma me keiñ.”",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Haba u la bred noh te ïa kita ki sbai ha ka ïing U Blei, u la leit noh bad u la leit sdien ïa lade.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Haba kita ki rangbah lyngdoh te ki la shim ïa kita ki sbai, ki la ong, “Ym dei ban buh ïa ki ha ka jingkynshew bakyntang, naba ka long ka dor ka snam.”",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Hynrei, haba ki la ïasylla, ki la thied da ki, ïa ka lyngkha u nongthaw khiew, ïa ka ban long ka jaka tep ïa ki nongwei.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Naba kumta la ju khot ïa kata ka lyngkha, “Ka lyngkha ka snam”, haduh kane ka sngi.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Mynkata la pyndep ïa kata ba la ong da u Jeremaïah u nongïathuhlypa, u da ong: “Ki la shim ruh ïa ki laiphew ki sbai, ka dor jong uta uba ki la kheiñ dor, ïa uba kiba na ki khun Israel ki la kheiñ dor;",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> bad ki la ai ïa ki na ka bynta ka lyngkha u nongthaw khiew, kumba U Trai u la buh ïa nga.”",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> U Jisu te u la ïeng ha khmat uta u lyngskor: bad u lyngskor u la kylli ïa U, u da ong, “Me long U Syiem ki Jiw?” Te U Jisu u la ïathuh ha u, “Me la ong.”",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Hynrei, ha kaba mudui ïa U da kita ki rangbah lyngdoh bad kita ki tymmen basan, um shym ïathuh ei ei ruh em.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Ynda kumta, u Pilat u la ong ha U, “Mem sngew ïa kaba katno kiei kiei ruh ba ki ïamudui ïa me?”",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Um shym la ïathuh te ha u wat kawei ka ktien ruh, kat ban pynkyndit ïa uta u lyngskor shikatdei eh.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Te ha kata Ka Jingkhawai Niam, u lyngskor u ju pyllait ha ki paidbah ïa uwei uba la set byndi kat uba ki ïamon.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Mynkata te ki la don uwei u koidi u basniew eh ka nam, ïa uba ki khot “u Barabbas”.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Namar kata, haba ki la ïalang, u Pilat u la ong ha ki, “Phi mon ba ngan pyllait ïano ha phi? ïa u Barabbas, ne ïa U Jisu ïa uba ki khot ‘U Khrist’?”",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Naba u la tip ba na kaba shun ki la ai noh ïa u.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Haba u dang shong te ha ka jingshong bishar, ka tnga jong u ka la phah ha u, ka da ong, “Wat leh ei ei ruh em ïa uta u bahok, naba nga la shah shibun ha ka jingphohsniew mynta na ka bynta jong u.”",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Hynrei, kita ki rangbah lyngdoh bad kita ki tymmen basan ki la ïa-pynkohnguh ïa ki paidbah ba kin pan ïa u Barabbas, hynrei, ba kin pynïap ïa U Jisu.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Uta u lyngskor te u da ïathuh u la ong ha ki, “Phi mon ba ngan pyllait ha phi ïano na kine ar ngut?” Ki te ki la ong, “Ïa u Barabbas.”",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> U Pilat u la ong ha ki, “Haba kumta, ngan leh kumno ïa U Jisu, ïa uba ki khot ‘U Khrist’?” Ki ong baroh ha u, “To ai ba yn sahnarphna ïa U.”",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Uta u lyngskor u la ong te, “Namar ba u la leh ka bymman aïu?” Ki te ki la nang ïapyrta jam eh, ki ïa-ong, “To ai ba yn sahnarphna ïa U.”",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Haba u Pilat u ïohi te ba um lah ei ei ruh, hynrei, tang ba long ka jingkhihwin pynban, u la shim ka um, bad u la thet ïa la ki kti ha khmat uta u paidbah, u da ong, “Ngam don jingrem na ka snam une u bahok: phin khmih hi ma phi.”",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Ki briew baroh ki da ïathuh ki la ong ruh, “To ka snam jong U kan long halor jong ngi, bad halor ki khun jong ngi.”",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Ynda kumta, u la pyllait ïa u Barabbas ha ki; hynrei, ïa U Jisu u la sympat, bad u la aiti noh ïa U ba yn sahnarphna.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Ynda kumta, ki shipai jong uta u lyngskor ki la ïalam noh ïa U Jisu ha ka ïingbah u lyngskor, bad ki la ïalum ha U baroh shi kynhun.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Te haba ki la loit noh ïa ki jaiñ jong U, ki la pynkup ki jaiñ saw ha U.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Bad haba ki la thain ïa ka pansngiat da ki shiah, ki la pynphong halor ka khlieh jong U, bad ki la buh u dieng ha ka kti kamon jong U, bad haba ki la dem khohsiew ha khmat jong U, ki la pyrthuhbeiñ ïa U, ki ïa-ong, “Khublei, U Syiem ki Jiw!”",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Bad haba ki la bynthiew ha U, ki la shim ïa uta u dieng bad ki la shoh ïa ka khlieh jong U.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Bad haba ki la lah pyrthuhbeiñ ïa U, ki la loit noh ïa kata ka jaiñkup na U, bad ki la pynkup pat ïa U da ki jaiñ jong U hi, bad ki la ïalam noh ïa U ïa ka ban sahnarphna.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Haba ki dang ïamih noh te, ki la shem ïa u briew u nong Kyrini, uba kyrteng “u Simon”; ïa une ki la ïa-pynbor ba un leit bah ïa ka diengphna jong U.",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Haba ki la poi te ha ka jaka ba ki khot “Golgotha”, kaba haba la batai, “Ka jaka Maloi khlieh”,",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> ki la ai ha U ïa ka sirka kaba la ïakhleh bad ka bakthang ban dih; te haba U la mad, um treh dih.",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> Te haba ki la sahnarphna ïa U, ki la ïabynta ïa ki jaiñ jong U, ki da ïakhalai, ba yn pyndep ïa kata ba la ong da u nongïathuhlypa: “Ki la ïabynta ïa ki jaiñ jong nga hapdeng jong ki, bad ki la ïakhalai ïa ka jingphong jong nga.”",
			"36": "<sup>36</sup> Te haba ki da ïashong, ki la ïa-ap ïa U hangta.",
			"37": "<sup>37</sup> Bad ki la buh haneng ka khlieh jong U ïa ka daw ka jingmudui ïa U ba la thoh: “Une U Long U Jisu U Syiem Ki Jiw.”",
			"38": "<sup>38</sup> Ynda kumta, ki la ïasahnarphna ïa ki ar ngut ki dakaid lem bad U, uwei sha kamon, uwei ruh sha kadiang.",
			"39": "<sup>39</sup> Kita kiba ïaid shata te ki la krenbeiñ ïa U, ki da kyrngah ïa ki khlieh jong ki,",
			"40": "<sup>40</sup> bad ki ïa-ong, “Me uba pynduh ïa ka templ, bad uba tei lai sngi ïa ka, to pynim ïa lade! lada me long U Khun U Blei, to hiar noh na kato ka diengphna!”",
			"41": "<sup>41</sup> Kumjuh ruh ki rangbah lyngdoh, haba ki ïapyrthuh beiñ lem bad ki nongthoh bad ki tymmen basan, ki la ïa-ong,",
			"42": "<sup>42</sup> “U la pynim ïa kiwei, ïa lade pleng um lah ban pynim! lada u long U Syiem ki Israel, to un hiar mynta na kata ka diengphna, te ngin ngeit ha u!",
			"43": "<sup>43</sup> U la shaniah ha U Blei, to un pyllait ïa u mynta, lada u mon bha ïa u! naba u la ong, ‘Nga long U Khun U Blei.’ ”",
			"44": "<sup>44</sup> Ïa kajuh de kita ki dakaid ruh ïa kiba la sahnarphna lem bad u ki la ïakrenbeiñ ïa u.",
			"45": "<sup>45</sup> Te ka jingdum ka la don ha ka khyndew baroh naduh kaba hynriew baje haduh kaba khyndai baje.",
			"46": "<sup>46</sup> Te hamar kaba khyndai baje, U Jisu u la pyrta da ka ktien kaba jam, u da ong, “Eli, Eli, lama sabakhthani” (kata kaba long, “U Blei jong nga, U Blei jong nga, balei ba me la iehnoh ïa nga?”)",
			"47": "<sup>47</sup> Te kiba na kita kiba ïaïeng hangta, haba ki la ïohsngew, ki la ong, “Une u khot ïa u Elias.”",
			"48": "<sup>48</sup> Te kumne kumne ruh haba la phet uwei na ki, bad haba u la shim ïa ka spanj, bad haba u la pyndap da ka bajew, bad ba u la spaiñ ha u dieng, u la pyndih ïa U.",
			"49": "<sup>49</sup> Kiwei te ki da ong, “To ieh, ba ngin ïohi lada u wan u Elias ban pynim ïa u.”",
			"50": "<sup>50</sup> U Jisu te haba u la pyrta pat da ka ktien bajam, u la ai noh ïa la ka mynsiem.",
			"51": "<sup>51</sup> Ha khmih ruh, ka jingkah ha ka templ ka la kad ar bynta, naduh na jrong haduh ha tbian, bad ka khyndew ka la khynñiuh, bad ki mawsiang ki la pdang,",
			"52": "<sup>52</sup> bad ki jingtep ki la ang, bad shibun ki met jong ki riewkhuid kiba la ïohthiah ki la mihpat,",
			"53": "<sup>53</sup> bad haba ki la mih noh te na kita ki jingtep hadien ka jingmihpat jong u, ki la leit shapoh kata ka nongbah ka bakhuid, bad ki la paw ha kiba bun.",
			"54": "<sup>54</sup> Te haba u rangbah shispah bad kita kiba bad u, kiba ïa-ap ïa U Jisu, ki la ïohi ïa ka jingkhynñiuh ka khyndew, bad ïa kiei kiei ruh kiba la long, ki la ïasheptieng shikatdei eh, ki ïa-ong, “Shisha une u la long U Khun U Blei.”",
			"55": "<sup>55</sup> Te la don hangto shibun ki kynthei kiba jngoh na jngai, kiba la wan bud ïa U Jisu na Galilaïa, ki da shakri ïa u:",
			"56": "<sup>56</sup> hapdeng jong ki la don ka Mari ka nong Magdala, bad ka Mari ka kmie u Jakob bad u Josis, bad ka kmie ki khun u Sebedi.",
			"57": "<sup>57</sup> Bad haba la janmiet, la wan u briew u bariewspah uba na Arimathaïa, ïa uba ki khot “u Joseph”, uba la long hi ruh u synran jong U Jisu.",
			"58": "<sup>58</sup> Une, haba u la leit ha u Pilat, u la pan ïa ka met U Jisu. Ynda kumta, u Pilat u la hukum ban ai noh ïa ka met.",
			"59": "<sup>59</sup> Haba u Joseph u la shim te ïa ka met, u la sop spaiñ ïa ka da ka jaiñ linen bani ka bakhuid,",
			"60": "<sup>60</sup> bad u la buh ïa ka ha ka jingtep thymmai jong u, ïa kaba u la tih ha u mawsiang; bad haba u la pyntyllun ïa u maw bakhraw ha ka jingkhang ka jingtep, u la leit noh.",
			"61": "<sup>61</sup> La don ruh hangta, ka Mari ka nong Magdala bad kata kawei pat ka Mari, ki ïashong ha marpyrshah kata ka jingtep.",
			"62": "<sup>62</sup> Te ha kaba lashai (kaba long ka sngi hadien ka Bapynkhreh), ki rangbah lyngdoh bad ki Pharisi ki la ïalum lang ha u Pilat,",
			"63": "<sup>63</sup> ki ïa-ong, “Ko kynrad, ngi kynmaw ba uta u bashukor u la ong mynba u dang im, ‘Ynda la lai sngi ngan mihpat.’",
			"64": "<sup>64</sup> Namar kata te, to hukum ban pynskhem ïa ka jingtep haduh lai sngi, ba ïoh ki synran jong u kin wan tuh noh ïa u mynmiet, bad ba kin ong te ha ki briew, ‘U la mih noh na ki baïap.’ Kumta, ka jingshukor ka bakhatduh kan long kham sniew ïa ka banyngkong.”",
			"65": "<sup>65</sup> Te u Pilat u la ong ha ki, “Phi don ki nongap, to khie leit pynskhem katba phi lah.”",
			"66": "<sup>66</sup> Ki la leit te, ki la pynskhem ïa ka jingtep, ki da shon shab ïa u maw, ki nongap ruh ki da don lem."
		},
		"28": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Hadien ka Sabbaton te, haba ka sa shai ka sngi nyngkong jong ka taïew, ka Mari ka nong Magdala ka la wan bad kata kawei ka Mari ban jngoh ïa ka jingtep.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Ha khmih ruh, la khih jumai bakhraw; naba u angel U Trai u la lah hiar na bneng, bad haba u la wan u la pyntyllun noh ïa uta u mawkhang, bad u la shong halor jong u.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Ka khmat jong u te ka la long kum ka leilieh, bad ka jaiñ jong u ka la lieh kat ka ïor.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Na kaba sheptieng te ïa u, kita ki nongap ki la kyiuh, bad ki la long kum ki baïap.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Hynrei, uta u angel u da ïathuh u la ong ha kita ki kynthei, “To wat sheptieng phi; naba nga tip ba phi ïawad ïa U Jisu ïa uba la sahnarphna:",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> um don hangne, naba u la mih noh, kumba u la ong. Ale, to khmih ïa ka jaka ha kaba u la thiah U Trai.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> To khie noh kloi kloi ruh, to ïathuh ruh ha ki synran jong u, ba u la mih noh na ki baïap; ha khmih ruh, u leit sha shuwa jong phi sha Galilaïa; hangta phin ïohi ïa u: ha khmih, nga la ïathuh ha phi.”",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Kumta, haba ki la leit noh kloi na kata ka jingtep, da kaba sheptieng bad da ka jingkmen bakhraw, ki la ïaphet noh ban ïathuh ha ki synran jong u.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Te haba ki dang ïaleit ban ïathuh ha ki synran jong u, ha khmih ruh, U Jisu u la wan tan ïa ki, u la ong, “Khublei.” Haba ki la wan hajan te, ki la ïabat ïa ki kjat jong u, bad ki la ïamane dem ïa u.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Ynda kumta, U Jisu u la ong ha ki, “To wat sheptieng! to khie leit noh, to ïathuh ha ki para jong nga, ba kin leit sha Galilaïa, hangta ruh kin ïohi ïa nga.”",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Haba ki la dang leit ruh, ha khmih, kiba na kiba ap ki la wan sha shnong, bad ki la ïathuh ha ki rangbah lyngdoh ïa kiei kiei baroh kiba la long.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Te haba ki la ïalum bad ki tymmen basan, bad ba ki la ïasylla, ki la ai sbai shibun ha kita ki shipai,",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> ki da ong, “To ïathuh, ba ki synran jong u ki la wan tuh ïa u mynmiet haba ngi dang ïohthiah.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Te lada u lyngskor un ïohsngew ïa kane, ngin khroh ïa u, bad ngin da ïa phi.”",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Kumta, haba ki la shim ïa u sbai, ki la leh kumba la hikai ïa ki; te ïa kane ka ktien la pynbna hapdeng ki Jiw haduh mynta.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Ki khatwei ngut ki synran te ki la leit noh sha Galilaïa, sha u lum sha kaba U Jisu u la ïabuh bad ki.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Haba ki la ïohi te ïa u, ki la ïamane dem ïa u, hynrei, don kiba la sngew-artatien.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> U Jisu te u da wan u la kren ha ki, u da ong, “La ai ha nga ka bor baroh ha bneng bad ha ka khyndew:",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> namar kata keiñ, to khie da leit noh ma phi, to pynlong synran ïa ki bynriew baroh, da pynbaptis ïa ki ha ka kyrteng ka jong U Kpa, bad ka jong U Khun, bad ka jong U Mynsiem Bakhuid,",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> da hikai ïa ki ban sumar ïa kiei kiei baroh kat kiba nga la hukum ïa phi. Ha khmih ruh, nga, nga long ryngkat bad phi ha la ka sngi, haduh kaba wai noh ka pyrthei.”"
		}
	}
};
module.exports = book;